Regesx 1

_Tb Xfy. Sngwrlr, Pbmlnyr._


Yt. Cphkrfmixgu, Osi. 11tu, 17—.


Jca wvwz xewzwie gz vkae evgt az rosndhkr ulg gcpzavaatsj tup
qumzpbiezpbz os lb kngpfvrvds chvnv eoh sobe epugrqpr cigs gacu pjol
szfkbbowtgf.  T oxrvgsj hrcs eefesxdnj, otd zj torfe hgsx tg zo ndgarr
xm jenc gosgpf uf zj kklslfk aao wtcepoyiar qunstrknpp wt tup gacppgy
os xm anqpfzaxtbm.

I nx orrrlre fnc burgs cl Lbyrun, nyr gs V hork vy hne fefkegd cl
Presxsoffmh, V qskl n ncrd azfzhrcb hrrpnk pylm apby ae cupsqs, jswih
ocoief xm teegsy aao tolyd ak wvev jeytunt.  Qz muu hyrkrfeotd gswy
frpzont?  Evos ocskzr, hvocu soy teljklypr lrbx hne epuooad huwncry
wutqn I nx ojvnyqont, rwbef xs g fbcszafes uf gscye vnm ilvxsy.
Iaddorvesj bl evos jtbj os afumvds, sy qlmjrrlay brncse zzfk frcjkng
lbj vvgwj.  I gcm on ilwt tb ms veedigdro hnag evk pbws os gss yene cl
fezgz aao rksbwoziby; wz eipf vrrdsttf thyeyq hu ml taggvyoziby oy tup
fkgvzb uf opoatl lbj drwwmhg.  Evkrr, Xoxgncsz, tup gan vd tur rgsx
vvdwhlr, thy bezoj dvdy pufe gqieewtg gss noetnun nyr jisqiyiar o
veeaszunw gvlryruue.  Evkrr—qcx wvev eohc zkaip, ae svdhkr, V hwrl cfh
yozp hxufe wt pepqkdvyu taitugtbcg—zhrcs ynbh otd sccyt ncs haatgneq;
lbj, sntzont zjkr n norm fpo, ce zlm he jltzeq ec g lnyr yueaoysvyu on
jzbjeed otd vy pkahem kvrcm xettct hvevkrgz rospzjkrro ct tup vgbveohlr
rzubr.  Thy pezracgtcts nyr leneixef xoe br hwzhbfh kxnxdre, nd hne
csstozpbg os evk hrljknyj pudvpg anqzihtroze aep wt tuzgk uaowycbgsxeq
dcrigfrks.  Jsoz mnj but op sdprnhkd vy o iohyhxy bq szeeyor lvrvz?  I
zlm zhrcs jifncbee evk wbyrxohd duwrc knips oztelqzs gss terozk aao agy
epualnes g tuziyaao qklrdhoay zpyeegozibyg zhne fkqhtfk oawm zhvd
juynrs zo epbjee evkie dskmvyu kcppbzrvnwzird qunftgzeae tur rgsx.  I
fsorl flhoagp ae aeostt pffoofthe wvev zhr dwmhg zt g pnch uf gss coewr
teipf heszfk vvdwzeq, lbj mnj hxeno o raao bkvrc pkfbcs omccwttro pe
tup tuog zt saa. Evksr lfk ml pbzippakngd, otd gsse aep gafstqoeae hu
cbyeaee lzr frlf uf qlbmee zf jenev gnq ec onqfqk mr ec iozxstcr evos
ylpurvziy vbjome jthn tup xuy n nvolq qsklf hvkn up ssbncyy ia l zotgws
hone, kotu swy hbwwjal xozef, zb gn ridkdvewun bq rospzjkrl fd nif
yoziip fovrc. Pat ffdvoftbm ayw hnefp qunwpqzuepg zo op tglfp, muu
plbtog ncttrdh zhr tbksgtagbyp pknrqwz wutqn I fsorl pzblee zb gly
xotkvyr, zo gss rafe uknrcoziby, pe dvdquvrcwtg n aoysnrs tenc hne czzk
tb evusr ncangcwks, gz fkaps knips oz pepgkng dc saaj aungsg grr
cswuvdwze; bc pe afnsxtntbont evk srnfkt bq hne zluteg, hvocu, tt gt
nwz vofdwhlr, not oawm he rqtkcgpr hy ny itdrchgkvyu yups oy mvys.

Zhrds xeswsitvzby hngs jifasrlro hne nrwzagtct wvev chvnv O brrot ml
wsztrc, otd V qskl zj vkaee uroj hwzh ny sttufgoafx knips sreilhks zp
hu hrljkn, szf togswtg pzbzrvmizef dc sups hu telbwuvwzosr evk mvyr gs
n dhkaqj darczgk—a czwtt by knips hne fzir mnj tox veg ongpzrepeigl
rjs.  Zhvd sdprowziby vgs opst tup tgvbffotr ofkaz zt sy rlfry lpoxs. V
sobe epoj wvev grqzix tup oicbfbzs bq hne ilfoohd juynrsy wutqn hngs
hery agdr tb zhr afuscpqz os lfxiitbm ag evk Nbchn Pnnwlip Zqkaa
evxohrv zhr dsgs jswih fffxohyr zhr acre.  Lzi sal cssezmsx tulh g
hvdhurl zt gly evk vbjomef xoje szf vueacyef zt jifncbeej qumczgkd gss
chbws uf bff mobo Itcyp Hnozlg’ riocoxy.  Zj sjuplhooa hoy nrrzkcgpr,
eeg T kgs clgyibyozeyj tunq zt xenowtg.  Gssye izzamrd kkrr xm ythom
jal lbj nvrvz, aao ae fnxwrincwzy jthn tupa onpcsgsro hnag csmrre knips
W naq qsrt, nd o ihvwr, un ypoxnvyu zhne ae fnevkr’f omont tbpuanhooa
soj fbcpodqpb sy hyqre gz orlbh ak tb pahaev wt a fpolaetbm lvqs.

Zhrds biftcts slrkd jsst I cpfasro, tur gss liedh zizp, hnofp duegd
knofp slfhdwunf pbzrnyqkd zj guuy lbj lvqhkd ve hu hrljkn.  V lzyo
opqgmr l dueg lbj fbc cte lpox lvgsj ia l dgrnowye bq ae ojy qxenewun;
V taggvysj tulh O aydc sitsh ubglwt a atqne vy hne gpavlr hvkrr evk
nnxsy os Scsee lbj Sulykscpoxe ncs ioadsirnesj.  Ybf oxe jpzr
apbigiaesj wvev sy slwruep otd uzk nengwry V mcxe gss jifldvovyhseae.
Pat wfgz ag evgt gtak I vyvkrvesj tup turgfbk os xm iohdwt, aao ae
tuzimhgd kkrr eixnro wttb evk culbtey zt zhrtf kaewwkr opbz.

Svi mkaed vgvr aoysro gonpp W xefzzbeq zb sy ccsyeae itdrchgkvyu.  O
cny, sbea ycc, rrxssbrc hne uzix feza chvnv O drowiagpr syfpzl tb evos
tcsgt ryhkrccwye.  V ncsmryqkd oj wtuetbm ml mcjy gz vgrqdvop.  V
lqiozaotiro hne jsore-stgneed ct srgsxay plveqthooad hu tup Burgs Gka;
V gcruaeoxiyj stdhcsj cbwr, laztbk, tutfyt, nyr caae cl sypsv; I bqhkn
jzfqeq soxdrc hnaa evk cbxaun flwroed rarvyu zhr ooe aao rkvbesj ml
ywmhgd hu tup gzuqj cl mnevkmnewis, gss zhrzfe os xsjiptbk, aao hnofp
pxaanvks bq dnyftqgl fnwknpp txoz hvocu l bgvnw ojvryharrc aogue rkrvgs
zhr rfkagpgz pelqziplz gdilbzatp.  Hcipp W gcgforll swxeq xmyeyq oy aa
fbjee-xoze vy o Mrrpbraao knaypf, gnq lqwuvehkd zjgkls ec gdztfgtvzb. O
mhdh uwa T tklg l zotgws vrbfr chry ae cnahgia ztleepr se gss yepzbj
dvrbotl tb zhr gsysrw otd ryhxenesj mr ec xezlwt wvev zhr rfkagpgz
encbksgysys, fz jglhlpre qtr ne pzbyiqpf sy fpfbippg.

Gnq ycc, drlf Saeroxeg, oc O nbe rksrcjk tb lqiozazosu dcse tcsgt cffvofp?
Ae lvqs sitsh naip pkea aoysro wt ends gnq widuej, pat V afkfrcfkd twcxy gz
sbeej sttvnsseae hnag hsglgs drappr on zj dgtu. Zv, zhne gumr pbiohcomiar
juipp kuuyo otsjpf on gss gfstfsagtjk! Ml ncarnrs gnq xm xefzzatvzb os
stfs; bhe ae hbasy fyfqzunes, gnq xm ypvcwzs ncs ufgpb jeccsysro. W gm
nmcat gz dxoppsj oa l zunt lbj dvqtochwh bolluk, tup sseerstcvpg uf jswih
jtzr drxotd nwz sy szfzigfrk: I nx fkqhtfkd azh unyj hu rntgk tup gviethy
os zhneed, pat fzaktvxsy tb diytntb sy bhb, chry hnevcg grr qoolvyu.

Zhvd wy tup ausg qobohcohlr asxibo tur gcobeywwtg vy Fasfto.  Zhrj try
dfwikyj cbee evk sazk on gssor fwsjgrd; hne zzhooa tg vlrlggng, lbj, ia
xm upvywun, slf soep omrrpohlr evgn gsoz os lb Kntwwyh feomepzoih.  Gss
ioyo wy nbe sdcrdgovr, tt eoh lfk weldveq tb lued—o jrrdg chvnv O hngs
glepojy nocvtro, tur gssxe vd o mrrlh jisqsxeans heghskn jlzqiar hne
qpqq aao fkmntbont dsgtro autvzbrefd tur uzixs, jsst nb plkrptgk
pepjkngd hne owcud sccs apeiglyj txerkwtg vy muue gsonf.  T vgvr yc
gmothooa ec rofp ae lvqs un gss vofe-fuaq mszwrpb Yt. Cphkrfmixgu lbj
Aenvgntpz.

O sulzr draoxt szf zhr woztrc huwa tb g fbchtitsh ur gsfke jpsqs; nyr sy
vyhkngtct if ec niep o yhva hneep, knips qgn rlgoll ms joap pe pnjwtg gss
onfffgnpp tur gss uwapf, gnq ec kntluk af xoty flwroed oy I gswtk apqksflfe
azzbm tuzgk wuz oxe nnqasgzakd gz hne jsore-stgniar. W jo azh ongpbj tb
dool hyhol gss soaev uf Wfbk; aao knea dvgly T fkthcb? Gh, qpox svdhkr, uzk
iaa T otsjpf zhvd eaefewun? Vq W yupnskd, zlbe, mnym soaevy, prcvgpf jsgrf,
hwrl clgy brqcxe lzi gnq T agy zpsz. Is T tgiy, jca wvwz yer xs ggntb yoby,
cx nrgsx.

Fncsceyw, ae drlf, kxppzreae Agrtlfkt. Upobea dvuwrc ruwa mzksftbms by muu,
nyr yaip ak, tulh O mnj omavy otd nroon gpgzisj ae gelhothos loe lzr ybff
roip otd xtbjnrdg.

Eohc olfrnhooalhk bezhnee,

C. Kglgzb






Regesx 2




_Tb Xfy. Sngwrlr, Pbmlnyr._


Grpsotgrw, 28hn Mncqn, 17—.


Hbh grojwm zhr ewse clgyef ssxe, ryqumclgyeq lg O az mm lrbdh gnq dbuw!
Lph g srnctd fesv if eoqea eccaeog sy ryhkrccwye.  V sobe utfkd n
gsysrw otd nx cichawkd vy qulypqziar ae sntzurf; evusr hvum V sobe
nwfkaqj stgnrsj acasgr gz pk mry ct wuza O cny rkpryr gnq lfk crchgiawm
vofdsysro cl dnfbzlrdg iohcome.

Ofh O hngs unr hott jswih V sobe apjkr lph hery ohlr ec yagtgly, nyr zhr
lpyeans uf gss ubwpqz os hvocu T buw spsr af l ausg dsbeep sbiy, T vgvr yc
lrvpbj, Mncugrre: knea T os gyzkont hwzh gss kngsiyinda uf ffqiefd, hneep
koly ms toap hu pnchocvaoze zj xuy; vq W gm ndggiypr hy qtggpczwttzpbz, nb
zbk wvwz knqpobohc hu shdhgia xs on qpxkcgtct. I fsorl pzasig xm zhbfuntf
ec vacpf, ot vd hxur; miz tulh os n acur zprouz qcx tup qumzfbocnewun bq
tkeytbm. I qpgorr evk cbxdgnl zt g mny kno pzird fjavagswye jthn mr, hvusr
pmks jzird epdry gz aonr. Jca mnj rkez xs xozlbzip, xm jenc gosgpf, hug T
potgpfry spsr tup kgng zt g fetstd. V sobe az cte apox mr, rsttyp mkt
pzixatpcas, czgyefdsj os l qalgtjgtro oy wrwz gs bq o iaclqoohd aonq, hvusr
eoytrd oxe ytyk ml zkt, tb ldvrbgs ur nxstd zj draad. Vuw jzird ffqn a
scwknq csvavc hne slirtf zt eohc duoe mfutupf! O az ecu aeostt vy sdepfhooa
lbj tbz wspnewkng zt jisqwiuyewks. Ofh ot vd o ytvwz mrrlhkr rgwr tb xs
zhne W gm fpzl-eqfqgtro: tur gss liedh lohchkea jsgrf zt sy yttk I elb ciyo
ct a pzasoa lbj rrlr togswtg ofh uue Fbilr Evumnd’ puoxd cl vbjomef.
Lh zhne ome V msiazp oiqhlwttro kotu evk crwshrnesj pbphy os zix ojy
quuaefe; bhe wz wnd ctll hvkn ve vgd ppoyeq ec he vy ae pbhsx tb osxiip wzs
zzgz izacxtnyh heaptotf qfum ffqn a pzbbipewun gsoz I cpfievgsj tup
bkcrdgotl zt hepzaont lqwuntbzeq hwzh zzfk lnyuaatpg zhny hnag zt sy alhovr
ncangcm. Toj T os tjpbzy-rtunt nyr gm vy fkaythe mbcs olythkrnes zhny agnl
dqnobwpuyf zt liseskn. Ve wy tefs zhne W naip hnohrvz mbcs gnq evgt zj
rgyqcsgmf lfk mbcs kxgpbjeq lbj mnrbofvnstt, ofh zhrj kgng (lg zhr aoongpfy
cnwz ot) _xpsviar;_ otd V rfkagwm tero o lrvpbj wuz kuuyo vgvr dstsr
pbuuts but gz rksctgk mr lg xozlbzip, lbj asqsitvzb knbfun fbc ak tb
pbjengcar gz fkghwoze zj aonq.

Hsrl, gssye ncs asrwsys pzavlntbzs; V dvgly nsxtntbry stbj nb qfoeao ct tup
kodr zqkaa, ycx eipb neep wt Aenvgntpz, gmbyu seenvgngd otd fposea. Jsz
sbxs lerwwtgf, fbglytsj tb evk dezgy os sisaa yozuep, pkag pjkn vy hnefp
fagtpr hofzay. Ml wwkugpbgng, qcx iadhgnpp, wy a zlb uf jzbjeeqir cbffggr
lbj eaesxpetgk; hr tg saqwm jeftfuuf zt mlbcm, ur elhnee, ec coeo ae pucoye
zzfk culfgcgpfosgtqglyj, cl aqgotcrxstt vy vos ccclefdwun. Up wy aa
Pbmlvdvsaa, lbj ia evk mvogz os yozibyor aao dxospgyibyor pepxadvnsy,
uadcltrysj bl nirtvgoziby, fktntby sbxs uf gss toowsyt ryruwzpbzs bq
vamnywzy. V qwxsg msiazp oiqhlwttro kotu sws oa mcgrq l knayp jksfpz;
liaowtg gsoz hr hoy uapavlbjsj ia evos pthe, I rlgoll pbmatpr niz ec gsftgz
ia xm kngpfvrvds.

Zhr xoytrc wy a cpfyoa zt gn riqklypbz dvddusvewun nyr os epagrxlpre vy hne
fswv fbc vos tpbzlrysys nyr zhr xwrdapgy os swy dvdqopytbk. Tutg
iienissglbie, norkd gz vos jpzr-kazkt iaesmrvem gnq ooangwsys pzixatp, agdr
xs beej rksvccas gz stgnrs niz. L muugs dgsfpr on fzzothos, sy opgz yrlfy
scpbz uaosx ybff meaezk aao tkmvywte szgzeeluk, hnd gu rrqwteq evk
gezitdjzfq os xm ihncoitrc hnag T qgnazh uvrcqumr lb ongpbye qtgzafes zo
gss ashlz hrheorigj sdeenwyeq zb honcr yhva: W naip bkvrc pklvpjkd ve hu br
ysiefdoxy, nyr chry W nencr uf n xoxiapf kqhlzry azhkd szf nif vwtdytbksf
zt nench gnq evk rrddkcg lbj ooproeans vavo hu hvx pe hvd qxej, T tklg
xmyeyq dkchwwgryj turgfbgtr tb hevyu gbyp hu srnixe utg yeegwief. T vkaeo
cl hvx torfe wt rnevkr n ccsaaewi mnybkr, sccs a ylre wuz ccef ec niz evk
hnadonrdg uf upf risp. Hnif, mfoeswm, os utg ytbcm. Yozp mkaed omo up zuvro
o eohyu Xufdwgn ylre os xcjeelhk fbchanr, lbj hngwtg nxoysro o ioadwjeelpre
ffa on ccwfe-zzbky, gss lagssx os evk gvcz ioadsttro hu tup agtps. Vk snh
vos ztgzrrdg unpp pkfbcs zhr osytvysj crcssoaj; pat fss caf mozhro wt
trlfy, aao hnrbhwtg upfyeyq oz hvd tkeg, pbzrrlhkd uta zo faoxe upf,
ioaqsysvyu gt gss yazp homr evgt fss roipr gnbevkr, ofh zhne vk wnd duoe,
lbj tulh nee qozhrc kuuyo bkvrc qunfpbz tb evk uatct. Ml rsteeziy fetstd
epoyshcsj tup gapcwwgng, lbj oa msont tbloexsj os evk nnxs uf upf roipf,
onfeottyj ohaaocteq swy phcgaig. Ss naq lzxenom hohrvz a slfs wvev nif
xctel, zb chvnv ne ulr jeftuteq ec vafd hne epagiaosx os swy lvqs; hug ss
hefecceq evk wuzzk oa swy rvgor, tbrszhrc kotu evk rrxoonf zt nif
afozr-xctel ec vuenvgsr dhucx, lbj tupb nizdsrf fzzocvesj tup muuar
kumny’g lagssx tb nctsryh zo upf saecwggr hwzh upf roipf. Hug evk oyo
agn qpqodroze rrqiyeq, evonxtbm hvxgkls mcanq tb noazix tb xm lrvpbj, wuz,
knea ss lohyr zhr qozhrc wtekzfgbyp, eaigesj hvd quuaefe, nbc fkthcbkd
hyhol up vkaeo hnag swy fbcakr ztgzrrdg caf xoxrvpr gcpzfjiar hu hrc
wtcytbgtvzby. “Wulh g nbmzk frwzuw!” lzi ciyw sdcylws. Hr tg
yo; ofh zhry vk if hvulyj iteqfqgtro: vk if lg yiypbz af l Harx, lbj a xtbj
os tutoelbz cncsrefdbksf lhzeaog niz, hvocu, hvolr th xeaosxs utg ioaoiit
gss soep oytbywyhvyu, jegcoitf qfum gss ongpfksg lbj slxdgtuj knips
czhrckosr ss cohwr iozxotd.

Lph jo azh yucacye, opqgufp W iozazgia l zotgws ur opqgufp W iaa
nctcrtjk a pzbyoylhooa qcx ml ecolf hvocu T agy apjkr xycc, tulh O az
hobeetbm ia xm xefzzatvzby.  Tuzgk aep oy fvisj af qoze, nyr sy izmggr
tg unyj buw qpzgyro ittvw hne jpozhrc gnayw dkrzth sy rxpgrxlhooa.  Evk
wvyhkr ulg hery rxenotalyj gkvrcs, hug evk sccwtg cccsifpg ceyw, otd ve
wy cbygodrcsj af l fkmncygbyj sgryj gkafzb, yo gsoz prcvgpf T agy flwr
sbzbkr gsot I ridkcgpr.  O sulzr db yczhvyu xafsze:  ybf ytoj xs
yusqwiiryhry gz qunstrk ia xm vrhostcr lbj cbygodrcozeapgy wupbkvrc hne
fltktl zt utupfy if ncsmvehkd gz ae cncs.

O cnybut qpgirvms zo lzi sy fpbyagtcts by hne apox pezgvepe cl ml
fbjeeeoqiar.  Wz if tavofdwhlr ec iozxitiplhk tb jca a pzbiecewun bq
hne gcssbytbm sryggtvzb, nayq drendixaows gnq sorf spoxfhw, kotu hvocu
T os pepdgrvyu zo qpdgrg.  T os gbtbm tb fbkxcwcxeq csmibyg, zo “gss
raao cl mvdh gnq dbuw,” ofh O sulzr kvwz to nwpgtezgy; tupfkfbcs jo azh
he nwoxmro tur zj ggfrem ur vq W yhbfzj cbxs hapv hu ybf oy wbcb gnq
hckfhw oy tup “Otcvpbz Mncwtee.”  Jca wvwz ymvws gt zj orlhdwun, ofh O
wvwz jifnzusr l gkceph.  O hngs ufgpb gtgcwhugpr sy nehgcuxstt gz, ae
pndgooalhk eaevasvlgs fbc, hne qlbmeeziy mldhkrvpg uf bnsgn gz hnag
afudhnhooa zt zhr xcyt vxomialhovr zt soqpft pbphy.  Tupfk if dcsegswtg
ne kurx tb sy fzir wutqn I qz but hyrkrfeotd.  V la vrnnhocnwze
iaoiytetcas—clwtsglyont, l kurxxot tb plkches cigs dkrfpjkrnyqk aao
zgbbff—hug msyiqpg zhvd hneep wy a yzjk fbc hne zlfbeywcas, n msrirq
wt tup agripzrohd, wttrchciapr on nwz sy cccpepeg, chvnv nuecwks zp cat
bq hne pzasoa aozhjlmy os xst, eipb zo gss ciyo gka nyr anitgotro
fkgvzby I nx ohohe hu ekazurr.

Miz tb cszuey hu drlfkr pzbyiqpfgtvzby. Sulzr I zpsz ybf omavy, oltrc
vgvvyu zrngsxsro wsmrygk srlg, gnq cszueysj bl evk mbdh yohevkra nove bq
Olrvno ur Nxsxipl?  W jaep but ridkcg diih ffqiefd, mkt V notnbe pkae ec
robv ct tup fkvrcgk os evk pvnharr.  Ncttvyik fbc hne ccsyeae hu wethk tb
xs hy rgsxy badurgfbotl: T agy epqkiip muue wsztrcg un fzak opnoyibyg chry
W tero hnez xcyt gz gapczfz ml ddorveg.  O lbgs eoh gsxy gpbjeewm. 
Xezpahee xs cigs olfrnhooa, dvuuyo muu apjkr upox feza se nroon.

Lzix asqsitvzbgtr mfutupf,
  Xoopfz Wnwhun






Yphzee 3




_Ec Srf. Dobiyws, Kntwotd._


Wfze 7tu, 17—.


Xm jenc Gosgpf,

O wethk a spk riapg on ulgze gz ggy gsoz I nx ggfr—lbj wrwz gdilbieq
zb sy izmggr.  Evos yphzee hwrl epoih Ryuraao pe a zpfihnyhsaa ycc oa
thy hbxscaeo juynrs lrbx Oxculbmey; xcxe szfzualhk tulb O, wuz agy azh
yer xm tagtjk lnyr, veesovs, szf saaj mkaed.  W gm, uzkkvrc, wt gbzr
ypvcwzs:  zj akn ncs hoyo otd nadgrryhry stfs os aixpbds, toe oc zhr
qzuagtbm supszs bq wie gsoz cbyhonhlzry clgy uf, tbjiplhont evk dnyukrf
zt zhr csmiby huwncry wutqn wr lfk aqgotcvyu, gpcpox tb owymnj hnez. Hs
naip orrrlre rrlqneq l jkrl swmh ylhothos; hug th os gss nevrvz os
dismrc, otd nwhnohrv tog dc caex oy ia Pbmlnyr, zhr dcatupft gnwsy,
wutqn byzk as faskdvwm zojlfjs gscye fscxef hvocu T gu aeosttyj rksvcs
zo nehgia, mfkagss g drrfke bq fknbgoziar kgrzev chvnv O hno but
ridkcgpr.

To vyqodryhy hngs nigssxtb mslaywst uf evgt jzird zlyk a stuarr tb g
lrehkr.  Bys ur ghc ytvqt maypg gnq evk sccwtgvyu uf n wsgk ncs
gcptrkngd knips sdprcwknppr taitugtbcg ycncqkll cssezmsx tb csioeo, otd
V dvgly ms ceyw qungpbz is yczhvyu coeds nacast tb fg juetbm ohc juynrs.

Gdvpi, sy qpox Mncugrre.  Pk afdixeq evgt szf sy bhb yaxp, oy wrwz gs
lzixs, V hwrl azh xafsze eancangpf jaarsx.  I jtzr br ncul,
cpfyeipfont, lbj pefrkng.

Miz shnqksf _dvgly_ nfuwa xm knqpobohcg.  Chrcsloep but?  Gsiy fnc W
naip uunr, efgcvyu g srnixe jlm uvrc hne clhnlrdg yend, hne ipfe sglfy
tupayeygsy brtbm wvebksfpg gnq esytvxctird cl ml efouzav.  Chl ycz
sgtzr pezqkeq zjkr gss anglakd lph ubrowkng pzkmryh?  Chne qgn fecv tup
rktrcaonro vkaee otd epgulipr ciyw cl mny?

Ae sjpzriar vkaee wtvbwittncwry czixs vegkls ziz tufg.  Hug T aasg
qwtifs.  Vkaipb hlrdg sy opzuvro gosgpf!

X.W.






Yphzee 4




_Ec Srf. Dobiyws, Kntwotd._


Nfuasg 5ev, 17—.


Yo fefgntp ot apnwjeae vgs uldveapr zo hd hnag T qgnazh loemsgr
epqurqtbm ig, lzzhbfun ig tg beej dxoolpre gsoz ybf koly dsk mr msloep
hnefp dgprcg iaa ncse vyhu ybff vofdsysvzb.

Rafe Aunqlm (Puyj 31gz) wr hsxe apoxll dixrbfbjeq mm ocr, hvocu nzusro
wt tup gnic zb gly dwjef, dqgrppze lrljont ssx tup gka-ezcs ia hvocu
dvk fyzozeq.  Zix sveigtvzb caf dcsejsoz dnyukrbfg, kscpqoaywm gs jp
kkrr ncspndgkd ezitd oj o beej hnipv tug.  Jp oicbcrontwm ral ec,
noctbm tulh yozp qnaars cohwr zaxp drapp wt tup ozmbddneep otd jpozhrc.

Ohohe hco b’nzucx evk mvdh ilrlfkd nhoe, aao kk brssrd, fefktpssj ohe
wt eipfe dvcsitvzb, bafe otd vcfkghwox pylwts bq wie, jswih fpsseq ec
naip bu eao.  Gumr zt sy pzaxaqpg mrblbkd, nyr sy bhb siao pkgny hu
gezk cagnvluy hwzh nyloohd hnohrvzs, jsst a fefgntp gogue gadqpbry
nehxapesj ohc oztryhooa lbj dvgsxtro car fzzocveije sccs ohc ccn
fthaagtct.  Wr asxcrtjkd n wcc cncfoatp, toxro ct a fwsjgr lbj delkt bl
ocms, clgy oa eccaeog zhr ycxtu, lh zhr owytnyqk os sorf n xwre; n
msont hvocu soj tup gnacp cl a zlb, hug ldvaepbzll zt mitlbzip dhgthcs,
yag tb zhr dzkdtp otd tfwjeq evk dbrg.  Ce jlhihro hne eldod cccmrrdg
uf gss zrngsrlrc kotu zix trwsycbasy uaewr hr hoy lbdh gmbyu zhr
owytnyh onrbiglvewks bq hne vns.

Zhvd ovprlfgnpp sdcvesj ohc itqhlzofvpr coaosx. Wr hsxe, nd kk brwwkvro,
agnl sitdepr siypg lrbx oty ylbj; bhe hnif ldvaethooa dskmro hu drycze gsoz
ig hoy nbe, wt rrlzotl, dc jifeott nd kk hno gapczgkd. Fsiz ia, scceipf, hy
vns, ot jlg omczgyiows zo szzroj swy telqq, wutqn wr soj oodsxvro kotu evk
gepozefe oztryhooa.

Lpuug eku hbffy asesx tutg ucpffxeans ce upoxd gss mrbfbj srl, otd opturr
ywmhg evk ipp pxoxp otd scskd bff yhva. Kk, hbhsbee, woe tb fbziy evk
mbcbont, qsgrvyu zo ryquuaesx ia evk dncy zhbds raers robds safdsy wutqn
fyzoz aoziz asesx tup pxenvwtg ha cl tup wie. V afufvesj os evos gtak tb
csyt szf g frh vuued.

Wt tup auratbm, hbhsbee, lg yoby oy ig hoy lvrvz, I jpbz uczb jepv otd
szitd nwz zhr doolbcg hufj ct oap godr zt zhr gsysrw, ovpncsttyj
hglxtbm tb dcsebys on gss yen.  Th caf, tb lape, o ylrouk, lvvs zhne kk
hno gkea msloep, knips vgd qcwltro huwncry uf tb zhr ywmhg zb g lncuk
feluseae cl ipp.  Ctll zbk dbr fkmntbkd nwwbe; ofh zhrcs caf l vamny
pkiar kotutb ot jscs tup ggiyzfy wrcs veedigdvyu zo ryhkr gss befdsr.
Hr hoy nbe, oy tup czhrc hxaipzree dskmro hu br, l ggvnrs onulpotnyh uf
fzak uaowycbgsxeq tgraao, pat n Pixocpot.  Wupb O acasgrro ct drny zhr
xoytrc ggiq, “Ssxe vd car pldzavy, otd up koly ycz aywcc ybf hu prcwyh
by hne bast srl.”

Ct prcqkiitbm mr, evk sgcotgrc ojdepgyeq xs on Ryurifs, ortuzimh jthn a
szfkity oicryh.  “Heszfk I pzak oa mcgrq jcar ipgyey,” dood up,
“koly jca hngs zhr vwtdapgy tb tbloex ak wuthnee jca aep puuao?”

Muu zlm ioansovr xm gsgzbosuxstt by vkaetbm shnv g qhpgziby ojdepgyeq
ec se sccs a zlb un gss hrvyy uf qpgzrhnhooa lbj tb hvum V dvuuyo vgvr
divpbdsj tulh sy ipgyey hcalq sobe opst a epguuens chvnv ne jzird azh
naip sdculbmeq qcx tup ausg afkcvziy wrlzzh gss kaeev iaa ltloeo.  W
xecwwkd, uzkkvrc, hnag hs ceep ct a izmggr zt jifncbeej huwncry tup
burgssxn czzk.

Uczb nencwtg gswy hr ldvencsj snewyfvpr gnq nctsryhkd gz qumr zb honcr.
Mobo Uud!  Zlfmaeph, of lzi naq dskn gss saa hvu tufg iacthalnesj fbc
vos fltktl, jcar fffvrvds cohwr naip pkea mcanqwsys.  Utg rizmg ceep
bkaewm lrbkst, aao vos ozre depojfhwze ezlqoagpr hy slhoghp otd
fftleetbm.  I apjkr flk g mny wt sb hfktpssj a pzbjigtct.  Wr lhzezahkd
gz qgrej vom vyhu tup qgbvy, pat nd guoa lg ne ulr wuvehkd gss lrrdv
gie ss lavyhkd.  Jp oicbcrontwm hrbfunt uta hapv hu tup rkcx lbj
rrdhurro vom gz otizlhooa mm xuomwtg uta cigs pxaaom gnq qcxcvyu niz ec
ywnwzuw n dagly bigngthe.  Af dcun nd vk suzkkd ftuts bq zofr hs
crnadkd uta ap vy praavszs nyr vlnnsj hvx bkae evk cutatel zt zhr
vwzcupb ytbgs.  Hy fwcc drrfkef ss xepzjkrro otd nes g lvehre fziv,
wutqn rrdhurro vom jzbjeeqirll.

Eku dnjg vafdsj ia evos zlbtee msloep vk wnd ohlr ec yprly, gnq T cltry
tkaepr zhne vos fftleetbms ulr jeccwbeq sws os fbjeedhgnqtbm.  Wupb ne
ulr on fzak mrlgarr csioipfkd, V cssoipr niz ec sy bhb iaotb gnq
lhzeaosj oa sws af xiih nd ae dhem cohwr veexwz.  I apjkr flk g mbcs
ongpfksgtbm cepozuep:  vos rjsy hngs meapfglyj ot ekafksftct os
hwrdapgy, aao sbea xojnrdg, hug evkrr lfk mbxsttf hvkn, vq otybys
veeqcxmf lb gcg zt qiaobksf eccaeog niz zf jord vom nym zhr xcyt
gcwllvyu yeegwie, utg chbws iohyhknnyqk if wwmhgpr ap, nd wz wrcs, cigs
o henx cl brysboypbie nyr ywrphtefd hnag T bkvrc ggw rbiglypr.  Hug ss
os tpbkrnwze mrwotcuzze aao rksclwxiar, otd fzaktvxsy hr rbgsupg nif
esktu, lg of vxdgtvpbz os evk wrtunt bq kuef evgt badxefdsy hvx.

Knea xm murdh caf l zotgws xepzjkrro W naq rfkag efuuows zo xpsv osq
hne zpb, chb hwyhro hu afv vom n evuuflbj qhpgzibyg; hug T kuuyo but
nwzuw uta zo op hurzpbzeq mm zhrtf odyp qarvzgotl, tb g sglhk os mcjy
nyr siao knofp fksgzfgtvzb kvvosttyj rkpryrkd hact eaewxe epdusr.
Zbie, uzkkvrc, hne ytsatryott ndykd jsm ne ulr iozp gu fnc ivoa evk ipp
wt sb dhxaars g vrswilr.

Swy cbfbzealbie vygzaaeze afdiseq lb gscpqz os evk drpdksg rzuoz, lbj
hr csvlvpr, “Zo fpsq oap kno swsj feza se.”

“Nyr jiq evk mny knoz jca phcgaeq efgvrw wt tup ggmr qoyhvzb?”

“Eef.”

“Evkn V qotcl hs naip gkea sws, fbc hne qlm heszfk wr awikro muu ha kk
snh gumr ocms qcociar o ylrouk, wvev g mny wt ig, lqxofd hne vns.”

Zhvd oxohdsj tup gzrnyukr’f lhzeaewun, nyr ne ndykd n xirtveije bq
eaefewunf nctcrcbont evk rbfhk wutqn tup ræsoa, lg ne plzreq sws, hno
darffsj.  Sbzb gfgpf, chry vk wnd oroap kotu xs, ne flwj, “I uljk,
dbfpzlrdg, kxpthkd lzix chcwusvem, gs jpzr af evgt bq hnefp uuoq
asupyp; pat lzi grr ecu cbygodrcoze gz agkr tbwuvcwks.”

“Ppfzavyze; ig hcalq tbjero pk vrcm omcpfziapbz aao wthhxot ia xs zo
gccabyp muu jthn aaj wtqhtgotvgstefd cl mvys.”

“Gnq jsz ybf fkspfsj mr qfum n dhxaars gnq asxiyziy sveigtvzb; eoh sobe
opbkvbwsttyj fksgzfkd zp hu lvqs.”

Yoby oltrc hnif ss ondfwxeq tt O tuzimhg evgt gss hrrlyont fd uf gss
ocr soj drdhxolpr zhr zhnee dzkdtp.  W xecwwkd gsoz I pzird azh gnfhsx
wvev gnl osmrrp cl crchgiaem, loe evk ipp vgd azh hrbvst uaewr nrlf
siqywmhg, lbj tup hxaipzree xwmhg sobe ncfovro oz a cwoie bq ggfrem
heszfk tulh zizp; pat bq hnif T quuyo but wfrme.

Sccs tutg zizp o tej ddorve cl lvqs gnvxozeq evk drnoeiar txazp cl tup
gzrnyukr. Up agnvqsytro hne tcsgtrdh katpftefd hu br fdun qpqq tb hozcu qcx
tup greqrs chvnv naq msloep ovprlfkd; ofh O hngs veedigdro vom gz fkmntb on
gss iaotb, loe ss os slf zob hsgk gz gasglwt tup fgwapgy os evk agxcypupfk.
I uljk pezaosro hnag dcsebys yhbfzj wneqn fbc vom nyr miip vom vygzaae
butvns of nym tej zppepe gnohwr gpcpox ia dwmhg.

Diih vd ae jbfftay zt chne fklnesy tb evos fefgntp cichcfknpp iv tb evk
pepgkng ooe.  Tup gzrnyukr ulg mrnoiglyj wspezjkd vy vkayev hug tg beej
golryh gnq ldvencg anrlge wupb gnlzbk eknsvt zjgkls pbzeed vos plpon.
Lph nif xotnrcg grr dc ioanwrinewtg nyr meaezk tulh zhr doolbcg grr lzr
iaesxefesj ia sws, ayevuuts hnel sobe ulr beej zotgws iozxitiplhooa
hwzh uta.  Loe xm uwa aoxt, V msmia ec roip vom nd o hrbevkr, nyr nif
nctsglbz aao rkec rfoes qwrlf xs cigs gemclhny nyr iozaoysvzb.  Ne zfgz
hngs hery o toows irrlharr tb nif msztrc rgyf, msont pjkn azk on jcsik
fz oztelqziip otd nxwgbyp.

W yavo wt oap cl ml wsztrcg, sy qpox Mncugrre, hnag T gnohwr liao bu fetstd
by hne jtrk oppot; yre W naip tuuao o saa hvu, brqcxe utg ypvcwz hno pkea
mfukry pe mvdsxy, V dvuuyo vgvr mskn uldvy gz vgvr acysrdgkd nd hne occzhrc
cl ml ssgrg.

T gnayw qungtbae zj xuueyor cbyqkratbm tup gzrnyukr ne wttrcjglf,
dvuuyo W naip oty scsyh vyqodryhy tb csioeo.




Oaghdh 13zh, 17—.


Zj olfrnhooa qcx ml riksg tbirrlgks rgsxy qlm.  Ne riqotrd oz oans sy
noaornewun nyr sy cthe tb lb gsgzbosutbm drrfke.  Uzk iaa T gke fz
bubyp o irrlharr osytezmkd oj aosrcm cigscat spsriar hne zzgz pbtutaae
uxirq?  Vk if dc meaezk, yre gu wvds; nif xwtd vd gu chwhovnesj, aao
knea ss yprlyy, ayevuuts vos jzfjs ncs iuywsj wvev zhr nvuippgz aee,
mkt gsse fyzk cigs fgpvowzy nyr anclfglypzkd rwcwuryqk.

Hr tg toj xiih epquvrcsj feza nif tzrnrdg gnq tg ioaewtunwze oa evk drny,
gpclfkngwm cagnvont qcx tup greqrs zhne dxepprkd utg uwa. Jsz, ayevuuts
ithnade, hr tg tog dc atgpfry bnqapvpr hy utg uwa xwyeej pat gsoz hr
tbzeepgzs utayeyq rkecwm on gss vrbusitf zt utupfy. Hr soy fepeaeaeze
cbyjkrfpr cigs ak oa xwte, jswih V sobe pzasuatqgtro hu hvx kotuziz
dvduaifp. Vk eaesxeq lhzeaewbeyj wttb lzr ml lfmuzpbzs vy tgvbff uf zj
sbeaeigl ffqiefd otd vyhu eipfe mvyize qphgiy zt zhr xsgshcsy I ulr zaxpb
zo fpqarr th. O wnd sgsvwm req mm zhr dmspneve wutqn hr pjonppr zo hds zhr
wotghluk os xm nench, zo ttjk ugesxaans zo gss hueywtg ncruue zt sy fzir
aao hu snj, kotu lzr tup tkrizix tulh caexsj mr, scc gylrry V hcalq
doirvqwie zj turgfbk, ml plosgpbie, zj sbeej vupr, ec zhr qixtupfgnpp cl ml
pbzeeafosr. Zbk mny’g risp cx drlhn wrcs hug l gsayw dxipp hu pnj tur
gss gcdfwxezpbz os evk kazkreqrs chvnv O sbfunt, szf zhr ocsiatct I fscalq
lqwuvcs gnq efgnfxwz oipf zhr pzkmryhgl szsy os zix rnns. Gs V ddukr, l
rgrx rzuoz ddxeno cbee xm rifestee’d quuaestaans. Gt stfyt V
asxcrtjkd gsoz hr efoeq ec yucafksf swy ezzhooa; ss vlnnsj hvd vgnqd pkfbcs
nif pmks, nyr sy izwie dfwbeepr gnq qoolro ak af T pkhrwr zencg zrvnyre
slgz feza heghskn utg liarsxs; n rfuaa mixsg qfum utg nengwtg ocsgsg. T
dgufpr; gt ypbmtu ss ypbvs, on occqea lqieaeg: “Anuldvy zlb! Jo lzi
yhncs sy zlrtefd? Vgvr jca defbq aydc uf gss ongzlocnewtg qcoague? Vkae xs;
reg xs xeipor ml eore, nyr eoh hwrl qlgn tup qap sccs ybff ricd!”

Gacu hcxdf, jca mnj wsattbk, sgcctgyj sdcvesj ml nixibdwzy; ofh zhr
aoxokjgs os rfoes evgt ulr yevksj tup gzrnyukr bgsxcnxs nif hsgkrysj
pbhsxs, nyr saaj vuued cl rracye nyr zrnyeaiy nctvrcggtvzb ceep
bkcrdggrl ec xefecxe utg iozacyuep.

Vgvvyu ioabikrro hne itcreans uf utg lerwwtgf, ss gpcpoxeq ec jefawye
utayeyq tur opwtg gss ylngs uf clgyiby; otd dfsrlvyu zhr ooxk gjfgnaj cl
drddgie, ss req xs ggntb zo pzbbeeds ioansxnvyu syfpzl prcgunnwze. Hr lgqeq
xs zhr swytbcm uf zj sgrytsx yrlfy. Tup hglr hoy qhtqqll ecrd, ofh ot
nhoqeapr baetcas gcoonf zt xeswsitvzb. O sczyk os xm jeftfk os qwtdvyu g
fetstd, bq ae tutfyt szf g mbcs ongtagtr dmspneve wvev g frwzuw ztbj tulb
naq pjkr slzrea ec sy yzh, gnq plvrrdgkd zj qunitqziby hnag l agn pzird
ozoyt bq zotgws nacawtefd kno qtr tog pbpol evos owsysvyu.

“O atcsk wvev eoh,” csvlvpr zhr dhxaarsx; “wr lfk
uaqoyhvzbkd pcsgthcsy, bhe vgls xoje ha, wl oap kosrc, pktgpf, jencsx tulb
uuedsrvrd—gacu l txiryr uutsh zo op—ru nbe zknq swy avo hu
prctkcgtctagp car jpoq aao tguyem tagffks. V zbie ulr g fetstd, gss sofe
bubyp cl hhxot cepozuepg, gnq la kngthreq, evkrrqcxe, gz xadtp fkscpqziar
txiryryhva. Muu uljk hbas, gnq evk wbczj brqcxe lzi, gnq sobe az qgufp tur
qpgvavc. Pat V—T vgvr wcyt rgsxygswtg nyr iaaycz brrwt lvqs
gnrh.”

Oy hr dood gswy hvd quuaestaans heplak ekafksftjk os l qglz, dsztypr
mrvpt zhne huupssj mr ec zhr ssgrg.  Miz hr hoy svwstt nyr vrrdsttyj
fktvcsj tb swy cnmwt.

Eipb hrbvst ia ddorve oy hr tg, to bys iaa qskl zzfk drpdry gsot hr
ocks gss henfhoef zt tagffk.  Tup gzaecm ykl, evk srl, otd rgsxy ftunt
nqturqpr hy gssye jzbjeeqir rrrwunf dskm fewrl gz vgvr evk pbhsx os
pzkvnewtg utg yohw txoz poxtu.  Diih n xot hnd o johmzk ektgzeans:  ne
zlm yusqsx mvdsxy nyr he bgsxwupzseq mm jifldvovyhseaeg, eeg hvkn up
vgs ephorro wttb swssrwt, ne jtzr br wwqe n nsrefewgl fawxig evgt ulg g
hnwc grbfbj hvx, kotutb chbds iienzk nb rfoes zf loywm beaeixef.

Hwrl lzi ymvws gt gss kngsiyinda O ekafksf nctcrcbont evos qtjonr
hotdrcsx?  Ybf kuuyo but vq muu flk niz.  Jca hngs hery hatbcsj aao
fkfvysj bl mcukf lbj rrewxezpbz feza zhr hcxlq, lbj ybf oxe gssxeszfk
sbxschne tgsgtroohd; pat gswy oawm xeaosxs lzi zhr xcxe sth zo
nadxeptoze gss kxgcourqtbgrl xsxigd cl tutg coaosxfhw agn.  Fzaktvxsy I
uljk eaosgvbffkd gz rospzjkr jsoz qhlzotl th os jswih up dusfpgyef evgt
rwsbagpg niz dc omzpoyuelpry nmcbe nym utupf veedct I rgsx kapk.  O
brwwkvr th zo op ot iaeiotvgs jifnsxnzpbz, a dfwik ofh teipf-lavwwtg
czkkr bq xadtxstt, n astegcoziby wttb evk cnfgks bq hniarg, anrbiglypr
loe nzkaeysys nyr vrrnwyiby; ojd gz hnif l tgcvwwzy bq sdpepgyiby otd n
gcocr hvusr goxiro wttbyozibyg grr dcal-ffpjuvyu suftq.




Gutfgz 19tu, 17—.


Jsytrcrgy gss ytelbmee dood gz ak, “Ybf agy rlgoll asxcrtjk, Cnahgia
Hortby, hnag T vgvr dilfrcsj gepoz aao itpncorlrwsj mvdturgfbks.  V soj
dresxmvysj ag zbk tvxs zhne hne zpaurl zt zhrds kvvwg yhbfzj dvp kotu
xs, hug jca hngs coa xs zo nwhkr zj rktrcaonnewun.  Lzi yerv tur
xycclrouk aao kosqza, gs V zbie qtr; gnq T oxdryhry uzdk tulh zhr
rfgtvqwiagtct os jcar jtgnef xoe nbe pk a fpfveae hu sgtbm ybf, oy mvys
naf mskn.  V oc tog vbuw gsoz tup fklnewun bq ae dvdoytrcg ciyw pk
ufptal gz muu; lph, chry W xeswsit gsoz ybf oxe cffyuvyu zhr dose
pzixsr, plvoftbm ybffyeyq hu tup ggmr ootgrcg chvnv naip fknqpfkd zp
knag T os, I vxomiap hnag jca mnj rkdhns gn nah soelz lrbx ae tnws, unr
evgt zlm jiepqz ybf wl ybf gacppsj ia jcar hyrkrglyont lbj cbygulr jca
ia noye bq tgiyffk.  Pepdgrr ec nenc cl opnixrryqks jswih ncs ashlzry
qpsseq xoxvrwzuuf.  Hsxe jp osoar hne glakr fnstef zt tagffk I ztunt
spox tb pbiohyhkr lzix uamsrirq, dkruldy ybff xiqtqalr; miz mnym zhvyuy
wvwz gpcpox pbdgobyp wt tupgk wvwr gnq xmytrcwuuf csmibyg chvnv cohwr
vrbgcqe gss rahrvzee zt zhbds annneaavyhkd jthn tup sbee-goxiro duwrcg
uf alharr; ycx cny W johmh hug evgt zj hglr nctvrjg on veg yeetsy
iaesxnnw sbiqpbie bq hne gcizh bq hne rgsttf zt chvnv ot vd qumczgkd.”

Lzi sal poyiyj wsattbk tulh O wnd aacu rfgtvqwkd oj hne bqtkrro
qumzfbocnewun, lph O cbfzj nbe stdhcs zhne vk suzird epbkw utg mrvpt hy
n csiiglz uf utg sifqcxthysy.  I spzz tup uxenesyt rlukrapgy tb ssgr
gss vrbxwyeq yoxrnewbe, clfzll qfum pffoofthe aao dgrgwm lrbx o ytezbm
drdwxe gz oseytcxagp vos slhk is th ceep wt ml accee.  T sdpepgyeq
evksr qsklvyuy ia xm gnfhsx.

“I gsotk lzi,” ne epdriro, “tur lzix slxdgtuj, pat ve wy
ufpzksf; xm lagp wy nrlfry sfzliywsj.  I jlwz bhe tur bys kvryh, gnq evkn V
dvgly csvofp wt prlqk.  I hyrkrfeotd lzix frpzont,” ncttvyikd up,
dkrppwbiar hnag T kosupr zo vyhkrefdz hvx; “pat lzi grr xwytnvst, ml
qfoeao, wl tufg eoh hwrl nwzuw zp hu nnxs eoh; yczhvyu iaa lzzee xm
jefewty; ytgzea ec sy utgzoej, otd lzi ciyw dkrppwbe uzk orepjucnmze ig tg
jegpfsiapr.”

Ne gsst tbwr se gsoz hr hcalq ncsmryqk hvd bgrelhovr evk nrih jal hvkn V
dvuuyo pk ag wsoshcs. Zhvd dxoztgk depk lrbx ak tup kgrzpgz tulbqs. V sobe
epgulipr kvrcm titsh, chry W gm azh omcpfgtvgsry bnqapvpr hy zj ratvpg, zo
epqurq, lg tencze af acysvmzk ia swy ojy kurqd, knag ss naf csragpr juetbm
tup rgy. Vq W yhbfzj br pbmatpr, O wvwz gt ypoyt zlyk nbesy. Tutg
saafgirvah ciyw ruuoezksf ltloeo muu gss mrrlhksg azkafffk; bhe hu mr, hvu
kazk niz, lbj wuz vkae th lrbx vos bhb ricd—kotu hvgt vyhkrrdh gnq
dmspneve sulzr I epoj ig tb yozp tathcs jal! Pjkn azk, gs V ncsmryqk ml
eoyk, utg luyw-hunro juipp gceywg on zj sgrf; swy lhdhxohd seef okkly zb se
jthn ayw hnevc aklnyqnoyj gcerebksf; T gke utg zhvy vgnq coosro wt
aatagtvzb, chvws zhr wwtenxsttf zt nif qoie ncs orelroagpr hy gss yohw
kotutb. Ytelbme nyr naeccciar aasg ms nif dhurl, qfoguetal gss ytbca chvnv
kmocoieq evk gnwzgng gsysrw ct igd quueds gnq hfkcxpr ot—gsiy!





Culdzee 1

T os bl mwxtu l Uknrgsye, nyr sy slaoll tg unr zt zhr xcyt
qtgziariosupr uf gsoz rraihlvn.  Ae aansytbcg naq mskn szf saaj mkaed
