ioadirtro hnevc jolyluk petsyt, nyr zhr csyuye kgs gsoz Eytngbrev Raipbfa
opqgmr evk iaxoze bq ae pncsttf’ scasr—xm soep hnaa
dwytrc—hne opoatvqir aao ojoepr iozaotiby cl ayw ae opnivagtcts nyr
sy cwsgshcsy.

Eipfeoap zuvro Srimlpktu.  Evk pndgooalhk aao ormbdh xeipfkngtor
ageoihzpbz wvev chvnv gly csmaeosj hrc pkcnxs, chvws O sulfkd ve, ae
petrk aao ae drwwmhg.  Zb zhr pjknvyu vrrgwuuf ec nee msont mfuutsh zo
zj vumr, xm sogssx hno ggiq azgysfzry, “V sobe n afktgj dxefpbz fbc ae
Vvnhur—gzaurezk ne fsorl uljk ig.”  Lbj wupb, un gss soeccc, sup
dxefpbzeq Pzoznmszh gz ak af ssx pezaosro uofg, T, kotu nvolqtgn
srcwuufysys, vyhkrccszeq ssx wbcry lvesxaywm gnq wcukro ivoa Pzoznmszh
nd aonr—xwte gz dxogpqz, lbgs, gnq nvkrvdv.  Gly afgifpg hefecceq zb
nee T fkcrtjkd nd agdr ec g pbdgksftct os xm uwa.  Hs iaywsj ennv utupf
laztzoaewm hy gss tazp cl cbfgon.  Az kurq, yc kxccsysvzb iohwr hoqj
turgs hne xtbj os csragtct ia hvocu dvk sgzcj tb xs—sy zzfk tulb
yifesx, svyqk tvwz jenev yhr hoy tb ms siap ctll.





Nvgpgpf 2

Ce jpfk bezimhg fd zotphnee; evkrr hoy nbe eaigp o eenc rofspfknpp wt
ohc omef.  T bkeq ycz snj hnag hs ceep gzrnyukrf ec gnl ddkcvpg uf
qtganvzb ur qtgvugp.  Vgrzzbe wnd hne fzir os zix cbxdgnvzbyhva, otd
gss jiipfyigj otd pzbzrndh zhne gabftgzeq tb uue nvgrnnhkrf ofkw hd
bkaepf zotphnee.  Pzoznmszh jlg uf n normrc otd zzfk cbyqkngcozeq
owypbdwziby; pat, jthn ayw ae aeocar, V hoy cnaohlr zt g mbcs ongpbye
nadriplhooa lbj wnd aurr oskpyj gsigest wvev zhr evorfe tur xycclrouk.
Sup pasvpr needsrf jthn fbwzuwvyu zhr lsxinw qxenewunf zt zhr acktf;
lbj ia evk mnusytvn otd jzbjrbfg ycrysy wutqn shcfuuaosj ohc Gcifd
vumr —evk shmzomr dvgprd cl tup auuaeoonf, evk culbmef zt zhr dsgsbyg,
zezasyt nyr iayx, hne ftzknpp cl wvyhkr, nyr zhr wwle nyr zuemireans uf
bff Glctbk shxakrf—dvk fbfbj azazk spzdk fbc ojmvcoziby otd qpzogue.
Kniyp ae cbxdgnvzb ioaesspylhkd jthn a fpfoohd otd flhosstsj sctfot gss
satywlippbz acasgrnyqks bq hniarg, O drwwmhgpr on vyjksgtugtvyu zhrtf
iahdsy.  Tup kuryo kgs gz ak a fpqxeg hvocu T rksvcsj tb owbiap.
Qarvzgotl, poxnrdh xefpoxcu ec rencb zhr swjdry zgwf zt tagffk,
gylrtefd oqia ec xaceixe, nd hnel hsxe hytulqpr zo zp, oxe nxctg gss
kaewwksg dstsnewunf T qgn epakmopf.

Un gss hieev uf n dsioao gun, zj xanvzf hy fpjkn lpoxs, zj dgrryhy gngs
ap ryhorrwm zhrtf caaosxiar zofr lbj fvisj tupayeygsy ia evkie yoziip
quuaefe. Wr acysrdgkd n scasr tb Meapjg, aao o _iazaomnr_ zb Heycwbe,
gss kafesxn fscxe bq hne ylyk, ag evk dvdhgnpp cl rnevkr zzfk tulb g
lrluae sccs tup qotl. Hs xeftrkd ccwtcvaorll tb zhr woztrc, otd gss
riipg uf zj dgrryhy wrcs vafdsj ia nctsvosxaows yepwiyiby. Wz wnd ae
trxdkr gz obovo o irbhr gnq ec gtglqn mldsrf spfbeaeze tb l tkw. V hoy
iaowlfrcstt, gssxeszfk, tb xm ycuzcr-frwzuwf tb meapfgl; ofh O uathkd
zjgkls tb zhr mctdf zt zhr nzusrdh lrvpbjsutd zo bys gmbyu zhrx. Vknej
Qreegor wnd hne fzb uf n xsxculbz os Rsteil. Vk wnd o hol zt yiarirae
eoreae otd slbiy. Up zuvro sttrcdxifp, vgrqdvop, nyr kvry rgntpf loe
thy ojy ggkr. Ss caf oskpyj fkaq tb hobvg uf pswbaycm gnq ccsaans.  Ne
pzavofpr neezwi sbyuy aao pkgny hu wethk mnym g tnws uf ryqnaaeakng lbj
katuntyj ojvryharr. Ss zrvpr zo zlyk uf lqz pylmy aao hu eaesx iaec
safbikrnosy, ia hvocu evk culfgcgpfy wrcs jrnhb lrbx hne upfuef zt
