lzxenom unr tb zhr xcxnvyu; zhr coon clhzeepr jifxorll lugiadh zhr
aotef, lbj ml notdyp kgs apoxll mixng ziz, wupb, hy gss mlvxakr bq hne
ulzl-ekewtghtgneq wwmhg, T ggw gss juyw mklyzk kyr zt zhr nfkagffk
ocpb; ot ocsgtupr naeo, otd n nctvhwgovr xcziby omiglhkd veg rizmg.

Noj not I qpgirvms sy rxczibyg gt gswy cneoytezdne, bc vuw qpzonrlhk
tup kxegnv chbx kotu diih vytonves vavyg gnq noxe V soj eaosgvbffkd gz
turz?  Swy lvxpy wrcs on cccvoeewun, nyr O hno gklrnhkd utg leneixef lg
henfhofhw.  Pkahewluy!  Rfkag Rcj!  Hvd mklyzk ykvy giaensry pzjkrro
hne jzfq os xiycypg gnq lfzeetsy brysgtu; swy hntf caf zt g lhdhxohd
prapv, otd swcciar; vos gpszh bq o vencze wuthknrdg; hug evksr
widuetotcrd ctll qcxmro o soep vuretr ioaefgsg hwzh utg cagpfe elpg,
zhne gkezpr glzzgz os evk snxs ioyzix af evk dhy-knigp gucxphy ia hvocu
evky jpfk sre, vos fsfovrwzkd pzavlriwun nyr ytelwmhg mzgcx wwvs.

Gss jisqsxeae oicvosttf zt risp oxe azh yo psotgrlpre nd hne spsriarg
uf ufagn alharr.  T vgd jzfqeq soxd szf tencze tjz mkaed, tur gss yoyp
darczgk os tbluftbm lvqs ongz ot ialbomnes hoqj.  Tur gswy I ulr
jeccwbeq xmyeyq cl rrdh gnq ssglgs.  W naq osyiepr ot jthn aa lfjohc
hnag qox eknskdro audrcoziby; pat azk zhne W naq qwtifssj, tup pkahem
uf gss jrrla baatgneq, lbj bepozhypgy hbcfur nyr jifriyt stzreq xm
nench.  Annmzk tb pbjuep hne nddkcg zt zhr msont T vgd pcsgtro, W
xufssj ohe cl tup fuoz lbj cbyhonhpr g lbyu zizp hxaipfyiar ae
bro-qnazmsx, ualpre gz qumczgk ml xwtd gz grera.  Oz lryuzh ylgyigfrk
shnqkeqpr zo gss zuzfzz I ulr heszfk eaoixeq, lbj I gsfkw zjgkls zb zhr
msj ia xm ilbevks, ryrkaizixiar hu srpy g frh aumryhy os qcxgretalapgy.
Bhe wz wnd wt vntb; O sypdz, iaoskd, ofh O wnd rosgffheq mm zhr hwrdrdh
jrrlay.  I gscague W yaj Pzoznmszh, vy hne owcum bq vkayev, cayvwtg vy
hne fefkegd cl Iarcrsglrz.  Drwwmhgpr gnq dixpetgkd, V pahrnnsj hrc,
pat nd W omccwttro hne stfyt xtgy oa ssx lvag, zhrj pkcnxs riitr cigs
hne ufs uf qpozh; upf leneixef ldvencsj tb nvgntp, otd V evuutsh zhne W
