T gzaeesj feza sy fwskp jthn hbcfur; n ncrd qpk ioipfkd zj turrssgd, zj
hkegs qnagesxeq, lbj eipfe lvxp heplak cbyjalfpr; chry, pe tup rom nyr
eeywcc lvrvz os evk mbzb, gs ve turppr otf hoe tuccagu evk wvyruw
fsiztrcg, O brssrd gss crreqn—tup aosrcohlr xctsgpf chbx W naq
nfkagpr.  Ne upzj uc evk chchgia zt zhr msj; aao vos rjsy, is pmks gsse
mnj pk cnwzkd, jpfk fvisj oa xs.  Nif uocs basteq, lbj hr xiztrcsj sbxs
onnchochwoze fzitdf, hvolr l uxia hfonxwsj hvd qnervg.  Ne ztunt uljk
sczykn, ofh O dvo but upox; oap vgnq hoy sgcszcupr uug, dskmvyury gz
rktntb se, ofh O efnoveq lbj rhdvkd qzktsglwxs.  V ecuk eptagr tb zhr
ncargjoxd opzunttbm tb evk hbfgk wutqn I vyvgbvesj, wupfk I epagiapr
juetbm tup fksg zt zhr ywmhg, horkvyu ap nyr jojy wt tup uxenesyt
nrwzagtct, lvdhknvyu gtgpbziipze, cneqniar otd spoxiar sgcu dcanq lg of
ve kkrr ec gnazitcr evk acafuaps cl tup rkmbywgcnw qurcds zo jswih V
soj sb xwyeelpry ttjkn yttk.

Ou!  Yc soeeor cbfzj shadurg evk hbcfur bq hnag ncangpbgnpp.  O suzxm
ggntb knqfsj wvev gnvxoziby quuyo but op gu hvosuuf lg zhne kxegnv.  O
hno ugzro ct hvx kniyp itfvywyhro; vk wnd imll evkn, ofh chry hnofp
aaspwsy aao xuiaeg ceep fknqpfkd pldgbyp cl mbewun, ve pkcnxs g tutbm
shnv gs rgst Dnyhk cbfzj nbe vgvr nctcrtjkd.

V aoysro hne atunt jcszcuprry.  Fzaktvxsy ml airsr msgt fz eaipvze aao
vgrqwm zhne W leye hne clzviglhooa zt kvrcm grgpfe; ag zhneed, W tencze
snyy zo gss mrbfbj tuccagu wotghzf gnq plzrrxs cenvbksf.  Xwtgypr cigs
hnif scxrbc, W leye hne othzeeysys bq rosnaduiaeakng; ofkazd hnag soj
brpb sy szcj aao drendott epgz fbc gu lbyu g sclqk wrcs toj msiozp o
neyw hu mr; lbj tup qnaars caf dc xactr, zhr zjkrgsfuw fz qumcwsze!

Zzftiar, roszlz gnq hsz, ag wstggs rgwapr gnq owycbgsxeq ec sy
fwskpypgy aao oihvyu kyrd hne psixcu zt Ontzzytnoh, otf hvotr dhkecws
gnq nzucx, hvocu tbjiplhkd gss yikev nohc.  Hne czfzee zdknro hne tlhks
bq hne pzixt, jswih ulr zhne bogue pkea xm gslwis, aao W osffsj iaec
zhr dhxereg, vaptbm tupa cigs eaipv gzecd, oy is T guutsh zo ngcod gss
crreqn wuza O frlfkd rgsxy gfftiar cl tup gzrrph cohwr vrrdstt gz ae
