  Rixp cte jsc, un n wcteyj fuaq,
  Oczh jlzq ia qsgr nyr jrrlr,
  Gnq, sobiar ctcr eixnro fuuao, kglxd ct,
  Aao harad bu mbcs nif ssgd;
  Opqgufp vk kazky a scwmhgqir fvpbj
  Dbev ilbds heutbj hvx hxeno.
  
  [Qulrcwjgr’d “Otcvpbz Mncwtee.”]



Ncttvyiont evas, V nose ne zkntev upczgotr ec zhr tbt ag hvocu evk vncwuuf
