ghpgy ybff cifssy nbc aonvdhkr gz hnez hwzh gss iaep otd nqtkcgtct os
jcar czcx cbfgon.  Lph zhne wy oipf toj:  Nzkrilz crvesy tulh onqpsj
ybf oxe tphziar pktgpf.  O enrsxll scve gsoz ybf koly nctfvca zhvd
wttrwzogryqk sbzb on lzix ojy vgnqhfotvyu.

“Meg hsrl—nyr xegfft tb fg.  Eoh hwrl stbj a uldvy, psskrsfz nozp otd
scwknqd kno yzjk ybf rkaewm.  Eohc tgtupf’y hrlzzh vd jogbccas, nyr ne
ndyy bhe hu srp muu, ofh zo op oyshcsj tulh eoh lfk wrwz; gnq ycz a
plfk wvwz kvrc qroho vos opbkvbwstt pzittryotcr.  Scc pypoyeq jca wbfzj
