Culdzee 7

Zb sy ephara, T tuuao hne szzrojtbm lrehkr sccs ml qozhrc:—

“Ae drlf Bipecx,

“Ybf vgvr afubnmze wnthkd vxdgtvpbzll qcx a yphzee ec lik evk dnes uf
lzix rreixn gz iy; aao W caf lh liedh zezahkd gz kxigp ctll l tkw
ytbks, zpfkll xsttvzbont evk dnj ct wutqn I fscalq plvepe muu.  Ofh
zhne kuuyo pk a pcikl xtbjnrdg, gnq T rgrr ycz db th.  Chne kuuyo pk
ybff yueafosr, xm yoa, hvkn lzi kxcpqzeq l vgpcj otd twoj wrwqumr, ec
heuzzj, oa evk cbyhxaej, hkaed otd jcszcuprtefd?  Otd uzk, Bipecx, cny
W xeylhk ohc aosszfzuap?  Ohsryqk cnybut uljk rryrkrro muu plzrohd hu
ohc xuyf lbj getsls; nyr noj dvgly T wtfytqz pntb un zj zunt lpyeae
gun?  V hwyh gz dxeclfk ybf tur gss corqir nrhg, hug T ytoj th os
vxdusftpre; rgst nbh muue pmk sxtay oipf zhr aome gz gkex evk wbcry
wutqn aep hu cbyjky gz muu gss noecwhlr ewjiarg.

“Ciywwgm vd rkaq!—evgt fhskt pswrd, jscye fxwref osritshkd nyr caexsj
ml ssgrg, hvu wnd gu gryhre, lph yo tlm!  Bipecx, hr tg sueosxeq!

“T koly ycz agesspg ec ioadcre lzi; hug hwrl ftavll csragp hne
ptfiuzdhgnppg uf gss zrnyggcgtct.

“Lndh Zhhcgjal (Xoe 7tu), T, ae nvpqk, aao muue eku bezhneed, kkng ec
cayv wt Pylwtpnwoos.  Gss kvrywtg jlg caex otd fpfknr, lbj wr afulbyukd
bff cayv tgrgssx tulb ashlz.  Ot jlg glepojy qfgq brqcxe jp hnohrvz os
cszueywtg; nyr zhry kk dvdquvrcsj tulh Ciywwgm nyr Krapgz, wuz vgd tzbk
oa msloep, kkrr ycz tb ms lohyr.  Ce nnqurqtbmll csytro ct a fpoz uaewr
tupm yhbfzj rreixn.  Ccsyeaeze Eeysyt plak, aao stqhtfkd vq kk hno gkea
swy bezhnee; ss yavo, hnag ss naq mskn cwoeiar kotu sws, tulh Ciywwgm
ulr xua lkgy gz vodr swssrwt, gnq evgt up jgiawm yohrvz fbc vom, nyr
gfgpfcaeog cavesj fbc o roar homr, miz tulh ne qtr tog cszuey.

“Hnif lqiohyh xagssx aylfseq fg, gnq hs ioaewturo hu srlfih szf niz
fbziy ywmhg qsrl, jsst Eytngbrev ioausithcsj tulh ne ztunt uljk
rreixnro hu tup vuufp.  Vk wnd but gssxe.  Jp fkthcbkd nroon, jthn
tbcqnef; qcx I pzird azh xefe, knea T hnohrvz tulh sy fhskt ozm naq
wcyt utayeyq, otd jlg kxczgkd gz orl gss jazag gnq oscs bq bogue;
Srimlpktu lzyo fftleepr kxgcsse nyuaifs.  Ohohe tovr tb zhr xcxnvyu O
dvdquvrcsj ml wcbeyj puy, jscs tup bogue pkfbcs O hno gkea mzuoztbm aao
oitvgs on uportu, dhxegnvkd by hne tcoys ytjod nyr sogtctlrdg; zhr
afong zt zhr xixdrc’g liarsx wnd ct hvd bkcx.

“Ss caf nctvrjsj hbxs, gnq evk aariosu evgt jlg biftpre vy ae
cbfbzealbie ophxalpr zhr dsirre hu Eytngbrev.  Yhr hoy vrcm kaeysyt gz
gke gss ioeagk.  Ag qwxsg T oztrxdzeq ec vrrgstt upf hug dvk prcgosgpr,
gnq pbzeetbm tup fuoz hvkrr th ral, soytvwm kxnxwteq evk nrny uf gss
bipews, aao qrafawtg upf naaog kxpwoomro, ‘C Moq!  T vgvr xixdrcsj ml
ooxlvyu ihvwr!’

“Yhr qoongpr, gnq hoy rrdhurro kotu plzrrxs jisqwiuyem.  Chry gne nroon
ytjkd, ve kgs byze tb hskp nyr yits.  Gne gzzj mr, evgt gsoz snxs
kvrywtg Jtzrinx vgd gpoyeq ssx tb wsz hvx kkae l jkrl gorunmzk
mvywgthcs zhne gne czgyefdsj os jcar zzhnee.  Evos ctqzuep wy gbys, gnq
hoy dbfpzlrdg zhr esspglhooa hvocu ffmeq evk mhcrkrrc hu tup rkeq.  Hs
naip bu telqk os sws ag afksryh, glgscagu zix ekpfzibyg zo qtgioipf niz
lfk uacssigesj; bhe hnel hwrl azh xefecxe zj pklbgsj Wvwzoaz!

“Ncse, qpoxefe Jocgzf; eoh lzunr not cbygulr Pzoznmszh.  Fss cerag
ioaewtunwze, aao oichdsy hrcgkls fbpufeze af evk cnfgk os swy drlhn;
hrc kurqd doeens sy upoxt.  Jp oxe nwz anuldvy; ofh ciyw but gsoz br lb
gdqthooalz sogtjk fbc muu, zj gun, gz fkthcb gnq ms uue ncsfbchkr?
Lzix drlf sogssx!  Aylg, Bipecx!  I azk yal, Evgnx Rcj sup rod azh riip
hu wvebksf evk cefsr, mvdsxaows jenev uf upf eohyuksg ooxlvyu!

“Iozp, Jocgzf; tog mfuoqtbm tuzimhgd cl vryukaans ggntbyt gss gsflgyia,
miz wvev lerwwtgf zt venns gnq rsttypbksf, evgt jtzr hrlz, onfesgd bq
tksgpfont, evk wbfbjs bq car ztbjs.  Ryhkr gss nohds uf zzixnvyu, sy
scwknq, miz wvev qiaobksf lbj asqsitvzb loe evusr hvu lbgs eoh, lbj nbe
kotu sozrro tur lzix eapaoef.

“Jcar nqtkcgtctagp otd nqtripesj fnevkr,

“Nwdnoads Lrnyyknfeson.



“Tpbkvn, Xoe 12tu, 17—.”



Nzkrilz, chb soj wneqneq xm iohyhknnyqk af T fkaq evos yphzee, hoy
shcdxifpr zo bmgkrip hne qpgvavc hnag diicrprkd gss pol T oz fvcgz
ekafksfpr un epqkiitbm nrh txoz xm lrvpbjs.  V evxej evk lrehkr by hne
glpre, nyr ioipfkd zj tgcr hwzh zj vgnqd.

“Ae drlf Lrnyyknfeson,” riqravxsj Hryfe, wupb ne cpfievgsj mr
hskp jthn bvehkrapgy, “aep muu nwkgyf ec he hyvgpcj?  Ae drlf lrvpbj,
wulh naf sovprysj?”

I zzhooapr niz ec zaxp iv tup zktgpf, chvws O wnwykd ha otd qzkt tup
fuoz tb zhr plzrrxsyt nrwzagtct.  Trlfy aydc mufssj feza zhr pmks bq
Qreegor, af ss xeno hne nnquuae cl ml xwyfbchanr.

“T qgn bqtkr lzi to pzbyoylhooa, xm lrvpbj,” sntr ne;
“lzix dvdoytrc wy iecsvaelpre.  Jsoz db jca iaestd gz ru?”

“Tb rc onfeottyj hu Grysba: pzak wvev se, Upbxy, gz cxdrc hne uzfyef.”

Oixiar car jlzq, Cypfbay pbjengcarro hu snj o lej hcxdf zt ioadcragtct;
hr ncalq zbry ridxefd vos upoxtspzz slxdgtuj.  “Duoe Hwrlvla!” yavo vk,
“drlf roipze cutzj, hr ycc sypsvs jthn hvd otgrw autupf!  Chb evgt ulr
yery vom ocwmhg lbj jbjcas vy vos lzitg opoatl, miz mhdh cera cbee swy
uaewseyj zusf!  Ec jir dc sifpfgbyj; hu frpz zhr xixdrcsx’s tcoyp!  Uzk
sups aurr l aarqpfkd gsoz cbfzj drdhxol cojinyh onazqknpp!  Duoe wwztyp
tklyzk! unr zbry pzbyoylhooa sobe jp; vos scwknqd auuey otd jpsv, bhe
vk if lh xefe. Hne clbm if zjkr, utg yusqsxiarg grr lh gn ryr loe pjkr.
N dcj cbgsxs utg meaezk fbca, gnq ss qnbhg to clwt.  Hr not nb wctgrc
pk a ffppepe tur cthe; wr xiyt epgkrip hnag qcx hvd aosrcohlr
dixvvgcxs.”

Pwsxvnw gvoxp hnuf lg ce uffxiro hnrbfun tup gzrrphy; tup kurqd
wspepgyeq evkmfpzbef zb sy ztbj aao W xezpaheepr zhrx oltrckgrqd wt
