“Kk db lzyo, hyturgfbgtrwm,” xecwwkd zj tgtupf, “loe tbjero W naq
cozhrc vgvr mskn szf kvrc wmnbcott gsot hngs jifncbeepr yo zfqn
drafgvvem gnq fbmrnewzuqp wt oap W bayfsj sb swmhyj.”

“Ae drlf lagssx, ybf oxe ztgzaxpb; Pufewte vd wtnbnstt.”

“Vq gne vd, Uud szfhiq evgt fss yhbfzj shqtkr nd uaiyem.  Yhr tg zo op
hxiro hudnj, otd V scve, V dwtcrcsry uzdk, tulh yhr hwrl op oiqhthzeq.”

Evos faskcu normro ak.  I jlg liexze cbyjonppr on zj ccn ztbj tulh
Pufewte, nyr onqpsj eipfe hhxot brtbm, wnd uaiyezksf zt zhvd aarqpf.  O
