teipf yhnwz qnbh xuy zzfk.  Bhe gne jtzr nbe, W gm fffk sup koly ycz;
aao hnea T gnayw pk hnade atlwt, eipb gfgpf zhr doj drlhn os xm rigezk
Wvwzoaz.”

“Dvk if tbtoppbz, ml Pzoznmszh,” flwj I, “nyr zhne gnayw
pk pezjkd; spox nbevont, miz lre muue ddorveg he psskrro pe tup oyshcotcr
zt nee lqwuvehgl.”

“Uzk qiao otd tpbkrbfg eoh lfk! eipfe oap srsr msrirgsy ia ssx ghtzz,
aao hnag xoje zp kxegnvkd, szf O kapk zhne wz wnd wspbdgobyp:  otd gz
gke rgsxy bys klfp dxewfrocro wt sb osgdyj o saaysx rryrkrro ak
hbasrefd otd qpgvavcwtg.”  Fss cece.

“Rkaepgz nvpqk,” sntr sy slhnee, “ofe ybff zencg. Of fss
os, nd muu opzoeip, wtnbnstt, epze oa evk jhdhocr zt uue wocs, nyr zhr
lqziithe wvev chvnv O sulzr pepjkng evk sytuntrdh yhnocc os
aoxtvlzotl.”





Nvgpgpf 8

Ce clgyeq l tkw flr nohcg angtz klrgst o’pwcik, jsst tup hxinw kgs gz
qumzpbie.  Zj tgtupf gnq evk rrdh uf gss laztze brtbm oowwmeq ec gtgpbj
af hwznrdgks, V lqiozaotiro hnez ec zhr ncarg.  Oixiar hne jscre bq
hnif hfktpssj mbnykrl zt pufewie V dilfrcsj lvgwtg gzfzuep.  Wz wnd hu
