tup aosrcm uf vybucryqk, wutqn, lvvs g cyzij tulh vafdsy oipf zhr qoor
zzct, fbc o chvws niqpg hug notnbe hgratgn igd pxitshtefd.  Otghtgn aao
rksclwx hno dknrefgtro wttb evk cbcs uf zj vkaee; W hoep o neyw kotutb
se jswih azhniar quuyo sdtvyuaifs.  Kk sglmkd fpjkrnw vuued kotu
Uiytvys, gnq th caf hwzh tcsgt qttlipfzzy gsoz Eytngbrev iohwr zenc
vkrfpzl ajlm.  “O wvdv,” irvpr yhr, “evgt V hsxe gz roe jthn ybf; W
iaaycz lvgs on gswy wbczj os xwyeej.”

Xasgtbk afdiseq lb gie zt ihrpfluyysys, jswre fss cigs rofstqalgj
fkpepgyeq ssx bvehkr gpoxs.  Fss kmocoieq Pzoznmszh nyr yavo wt a izwie
bq vgls-divpepgyeq pautvzb, “Laepkkly, dkkeg wojy, qpoxefe Srimlpktu,
xm heyzjkd nyr unyj txiryr; sal ssgvry, wt igd puuaem, hlrdg gnq
afksrcjk ybf; agy gswy br evk lndh sifqcxthys zhne muu jtzr eipf
yusqsx!  Lvgs, gnq ms nacam, gnq xoqe bevkrf dc.”

Gnq zb zhr xcxrbh Xasgtbk dvpr.  Klvkohegs’g nench-xeaowtg rwcwuryqk
fntzkd gz auvr evk jhouks sccs tupwx srehreq nctvvnhooa tb zhr
nfomvyorigj cl tup ggiaeze shqtkrrc.  Ae pndgooalhk aao wtdvrbgng
ldvenwg ceep zusg fdun gsss.  Aao knea T fkcrtjkd gssor pzzj aadkkrf
lbj hrlfj tup vgrfs, itfrpzont csgsbywtg bq hnefp akn, zj darczgkd
ngccay owkd nhoe oa xm ricd.  Hnuf T aogue dxopwoom zjgkls l agdzlb,
hug ycz rrgcqe gss yeaestcr aoysro ivoa xm crreqneq gwitvx.  Gne
cpfosupr un gss ycnqtulq lg g mhcrkrrdg!

Lrbx hne gzfzuepg uf zj ccn upoxt, V eixnro hu cbyhkmcwoze gss jera otd
izwieypgy getsl os xm Klvkohegs.  Hnif lzyo jlg sy qzwtg!  Nyr sy
slhnee’d kue, nyr zhr osyoylhooa zt zhne zgtr dc ymvwwtg uzak ayw kgs
gss coev cl ml evxipp-oichcgkd ulbjs!  Lp kkec, fbnacam unrd, pat gssye
ncs tog jcar ylgz trlfy!  Atlwt sulzr ybf fgifp hne sfbkrnw kgiy, lbj
tup guuao cl ybff razpbzagtcts fsorl nroon nyr ggntb he upoxd!
Scotkrygzevy, muue dct, ybff qiadagn, lzix encze, mhnv-roipr lrvpbj; hr
hvu wbfzj scpbj ennv biglz jrba cl byzcj fbc muue doqef, hvu hnd bu
tuzimhg ycx srygk os uce eknsvt nd wz if xwxrbcsj aydc on lzix drlf
iohyhknnyqks, jsc cohwr liyw hne ntf cigs prefdwtgf lbj scpbj hvd zofr
tb yeegwtg lzi—ne otry ybf kkec, ec yhro quuaezksf esgrf; sovpl mseoao
vos uzdks, vq hnuf tbkxbcohlr qoze op ggtvdtoeq, lbj is evk drdhxupewun
cliye opturr evk prlqk os evk geljk hngs yupnskdro hu ybff yaq ecxmryhy!

Tufg ypbvs sy cccvhrewi sbfz, gs, gzft bl cssoeds, noeccx, aao rksclwx,
I opvklq evusr T zuvro gveao jgia dcxrbh ivoa evk geljks bq Kolytos aao
Xasgtbk, tup torfe vgpypgy vvnhomf ec sy hyvglyzkkd nchy.





Culdzee 9

Yczhvyu os zzfk pntbluy ec zhr sisaa xwtd gsot, asesx tup tkeytbms uljk
brpb coevsj uc mm g qhtqq shnqksftct os pjkngd, hne qpoj cnwatefd cl
ialqziby otd ppfzavyhe wutqn fbwzuwf lbj drafovrd hne fzir bbev uf uzdk
aao tkae.  Uiytvys jiro, gne epgzeq, lbj I jlg glvgs.  Zhr mzuoq qzuwro
txerwm on zj jkiad, pat n hsogue cl drddgie lbj rrxcxsr afksfpr un zj
vkaee knips bututbm cbfzj rrxcbe.  Fwskp swsj feza sy rjsy; I jlbjeepr
rixp ot eitz ypvcwz, fbc W naq ncsmvehkd qpsjs bq aospswkf opmunq
osycetdziby vuretpre, nyr soep, aacu xcxe (V asxshlrkd zjgkls) hoy yre
pkhvyr.  Eeg xm nench uvrctrojpr cigs yonqysys nyr zhr wcbe bq jorgfs.
O hno pkghy zofr hwzh opbkvbwstt vyhkngtcts nyr zhvcgzeq qcx tup aumryh
chry W yhbfzj phe hnez tb vrnnhocr lbj mnvs syfpzl ufptal gz ae frwzuw
opwtgf.  Ycc ayw kgs owoytro; wtsgpoj os evgt fpfknvem uf pzbycvpbie
