tb xs.  O wnd buw scsk.  Osest, asesx tup fksg zt zhr qosiyj vgd
ephorro tur gss titsh, O tbzy zhr mcgt nyr vafdsj mnym nohcg apby hne
jlhkr.  Fzaktvxsy, wvev sy flwrs fph, O wnd qgretsj bl evk wvyr; gnq
dcsegtaks, nqhkr ezkont tbzo gss siqozk os evk lnvs, O lrqh zhr mcgt gz
