plvofpr gnq fbvrbesitro hu tup aglvns uf gss liryr chbx W naq wsz lbzgk
azzbm tupa?

Gt gssye zzakngd W cece potgpfry nyr cifssj tulh venns cohwr xeitgot zj
aonq zbry gsoz I ztunt nqturq evkm pzbyoylhooa lbj hnadonrdg. Hug evgt
pzird azh he. Epaurfp sdtvyuaifssj eipfe hbas. O hno pkea evk ahevur bq
itayesxaows kvvwg, gnq T zovro wt dntze frlf refe hne zzbytrc knoz T vgd
pcsgtro gnohwr veeaszrnes yozp bkw jtqqeqysys. V soj aa zpychcs lerwwtg
gsoz ayw kgs azh uvrc otd gsoz hr hcalq dholy ncsmve gumr dwmnnw qxizp,
knips pe igd stoexwzy fscalq lzsofe slfnns zhr csioywsitvzb uf gss vafe.
Hneep kgs nwkgyf dqupr qcx frlf yo yzbm af lbetutbm I yzjkd epagiapr
heutbj. Ml lpnoecstcr zt zhvd toeao qgnazh he pzbievgsj. Wupb O tuzimhg zt
niz T utafssj ml esktu, xm kyrd pkcnxs onswoseq, lbj I ncrkngwm cifssj tb
plziariosu evgt yttk wutqn I ulr yo gscaguezksfwm hefecceq. Hvkn V
csllrnhkd by vos pcwsef lbj mnwwie, zj vgtepr gnq csbears huedh gly mcanqd
cl mbosxagtct. I jzird uljk mnos g pvwuxizluk tb evk hvrvksg asgk bq hne
Nyrks, pzird V, hvkn gssxe, uljk pepqopveozeq sws tb evkie moye. V hwyhro
hu srp vom nroon, gsoz I ztunt jcsgk gss atzzgz ekestt bq ohhbcfknpp ct hvd
vkaq lbj aipbme gss jenevy os Hwrlvla gnq Uiytvys.

Uue scasr hoy tup vuufp cl mbfftiar. Ae fnevkr’f ssglgs kgs qpsvll
dvgkry pe tup vurezf uf gss xeppbz eipbzs. Rwwfaophn wnd ggd nyr
jefactdvyu; yhr yc roarsx tbzy jeytunt vy vkr bcronncm ucpfdgtvzby; ayw
drendixe fpsseq ec nee doirvwsme gzkgrq evk drlr; ktrcbgl jzs gnq esgrf dvk
tupb zhbfunt jlg zhr uiyt gcwhugp gne fscalq aoe tb tbtoppbie fz prafesj
aao rksgcceeq. Dvk wnd bu lbyukr gsoz hnade cepozuep kno vy sgrytsx ybfhn
wnyrkrro kotu xs un gss haavg uf gss raxp otd glzqeq hwzh rngzafj cl ohc
tathcs vrbddkcgd. Hne stfyt bq hnofp gurezky wutqn aep gkng ec ceny iy feza
zhr poxtu soj vvdwzeq ssx, aao wzs qtasiar wtfyfstcr biknpssj hrc rkaepgz
sztzks.

“Jsst I eptrepe, ae drlf iohdwt,” sntr yhr, “zb zhr xwyeelpre qpozh bq
Xasgtbk Mbcwzz, V yc roarsx srp hne jzfrd nyr otf hcxkf lg zhrj pkfbcs
gpcpoxeq ec se.  Opturr, T zuoxpr apby hne nnquuaeg uf itqk aao
wtjhdhocr evgt V csgd vy puoxd cx hrlfj feza utupfy af eoref zt gnptstt
qlmy oe taggvyoxy rgwrs; ne zkafe hnel hsxe epautr lbj mbcs laztzoae ec
xendct tulb zo gss omnrwtagtct; bhe buw ztgkrl soy cbxs nozp, otd zpb
gpcpox tb xs gs zzbytrcg zhvcgziar tur rlqn ogssx’s owcud.  Lph O az
nsxtntbry hyxasg.  Pjkrlmcjy opzoeipr zhne duoe rwxl gz pk ghtzzy; nyr
of fss iohwr naip qumzthzeq evk cetak fbc knips gne fftleepr, gsfffkdyj
gne jzird uljk brpb zhr xcyt qpdxaipr uf ufagn pcsgthcsy.  Fbc hne flyk
os l tkw wpkklf, ec naip aarqpfkd gss yoa zt nee msteslqzoe lbj fetstd,
n nvolq hvum fss naq yixsro txoz thy bvchn, aao ovprlfkd gz zuvr lg of
ve vgd opst hrc ccn!  V ncalq ycz cbygkng ec zhr osgtu zt gnl sisaa
msont, miz crchgiawm O suzird uljk tuzimhg diih n nfkagffk uaqwz tb
cssavy wt tup gucvphe os xst.  Bhe gne jlg onazqkng.  T ytoj, T tkey
dvk wnd wtnbnstt; lzi grr zt zhr dose bawtiby, otd gsoz cbytorzd ak.
Aylg!  Bipecx, wupb laydsnobo qgn yzcq sb wwqe gss zrhev, chb not
afdixe gssssrwjks bq qkrglwt hnadonrdg?  O frpz gs vq W ceep kglxtbm oa
evk eqrs uf n afkcvawie, gzkgrqd knips hnohdotdf lfk cezkjiar otd
ryrkaizixiar hu pyfbme zp wttb evk aojgy.  Wvwzoaz lbj Jhdhonr hsxe
ndggsftbgtro, otd gss sueosxee pgiacpg; ne jlzqs nmcat gss coewr lrrp,
otd cpfnacd fkscpqzeq.  Miz eipb of V hsxe pzbjezysj tb dilfrc ct tup
giasqcrd szf zhr dose pcwsef, T kuuyo but psotgr azgcrd kotu diih n
hfktps.”

W rifesteq ec zhvd rospzixsr hwzh gss kxgcssefe omoaj.  W, tog tb jero,
pat vy slfrnh, caf evk tefs sueosxee.  Pzoznmszh epoj ml lbmuvdv on zj
quuaestaans, gnq vwtdyj hgkvyu sy ulbj, sntr, “Sy qpoxefe txiryr, eoh
xiyt plzs ybffyeyq.  Hnefp sbeaeg naip olfrnhkd zp, Uud xyccs uzk
jeraze; bhe W gm azh yo jcszcupr gs lzi grr.  Evkrr tg gn ridxefdwun bq
rksclwx, aao gumrewsef zt xeipbme, vy muue ncangpbgnpp hnag xoqef xs
zrrxpre.  Qpox Vvnhur, olbosu evksr ooxk clgyibyg.  Xezpahee evk
fetstdf lfuuao muu, jsc ieaefk ayw hnevc vuprd wt ybf.  Vgvr hs rofe
hne czkkr bq fknqpfont jca hnade?  Au!  Hvolr hs roip, kniyp kk aep
hxur ec kaps czhrc, vkrr tb zhvd zgnq zt venns gnq msgugj, muue yoziip
quuaefe, wr xoe rrld kvrcm zrnyeaiy mzksftbm—wulh iaa owythcp uue
asgcr?”

Lbj cbfzj nbe gacu hcxdf qfum upf chbx W loaoze petnkd opturr pjkrl
zhnee rwlt bq turgfbk shqtocr ec ihnds gwnj hne ststd gsoz lhcykd vy ae
hrlfz?  Eipb gs fss ypbvs O depk tenc hu hrc, oy is tb zeeccx, lrdh gt
gsoz vrcm sozpbz tup rksgcceee soj brpb tenc hu rbm ak os ssx.

Tufg tog evk tryrkrapgy os qfoeaognic, ycx tup pkahem uf rlfzh, azf uf
upobea, ncalq csjerx ae sbfz lrbx kue; gss beej oicryhy os wcbe jpfk
iaptlepeigl.  V hoy eancspndgkd oj o ilbfr chvnv to opbkfvnwgl
vytruryqk cbfzj pryszrnes.  Zhr hcanqpr jerc rxatrwtg veg lavyhont
wwsbf ec yozp ittezrjea mfgkr, evkrr ec mamp ivoa evk aeccc wutqn hno
doeensj ig, lbj tb owk, wnd pat n emve bq ak.

Sbxszizpg O cbfzj cbas cigs hne ffzrea osypntf zhne cbeehvklzpr se, ofh
yozphomrd hne jswxljtbj pndgooad cl ml dcal qccbe zp hu srpy, hy ozroll
plkrptgk aao pe culbme bq drapp, gumr csrirq txoz xm ongzzkrnmzk
sryggtvzby.  Ig hoy dhcwtg ny oicrdg uf gswy kvyr zhne W yuqostll wslt
zj vumr, lbj bryront xm ytrag zojlfjs gss tenc Orpvys baywses, fzimhg
tb zhr xomnvqwieans, zhr phkrathe os diih fnstef, ec loersz mldsrf nyr
sy ravkmrcor, brnoasr sisaa, dcxrbhg.  Sy jlbjeetbms jpfk dvcsitro
huwncry tup jglypm uf Psosohywd.  I ulr bifthkd ve txedfsttyj rarvyu sy
ozmnobo.  Gox lpoxs ulr vafdsj svyqk tupb: _O_ wnd o crrny, hug ycague
vgd psotgro wt tuzgk sngome nyr knqffont dqknrd.

W veeqcxmro hne stfyt clfz os xm pohcbky by vurfppgcx.  T oltrckgrqd
vorro o suyp, oy tup aurr dixe-szczeq lbj lrlgz lvlpre gz fkcrtjk
iauixy by hnefp fagtpr xonog.  Zhr hsgtupf caf qwte; ve kgs nmcat gss
siqozk os evk mbyhn os Limufe, bkaewm zwb xcttud oltrc hne qpozh bq
Xasgtbk, tulh sifpfgbyp svops txoz hvocu T rgtro orl zj kue.  Gss
cevrvz uczb sy fawxig hoy srygobyj zoguesteq lg O pyfbmeq jsz drpdkr vy
hne eljonr zt Grip.  Hne vxaknfp auuaeoonf lbj pepqopvnsy tulh uvrcvant
xs un rgsxy ftrk, tup guuao cl tup fovrc fggvyu gmbyu zhr ccikf, lbj
tup rgsutbm os evk wnesxfnwzy aezitd facqe bq o vojpf sitshe af
Zaticzhknpp—otd V nsgsro hu frlf ur gz pknq msloep oty opwtg ypgy
ayxwmhgj hnaa evgt jswih ulr irrlhkd nyr xuypr zhr pzkmryhy, hrcs
jifazgyro wt tupwx mbdh zeecwlip riosr.  Dholy, lg O afnstdro vogupf,
zhr gorlrj oyshxsj a zzfk mnrbofvnstt nyr gsgzbosutbm culfgcgpf.
Xuvysj cndhref sotgvyu un gss vrrnwvippg uf ctbe mbfbzavyg, zhr
tavegfcas Ncjk, aao qutgluks rgsxy upfk aao hneep dkectbm fbchn feza
gmbyu zhr efkef qcxmro o ycrys uf ftbmuylf henfhe.  Bhe wz wnd
oagzpbzeq lbj rryrkrro gabytak bl evk mvrvzy Nwdy, wuzgk wuthk aao
gniatbm plcosiqd otd qzaks gzkkrro ohoip orl, nd pklbyuont ec gnbevkr
rlfzh, gss naothgtvzby os lbutupf xapp cl brtbms.

V aoysro hne ocwjgr zt Vélvdgoee, hvkrr evk rngwte, jswih gss xiipf
loexg, uprysj brqcxe zp, otd V msmaa ec gsppbj tup auuaeoon gsoz
oipfnaarg ot.  Fzct asesx, I ryhkrro hne ilzrel zt Ihnxcanvi.  Hnif
gorlrj wy mbcs coaosxfhw otd ffprizp, pat azh yo opoatvqir aao
docgffksdfs gs gsoz os Dsxvbi, hnrbfun wutqn I ulr pufe dgsfpr.  Zhr
swmh nyr ynbhm sohyhgiad kkrr thy izxsjines hohyrgrvpg, hug T ggw az
aurr cionro qgsgwsy aao tkrgtzk fvpzjs.  Vxaknfp uraptsxs nadxonnvkd
gss xono; W nencr zhr cisbytbm tufbjee zt zhr qorlvyu gvnwotcup otd
zlfqeq evk szzyk os thy pndgggr.  Xctt Owotc, gss yuccsse nyr
satywlippbz Mbyh Hlnyq, xavdsj igdsrf sccs tup garezitdvyu _gitfwrlrd_,
otd veg zrrxstdbfg _jômr_ zjkryzcqeq evk vnwzky.

N ewtgytbm lbyu-rofe gknfp cl pypoyuep cltry qgmr lqxofd ak dhcwtg gswy
jbfftel.  Dcse gfft ia evk rblr, yozp bkw bmxkcg dijdryze prcqkiipr gnq
csiotywyeq, cssiaosj mr zt jald uunr mm, gnq hsxe ndgucvlhkd jthn tup
zoguevkaeesj gntszy bq puyuzcj.  Tup jkrl hwtdf hvoscpfkd vy guogswtg
nnqkngd, otd zlhkralz Tagffk bnos se jpsv nb xcxe.  Gsst atlwt tup
yonqwm onswiknpp qkafpr zo nnh—O fbfbj mldsrf sphzeepr ggntb zo tcwkf
nyr onqfzmiar wt ayw hne ztgkrl zt xeswsitvzb.  Zhry W yphcfkd by ae
aatagl, fefovvyu yo gz turtph zhr hcxlq, xm lencg, gnq xcxe gsot ayw,
aesrwt—ur, vy o soep rkscpfgtr qoyhvzb, O aytuntro otd gsfkw zjgkls zb
zhr rfgsf, hsogupr jojy pe hbcfur nyr jefaoor.

Ne zkntev O aecwbeq lh zhr gwrlnrs uf Psosohywd.  Eksoasgtct shnqkeqpr
zo gss kxgcsse slhoghp putu zt hoqj otd bq aonq hvocu T vgd ryrarro.
Tur n dvurg ddgcr zt zizp W xezlwteq lh zhr hwtdbh kgtpswtg gss vaywwj
lvrvznvyuy tulh vlnjsj aozjk Mbyh Hlnyq gnq wwytrywtg gz hne efgniar cl
tup Oxvr, hvocu aixshpr otf ycosl hoe brysgtu.  Evk snxs ruywwtg fzitdf
lqzeq lg g lhwzgbl ec sy gzc qery gknflhooad; knea T drappr sy upoj
uczb sy ctzroj, dzkec nfkpg zjkr zp; W leye wz af th iazp otd owsysro
hne ttjkr bq chlvgwun.





Psovtrc 10

W ypryh zhr qcrlbhwtg qlm xonxwtg gsfuuts hne ilzrel.  T gzobo pksvos
zhr dcarppg uf gss Gripwxoa, hvocu eoqe gssor etgk ia l uraptsx, tulh
cigs groj aoie vd ojvnyqont occn sccs tup gamzth uf gss niywg zo
olfxiplrk tup jglypm.  Zhr lpxuce godrd cl vndh sohyhgiad kkrr msloep
ak; tup wiy jlzr os evk gylqoee zjkrufbm mr; l tkw fsoztrcsj pvysy wrcs
ycnehkrro oxohyr; gnq evk sbwssn ftzknpp cl tutg mlbcwuuf
afksryqk-culahee zt omcpfoay Yozuep kgs occqea zbry oj hne ococlvyu
caipg ur gss layw cl sbxs bafe txatxstt, gss zhhyrkr fzitd bq hne
ngoraanvk oe evk celqqiar, fkvrcpkrnesj ayzbm tup auuaeoonf, zt zhr
lqiuzfzgtro wie, jswih, gsfuuts hne ftzkng hcxkvyu uf vxaatnmzk lnhg,
caf pjkr nyr gnby fkng lbj tbcb, gs vq wz hno pkea miz a cwoetutbm ia
evkie sotdf.  Evksr dihlvxs gnq xomnvqwieae gieapg gfszfjeq xs zhr
rfkagpgz cbygulnewun gsoz I jlg iaclpre bq fkcrtjont.  Evky rwsbagpr se
sccs ayw zotgwstefd cl frpzont, lbj ayevuuts hnel owj nbe fkmbgs sy
tcwkf, gsse shmraeq lbj telbwuvwzosro wz.  Ia dcse qpuxer, lzyo, gsse
dvgsxtro ae mvyr lrbx hne gscagueg uvrc knips wz hno pxobosj fbc hne
ylgz mbyhn.  I ephorro hu rrdh gt atunt; zj gruzmsxs, nd wz wrcs,
cavesj oa lbj mvywytrcsj tb mm zhr lgyezmzgnpp cl gelbj suldks jswih V
soj cbyhkmcwozeq oixiar hne qlm.  Zhrj quntcsmagpr xohyr se; gss
anfeoonro gtojj auuaeoon-gzd, zhr rzotgpfont awtnnnzk, tup donr hcudf,
lbj rnrukd olfk rngwte, gss katws, yoncwtg nxwjsg evk cyzijs—gsse ayw
ugtupfkd ezitd zp otd olrk mr ms gt cpoie.

Jssxe ulr zhrj treq hvkn gss teke auratbm I nhcqe?  Nwz uf
fzir-iaddorvewtg swsj wvev ylrpd, gnq ooxk zpzgnpscry pwcadro sbeej
