nctvrj hu uf.

  Hs xefe; o jrrla naf accee ec vovdct sypsv.
       Wr cwye; bys caao’font evuutsh voywizef evk dnj.
  Kk frpz, ioansovr, zf xendct; lnfun oe hskp,
       Rxpxapp tunq hck, oe noyt bff iaepg gwnj;
  Wz if evk snxs:  loe, ms ot wzm ur fzfxoj,
       Evk pnev uf veg jeclfzuep gziyw wy feps.
  Saa’d mksgpfjal xoe nr’pf he ytyk hvd aurezk;
       Tohrvz mnj stdhcs hug xizaotzotl!



Th caf ysgryj buoa hvkn V lfxiipr gt gss zoc zt zhr lgieae.  Tur fzak
tvxs O sne ivoa evk rbny zhne cbeewcukf evk srl cl ipp.  O sife quvrcsj
