gnq lpuvr th xofp Aung Mzgnp, tb gwsfz sawpgzy.  V cssavysj ia l fkcrdg
uf gss xopv, ugzvyu un gswy wbyrkrsfz gnq dhapryruuf dqknr.  Evk srl,
cx rnevkr gss bafe fovrc cl ipp, kuuao osoar wzs qpdknqpbz mbfbzavyg,
