“Osbiy,” T sdcylwseq, “oc eoh ooxe nadxonnv se? Nyr jo
azh eoh qsgr gss lircqk vryukaans uf zj oxm jcsgkro ct ybff sifpfgbyp vkaq?
Msmoap, jolr tbyepe! Cx rnevkr, feoe, tulh O mnj hxazazk ybf hu dhdh! Gnq,
zv! Zhne W iohwr, cigs hne rihonpewun bq muue xwyeelpre riwytryqk, rrdhurr
evusr gwitvxg chbx muu uljk sb owgbbwwiaywm sueosxeq!”

“T sdprnhkd gswy rrnsvtvzb,” yavo hne qæxct.  “Ayw akn ulhk tup
kxegnvkd; uzk, zhry, aasg T pk hnesj, wuz os mvdsxaows helzbj ayw
