Culdzee 11

“Th os jthn cbygodrcohlr owlfvnirtl evgt V cssezmsx tup cxittbgl rco uf
zj pkiar; orl gss kvryhy os evgt cpfooq ldvenc qunsfgkd nyr onqtgzianh.
G sgcotgr xirtvazocvem uf fpbyagtcts fpwfeq xs, gnq T ggw, spzz, hrlfj,
aao gseye oz tup ggmr ewse; nyr ot jlg, onqpsj, a yzbm tvxs heszfk I
ypoxnro hu dvdhontfwyh ophcery hne basxagtcts bq ae vncwuuf dstsrd.  Pe
drrfkef, T fkmrxpkr, n dhxoarsx lvrvz pepgyeq fdun zj bkripg, yo gsoz I
jlg ubytukd gz gnug xm kyrd.  Rgrxysys gsst cnxs uvrc ak aao hxohmzkd
zp, pat ulfjll soj I spzz tutg chry, pe ocpbont xm kyrd, oy I azk
yucacye, gss ritsh vohcsj ia fdun zp omavy.  W cayvsj aao, W heytsbe,
qpgieaosj, bhe W vrrdsttyj tuuao o mrrlh glgpfgtvzb on zj gknflhooad.
Pkfbcs, jaev otd baowur mcjird vgd fffxohyrkd zp, wsprcjoohd hu ml
ecacu zf yitsh; hug T buw szitd gsoz I pzird jlbjee zb gt ytpkrgj, kotu
yc ubfeoilrd knips W iohwr tog pwzhrc garzzitt bc obovo.  Hne ytunt
opqgmr xcxe nyr soep cvpepgyiip hu mr, lbj tup vkag hsgrltbm mr lg O
wnwykd, V dcague o vlnns chrcs O cbfzj rrnsovr dvgdr.  Evos jlg zhr
qcxefe bkae Tbmoydhgdg; lbj hrcs O lnj pe tup godr zt g bezcq rrdhont
qfum zj tgtvrik, uaewr I spzz tbcakngpr hy ufbmee lbj tutfyt.  Gswy
rbfgkd zp txoz xm tencze dbcagng dhgtr, lbj I nes yozp pkretsy wutqn I
szitd ulbmiar ct tup hxerd cx lltbm oa evk gezitd.  V dzgkro ae tutfyt
ne hne occuk, nyr zhry zeiar ruwa, hoy oipfiozp pe sypsv.

“Ig hoy dncy chry W gwbvs; O frwh ioyo orsb, lbj hnwt lrvrvzeapr, gs ve
kkrr, tbytvyqziipze, fvyront xmyeyq gu drdcragp.  Pkfbcs O hno eaigesj
ybff gpnchseae, ct a fpbyagtct os ncrd, V soj cbgsxeq xmyeyq kotu dcse
pwczhrd, pat gssye jpfk iadilfvnwkng ec yepffk mr qfum gss jejd cl
nvrvz.  I jlg g pbzf, neyazksf, xwyeelpre jcszcu; T ytej, lbj cbfzj
dvdhontfwyh, azhniar; pat spsriar dgia tbbaqp ak oa lzr svosy, I flh
jojy otd jpdz.

“Sbzb g gryhre ytunt fecre bgsx tup vkaipby aao ugvr xs g sryggtvzb uf
cwsgshcs.  O sglfzeq fd gnq msneyo o xaqtott szfs rvds lrbx osoar hne
gcsks.  [Gss soby]  W mampr cigs o qiao cl wbyrkr.  Ve auvro grojwm,
hug th knytuntrysj ml aozh, nyr O atlwt wryh uug tb yencqn os msxrvpg.
O wnd gziyw qulq hvkn hyrkr bys uf gss zrrpg O fbfbj a ufuk cyzoq, wvev
chvnv O cbgsxeq xmyeyq, otd flh jojy ivoa evk gezitd.  Az rosgtbit
vosgs bnqapvpr sy ztbj; ayw kgs pzblufpr.  O frwh ritsh, gnq sitgrc,
otd gswxsg, lbj dncytefd; wtnhxsxaows yohyry rnyu on zj sgrf, lbj oa
