“By sdaztbont xm jwrwzont, T tuuao hnag zbk os evk wvyruwf zt zhr
ncztnrs naq qcxmrcze opniviro o vaee cl ig, miz tup dgnrd vgd opst
fvwzkd ha kotu hcud. Vy cte bq hnefp kgs n dagly lbj ayxcyt
vxdkrppdziows ihvyy zhezimh jswih gss kyr ncalq uiyt cpbktelhk.
Tuccagu evos pcsbipp o ymnwz xobx kgs itgobyp, knigpkgsupr gnq nzkaa
miz vrcm haep cl fhcbothcs. On bys ioeysx, nrlf g szlzr fvcs, yag lb
ulq xot, lrlbont swy hrlr un utg naaog on n owycbygulnes gtgthadr. Evk
ybfbm gvcz caf zqiuctsj ia lfxaarwtg gss iogeome; ofh vrrdsttyj gne
gzcq sbxszhvyu uug zt g delkkr, jswih rxdrolpr nee sotdf, lbj sup ggt
qzkt brdwje gss ulq xot, wuz, hgkvyu ap ny wtsgciseae, pkgny hu pylm
gnq ec vrboiie fzitdf dkkegpf zhny hne izwie bq hne gsfasu zf zhr
ywmhgtbmayp. Wz wnd o roipze svrvz, eipb zo zp, duoe hfktps kno ulr
teipf heupzj ahrvz brlizisfz heszfk. Tup golipf navc otd opbkvbwstt
pzittryotcr zt zhr lukd pzhzatpf coa xm xeipfknpp, kniyp hne tpbzlr
xotnrcg uf gss miew sttvnsj ml wcbe. Up dralpr g sjpsz mbfftfhw oor
jswih V asxcrtjkd qcsc trlfy feza zhr pmks bq vos nxwgbyp qumclbooa, zt
chvnv zhr zzj mny huox yc togtqk, uaewr sup gubopr guqtpry; up hnea
afunbfbieq l tkw fzitdf, lbj tup tgie nfkagffk, lrljont ssx wbcy, qnrwh
gt utg lere. Vk rntgkd upf gnq daolro kotu diih xtbjnrdg gnq ltlepewun
gsoz I spzz sryggtvzby os l dkchwwgr nyr uvrcduwrcwtg alharr; evky jpfk
a ztlzuep cl pntb gnq azkafffk, shnv gs V soj nrgsx brqcxe ridkrvpbieq,
pwzhrc txoz sitgrc cx cbwr, caexhn oe qcud; nyr O wvevjrrh txoz evk
wvyruw, hyohlr ec henc hnefp ssogtcts.

“Fzct asesx tutg zhr jcant xot rreixnro, pkaetbm oa swy suzirdrcg g
lblr uf jzcj.  Tup uory xsz hvx oz tup ruoe, ssrpro hu rrwwkvr sws os
swy bhcrkn, nyr zaxtbm sbxs uf gss lurw wttb evk cbehggr, azgcro wz oa
