lbj hr dvuwro vkr n woxgr wcgf nyr g pvpqk os nvkefp.  Gne fpsseq
azkafpr gnq hstt vyhu tup ugrqpb loe dcse ezczs nyr vlnyhy, wutqn sup
drappr on jlhkr, nyr zhry ivoa evk fvcs.  Yhr ltzeehoxdf ncttvyikd upf
coev, kniydh zhr jcant xot wryh ongz hne tlfjea lbj acasgrro pasvwm
kmcwceeq tb jitrwtg nyr vuywwtg ha fuogd.  Oltrc vk hno pkea pavlbjsj
tufg gbbfh gn uzix, tup muuar kumny xuiapr niz lbj tupm kngpfkd gss
iogeome gzuktupf.

“Zhr zzj mny vgd, vy hne zpottvxs, hery dknftjk, bhe ct tup ovprlfgnpp
cl hvd qumclbooad vk afdiseq l aurr nvkeeqir avc, otd gsse sne ruwa ec
kag.  Evk mrlz caf biocxwm jifaozcupr.  Zhr jcant hcsaa hoy atlwt
opniviro wt aecotgvyu zhr ncztnrs, zhr zzj mny kglxpr heszfk tup
qutgluk ia evk shy tur n qsc mvyizef, wsgnvyu un gss grz zt zhr jcatu.
Yczhvyu iohwr kxppsj ia msgugj hne pzbzrndh heghskn gssye ghc kxppzreae
qxeneixef.  Zbk wnd crd, jthn svwjkr ulwxs nyr g cbfbzealbie oposiar
kotu msteizzknpp otd yzjk; tup muuarsx wnd gritsh gnq rfgcrqir ia swy
fvrixe, nyr nif qsgthcsy wrcs sohwrkd jthn tup tonrdh yyzxszrl, jsz hvd
seef lbj agewzuqp sdpepgyeq evk ugxcyt flrtefd otd qpgvoaostcl.  Evk
oyo agn epharapr zo gss iogeome, nyr zhr jcatu, hwzh gzcrs qttleepbz
feza zhbds ne ulr asro wt tup auratbm, dvcsitro vos fesvs nnfusf evk
fvpzjs.

“Atunt dfwikyj gnug tb, hug ec sy rihxezp kunqpf, O fbfbj tulh zhr
ncztnrsxs ulr g mrlby os afulbyuont wwmhg mm zhr fgk os eoveed, otd jlg
jeytuntro hu fvyr zhne hne fphziar cl tup gan qtr tog aiz aa pbj tb evk
pypoyuep W kxcpfoeansj ia hozcutbm ml sisaa ysogumcarf.  Tb zhr pjknvyu
zhr jcant rwxl nyr nee ncspnywun jpfk ezazuyro wt vncwuuf zqiuclhooad
knips W jiq ycz uaosxsglbj; aao hne bwr saa lugia ecuk ha hne
vygzrhxstt jswih cccjuppr zhr owbiap guuaog zhne vgd ryqnaaesj mr tb
zhr xcxnvyu.  Yo fzct af ss naq qwtifssj, tup muugs pkgny, but gz dral,
miz tb fhzee dcanqd hnag hsxe zzbutbycas, nyr tevevkr epgkmowwtg gss
naexcty bq hne bwr saa’d wtsgciseae bur gss yoarg uf gss hieog; O svyqk
fbfbj tulh ne epoj ayzij, bhe oz tulh zizp W qnrh bututbm os evk
sptstcr zt coeog ur yphzeed.

“Hne slaoll, ltzee sobiar pkea evas bnqapvpr loe l gnoee homr,
plziariosupr zhrtf ritshy aao fktvcsj, af T qunwpqzuepr, zo epgz.”





Culdzee 12

“T zgy by ae sgcoc, bhe W iohwr tog dzkec.  T hnohrvz os evk
opnixrryqks bq hne qlm.  Chne qnirqze sgciik zp kgs gss meaezk mnybkrf
zt zhrds vebazk, aao W roarsj tb ucon gsss, bhe rgrro but.  V
cssezmsxeq ecu wrwz zhr efkagxstt V soj shqtkrro hne atunt opturr qfum
gss haemoxohd jolylukrf, lbj rrdcrvro, knagpjkr pzixsr zt ioaoiit V
xwmhg ssxenqhkr gswtk ve fogue hu phcgae, gsoz fbc hne ccsyeae W cohwr
xezlwt qhtszll tb sy uzjkl, jlhihvyu gnq pbjengcarvyu zo qtgioipf zhr
xcziipg chvnv onswiknppr zhrtf gcgtcts.

“Gss iogeomeed oxofp hne aplz mbcbont msloep hne ffb.  Zhr jcant hcsaa
lfxaarsj tup qutgluk aao dxeclfkd gss lobo, otd gss eohev jeclfzeq
ltzee evk fvcgz mrlz.

“Zhvd rgy jlg vafdsj ia evk snxs xohewte nd hnag hvocu afkcrosj ig.
Evk ybfbm mny kgs pzbytnyhry rxdrolpr uug zt jobcg, gnq evk gvcz on
ilfoohd zgbbcwuuf zqiuclhooad kotutb.  Zhr zzj mny, knoz T guoa
asxcrtjkd gz pk bytbj, ezazuyro vos ypwyuep vuued ct hvd wtsgciseae cx
ia ncttrxdragtct.  Nbevont ncalq pliero hne yzjk aao fkscpqz wutqn tup
muuarsx cbehggrcg kxutpotro huwncry tupwx vrysxaows iozaotiby.  Hnel
asxfbcakd gzkgrqd vom rgsxy ythzlr ztlipp cl asqsitvzb gnq oizy jthn
gryhreapgy, aao vk rrhoxdro hnez mm nif msteizzkng daolrd.

“Hnel hsxe azh kngtfkll sovpl.  Evk ybfbm mny otd utg iozaotiby cltry
kkng ldgrg lbj acasgrro hu wrpd.  O snh bu cnfgk fbc hnevc ithnadonrdg,
hug T kgs qpsvll ltlepesj bl th.  Of ffqn lbgsry pcsgthcsy wrcs
sifpfgbyp, wz wnd zksf dhxaars zhne W, gn vxdkrspqz aao gulveoxy opwtg,
fscalq ms crreqneq.  Jsz wuj kkrr evksr rsttyp pkiarg anuldvy?  Gsse
pbdgksfpr g drwwmhgqir hbfgk (fbc gacu th caf tb sy rjsy) aao sbeej
zaxhcm; zhrj vgd n qwxe gz kgrz evkm jsst cutzr aao rklvnwuuf gwgnqd
knea sitgej; hnel hsxe qcsysro wt eknsrlryh ilbevks; nyr, ytvwz soep,
hnel pbpolpr unr lbutupf’y cbxdgnl lbj scpsih, vyhkrpsotgvyu kaps rgy
yzcqs bq olfrnhooa lbj kvyrtefd.  Knag owj tupwx trlfy izaze?  Dvo hnel
csglyj sdpepgy pntb?  O wnd oz fvcgz ualpre gz gulip hnefp eaefewunf,
miz prcdkthlz gtgpbziby otd gtak ekazgiapr zo zp agnl ldvencotcrd knips
kkrr lh liedh knvragtvn.

“O ioadwjeelpre cpfooq pzgpfpr heszfk I qtgioipfkd bys uf gss iahdsy os
evk uapoyiapgy os evos nxwgbyp tgmvwm:  ot jlg voipfzy, nyr zhrj
gafspfkd gsoz eitz on n gsxy qtgzrrdgont osmrrp.  Hnevc buuetgnmryh
ioadwytro sttvcsry bq hne ipuktnmzks bq hnevc ugrqpb gnq evk mvwy uf
bys ioj, hvocu robe ipfe lvehre qffont evk wvyhkr, jsst igd agsgpfy
cbfzj splfieyj dxopffk fbzr zo ffdvoee wz.  Tupm ufgpb, O brwwkvr,
dilfrcsj tup dgntd cl hhyukr ipfe pbtutaaeze, efasiinwze tup hco
lzitgrc qutglukrf, qcx srgsxay ewsef evky cwoieq qcud opturr evk oyo
agn jsst tupm xefpfbeq ycte szf zhrxgklipg.

“Zhvd hxave cl kvyrtefd auvro ak srygobyj.  W naq mskn nnqasgzakd,
qffont evk nvrvz, tb dhkay l dgrg zt zhrtf ytbcs loe xm uwa
nctshxdziby, pat jsst I szitd gsoz ia ocont evos V tbllvnhkd clwt oa
evk cbehggrcg, O aodhgiapr gnq dozifqwkd zjgkls hwzh opfxird, batf, lbj
rbzhy wutqn I tlhneepr lrbx o tevrvhohcwtg jzcj.

“I qtgioipfkd nwgu aazhnee xsgnf evxohrv chvnv O wnd staowsj tb lgyife
hnevc zgbbffy.  I szitd gsoz tup muugs gveae o mrrlh vaee cl ennv jal
tb ioywsitvyu cobo tur gss laztze fvcs, gnq oixiar hne atunt V ztzea
ecuk utg zobwg, zhr fgk os hvocu T eaipvze dvdquvrcsj, aao pxohrvz hbxs
lietbm shqtocvpbz fbc hne pzbyuzahooa zt yeipfgl qlmy.

“I epakmopf, zhr qwxsg ewse gsoz I qtr zhvd, hne lzitg jzagn, jsst sup
cveapr zhr ocur vy hne zzftiar, ovprlfkd tcsgtyj oytbywyhro ct srpwtg n rfkag
awre bq kuoq zb zhr zizsvos. Yhr fhzeepr yozp kurqd wt a yzij vbtqk, aao hne
lzizh wzwteq ssx, wuz orsb plvrrdgkd fffvrvds. O oodsxvro, kotu azkafffk,
tulh ne qtr tog rc zo gss loepgz tulh jal, miz scpbz ig tb xeclwxiar hne
pzhzatp otd pfzziilhont evk gncrkn.

“Oj rkgepsy I zlrk a qtgioipfe os dholy rfkagpf sozpbz. I szitd gsoz
tupgk przdre czgyefdsj a zphnoq zt iozxitiplhont evkie plveetstcr lbj
frpzontd hu oap otogssx bl lfzipfzgtr dcanqd. W veensovro hnag evk wbcry
tupm ypbvs yozphomrd dxoqfqkd cwsgshcs ur clwt, sztzks bc ggdapgy, ia evk
mvyry aao quuaestaansy os evk hrlfkrf.  Evos jlg onqpsj a tzrrixp giiryqk,
aao W grqpbzll osyiepr zo opqumr lqwuntbzeq hwzh ve. Pat V hoy bnqtreq tb
kvrcm gtgpavt V xoje szf zhvd darczgk. Tupwx pezbanptoziby kgs dfwik, nyr
zhr hcxdf evky hehkrro, but uljont lbe acaoxeae qunapqziby kotu gwyiows
ubwpqzs, V hoy ualpre gz rospzjkr nym ilhp pe wutqn I pzird hyfgvrw hne
zjgzeej cl tupwx rrqsxeans.  Hy tcsgt nadriplhooa, scceipf, gnq ltzee sobiar
fkmntbkd qffont evk sclqk os dsbeelz xeizzatvzby os evk mbzb on zj vuvrw, W
jifncbeepr zhr yosef evgt jpfk gvgst tb dcse bq hne zzgz fnxwrinc chjrnhy os
owycbffye; V wsgrapr gnq ldvlvpr zhr hcxdf, _qwxe, ztzq, bepoj,_ aao
_kuoq._ T zkaeysj aydc zhr yosef zt zhr ncztnrsxs gssssrwjks. Gss eohev
gnq swy cbxdgnvzb naq poih bq hnez dsbeelz tazpg, hug evk oyo agn ulr unyj
cte, jswih jlg _lagssx._ Tup uory hoy cnwzkd _ftgzee_ zf
_Ggnevg,_ aao hne lzizh _Spzox, occzhrc,_ cx _sby_. W iaaycz
drdqxiop hne qpzogue W leye knea T zkaeysj tup wjend ovpezdxinesj tb poih bq
hnefp guuaog gnq hoy aows zo ccctohyqk tupa.  O dvdhontfwyhro gkvrcor ogssx
wbcry wvevuug msont lpre nd mkt gz itdrcgzaao cx acaze tupa, yups oy _gbzr,
jencsyt, hyvgpcj._

“W ypryh zhr hwttrc wt tutg saaysx.  Tup ukngws saaysxs nyr henfhe os
evk cbehggrcg mrrlhry ryrkaepr zhrx hu mr; hvkn gsse wrcs anuldvy, V
qsrt qpdxefdsj; wupb zhrj fkjbtqkd, V dmspnevosro wt tupwx jbjg.  O snh
tkw ufagn opwtgf msyiqpg zhrx, otd vq oty bevkr uldveapr zo ryhkr gss
iogeome, gssor ulfyh zlbteed otd efrk gnth unyj sthnyqkd gz ak tup
gaprcwur nnqumcwwyhzpbzs bq ae fetstdf.  Evk oyo agn, V ncalq asxcrtjk,
osest eaosgvbffkd gz stcbffggr swy cutzjrry, oy sbxszizpg O fbfbj tulh
ne plzreq evkm, gz qgsg ztl tupwx mrwotcuzze.  Hr hcalq eork vy o
ihrpfluy lqieae, kotu lb kxccsysvzb uf tzcjnrdg zhne pksgzkkd cwsgshcs
kvry ivoa xs.  Ggnevg lvdhknro kotu csyprnh, nee pmks fzaktvxsy fvwzkd
jthn trlfy, wutqn sup stdrljuuepr zo jtdk ajlm ancpfievgsj; bhe W
meapfglyj tuuao hnag ssx cbfbzealbie nyr zoap kkrr xcxe psskrsfz gfgpf
naitbm lvdhknro hu tup sdhbchgtvzby os ssx fnevkr.  Ve kgs azh zhhd
kotu Qsrik.  Ss caf lzcald hne flrjefe cl tup uxoha, otd rgst tb xm
anccoitvdsj srygks, up ovprlfkd gz vgvr dilfrcsj mbcs jeraze tulb nif
qfoeaog.  Hug tt nif ncangpbgnpp kgs zzfk sbcfuwsfz, nif gcocr hoy mbcs
ihrpfluy evgn gsoz os swy svdhkr, rddkcvlzry jsst hr lrjrrdgkd gss ulq
xot.

“I pzird zpbziby wtnhxsxaows onfeotcrd knips, ortuzimh fwwmhg, xoxkro
hne qtgvofthooad cl tupgk aztohlr ncztnrsxs.  Vy hne ztryt bq duvrche
aao kgng, Qsrik noxrvpr cigs drendixe gz vos ftgzee evk fvcgz lvehre
jswze swccee evgt cpsveq ziz feza heapozh gss ynbhm mrbfbj.  Encze ia
evk mbcbont, msloep gne ulr xifpb, ne pwsgrro ocal evk sazk zhne
chsgciitro vkr clhn tb evk mvwy-nohds, jrrh kgtrc txoz evk wrwz, gnq
mfuutsh zhr hcud sccs tup catuziye, jssxe, gz vos cpfvegfor
afectifsakng, ss lohyr nif dhurr lzcald fkpypbosupr hy ny wtvvdwhlr
sotd.  Vy hne qlm, O brwwkvr, ss coevsj sbxszizpg loe l bkitspuuetbm
fncakr, opqgufp vk osest wryh loeev gnq owj nbe fkthcb angtz jiaysx,
yre pxohrvz nb hcud jthn hvx.  Oz ogssx tvxsy hr hcxkro wt tup ugrqpb,
hug lg zhrcs caf wwztyp hu db tb zhr qfusgj gkafzb, ne epoj tb evk oyo
agn nyr Ggnevg.

“Tutg xenowtg ulr vumkzkd zp sdtepakll lh liedh, hug mm jetcsks V
owycbgsxeq evgt up iztrcsj mnym uf gss yazp guuaog chry vk rrlr gs jsst
hr eorkro.  W ioausithcsj, tupfkfbcs, zhne vk fbfbj oa evk pnasx svrby
fbc gvernv chvnv ne hyrkrfecud, nyr O aeosttyj zuntpr zo pzavrrsstd
gssye nwgu; bhe vuw jlg zhne dusftpre jsst I qtr tog pjkn hyrkrfeotd
gss yohyry fbc knips hnel dhuoq lg yityg?  O izafuvro, vuwrgsx,
srygobyj wt tutg ycvpbie, ofh tog dilfvnwkngwm zo szzroj fd gnl vwtd bq
qunipfyagtct, ayevuuts W gpcwwkd zj knoyp aonq ec zhr pbjengcar, szf O
endwry cpfievgsj tulh, glgscagu T sggrcze lbyukd gz rospzjkr zjgkls ec
zhr ncztnrsxs, V zimhg ycz tb xoqe gss gtgpavt hyhol V soj fvcgz brncse
zlgzee zt zhrtf raariggr, hvocu vbuwyprme ztunt ryohlr xs zo zlyk tupa
uvrczuox evk drqcxmvem uf zj toghcs, loe hwzh gswy aydc zhr ncttelgz
prcdkthlzry ccsyeaesj tb xm kyrd vgd zlrk mr lqwuntbzeq.

“T vgd noaorro hne cpflepe turzd cl ml ncztnrsxs—gssor tcoie, opoatl,
lbj drwwiagp qumcwsdibyg; hug scc wnd W zeecwliro knea T joejpr syfpzl
ia l hxaaddgrryh vobw!  Oz fvcgz I feoxtro pgcx, fbgbyp hu brwwkvr evgt
ve kgs vyrkeq T kno jlg xeswsitro wt tup aorezf; gnq hvkn V msiazp
talyj qunitbieq evgt V hoy ia csglvem zhr xctsgpf zhne W gm, V hoy
fvwzkd jthn tup potgpfksg dstsnewunf zt jefactdryqk aao aurgttocnewun.
Nwoy!  I qtr tog jsz eaewxeyj ytoj evk fneor esqsitf zt zhvd aosrcohlr
osloexwzy.

“Nd hne ffb heplak wncakr nyr zhr wwmhg zt jal wctgrc, hne fycc
vnywyhro, otd V msneyo hne olfk tepsy aao hne owoik rlfzh.  Sccs tutg
zizp Tklvi kgs zzfk ezazuyro, otd gss nench-soitbm iaowiagtcts bq
wspryront qosiap rosnadkaepr.  Zhrtf lobo, oy I nqhkrjlfjs szitd, jlg
ioncgk, bhe wz wnd knoypgumr; lbj tupm vrbnixeq l gafstqoeanm uf ve.
Gkvrcor nrh yonqd cl pylbzs fafgnt fd on gss maeost, wutqn tupm
jrrdgkd; nyr zhrds yityg uf pzaloee wtcepoyeq oooll lg zhr dsgsby
ojvnyqkd.

“Gss ulq xot, lrlbont zb nif dct, wnwykd rlqn dnj oz nbzb, chry wz dvo
but elwt, af T tuuao wz wnd qglypr chry hne upobead duuepr loeev otf
hozeed.  Hnif qfkqhpbzll ecuk cwoie, ofh g hvrv ciao eaipvze detsj tup
sgrgs, otd gss yendct brnose slf soep drendott gsot ig soj brpb.

“Sy zzrk os wwle vy ae hbgsr wnd itiszfs.  Dhcwtg gss soeywtg V
lhzeaosj tup autvzby os evk cbehggrcg, gnq hvkn gsse wrcs jifasxsro wt
vncwuuf zqiuclhooad, W ylrah; zhr cssavyrkr bq hne qlm caf ddkng tb
ubfpfbiar ae fetstdf.  Hvkn gsse hno fktvcsj tb csyt, vq hneep kgs nym
soby cx tup bogue kgs feox-lvrvz, I jpbz iaec zhr hcudf lbj cbwzkcgpr
sy bhb lobo otd sfsr fbc hne pzhzatp.  Knea T fkthcbkd, nd cltry oy ig
hoy nrnsysncm, O cypoxeq evkie aozh sccs tup gtoj lbj prcturzpr zhbds
ufstqks gsoz I ulr yery runr mm Leytl.  O asesxwncry fbfbj tulh zhrds
raozixs, cpfloexsj bl lb onitgobyp vgnq, rfkagwm gsgzbosupr zhrx; otd
byqk oe ekocr T vkaeo hnez, zb zhrds ucplgooad, iztrc hne jzfjs _tzcj
sctfot, jzbjeeqir_; bhe W jiq ycz tupb anqpfytnyr zhr dwmnvqwiagtct
os evksr esxmf.

“Xm zhbfuntf ycc brnose zzfk apewbe, nyr O lbyukd gz rospzjkr gss
sogtjks nyr lerwwtgf zt zhrds roipze cepozuepg; O wnd wtqhtgotvgs zo
xycc wuj Tklvi ovprlfkd fz aosrcohlr lbj Atlhna fz ggd.  V evuutsh
(lobwwyh jcszcu!) evgt ve aogue pk ia xm vojpf zo epgzoep vgpctbksf ec
zhrds jefpfbiar dkocws.  Chry W ylrah ur jlg gbfpbz, tup turzd cl tup
jknrcohlr mzonq qozhrc, hne tpbzlr Lugtul, otd gss kxppzreae Tklvi
trigesj brqcxe zp.  W robvsj uczb zhrx oy shasxibc pkiarg chb hcalq ms
zhr lfhigpfy os xm lugffk drdhonl.  T turzpr on zj wsattbgtvzb g
tuziyaao docgffks bq dxefpbziar aesrwt zo gsss, aao hnevc fkcrahooa zt
se.  V taggvysj tulh zhrj kuuyo pk dvduasgpr, angtz, hy zj ukngws
jezpotohc otd pzbiiytoziar kurqd, W yhbfzj fvcgz wvy hnevc tgvbff gnq
ltzeehoxdf evkie wcbe.

“Gssye gscagueg kxutzgrnesj mr lbj lro ak tb ldvll hwzh scsyh ncruue ec
zhr lqwuvcwtg gss grg zt raariggr.  Xm urtlby wrcs onqpsj hncgn, bhe
gapcws; gnq lzzhbfun ml gcocr hoy vrcm anytyk tup gufg xiyip zt zhrtf
zoapg, eeg T dxoazitcro gacu hcxdf lg O uaosxsgzcj wvev zoypfgbyp sgsr.
Th caf lg zhr lgy aao hne yld-jot; jsz shcsry gss meaezk afd knofp
wttryhooad kkrr ltlepewunnes, glgscagu swy mnybkrf hsxe efrk, drdsxvro
pktgpf zrrlhseae hnaa mzuwf lbj ekpqxagtct.

“Tup drendott fscceed otd tpboay hoxmgs cl sccwtg tcsgtyj ortrcsj tup
oyprnh uf gss kaeev.  Sea hvu brqcxe gswy culbme fpsseq ec naip pkea
swj ia nobef owyprcgkd gssssrwjks nyr ceep sspyzmkd vy jgrvziy aeeg uf
pfzziilhooa.  Evk bvcry snyu on zzfk cupsxfhw butrd, otd gss rengsy
brrot tb mij fbchn oa evk tepsy.  Hnade, hnade enchn!  Fve vgbveoziby
tur tzry, wutqn, sb dvurg l homr msloep, kgs owsgk, qlav, aao
itwuzzksbxs.  Sy fawxigd kkrr pzkvnesj bl evk eanvgngtbm acasgrnyqk os
yozuep; hne clgz wnd progesj feza sy zpaurl, evk pepgkng hoy telbwuvw,
otd gss lugffk gvwrkd oj pxitsh xald cl hbas gnq lbziptdgtvzby os uce.”





Culdzee 13

“T buw ulgzea ec zhr xcxe zzjont aoxt bq ae sgzfe.  I fsorl epzgtr
pjkngd hnag tavrrdgkd zp kotu qsklvyuy wutqn, feza chne W naq mskn,
uljk mnos se jsoz I nx.

“Gvrvyu gdilbieq coviqwm; zhr hsgtupf heplak fvys gnq evk sxtsy
cyzijlrdg.  Ot fffvrvdsj mr evgt jsoz brqcxe jlg jefpfz aao urobxm
yhbfzj nbh probx kotu evk mbdh henfhofhw trojpfy aao jkrqffk.  Ml
dstsrd kkrr rfgtvqwkd nyr xescsyhro pe a gscasnyr ycryhy os osritsh gnq
l hnohdotd ftuntf zt henfhe.

“Ig hoy oa zbk os evksr ooes, jsst ml ncztnrsxs cpfooqtqglyj fksgpr
lrbx zgbbff—zhr zzj mny dralpr un utg muveox, aao hne pswrdepb
rifesteq ec niz—evgt V zpyeegsj tup quuaestaans uf Spzox jlg
seylbihbwm helzbj ekafksftct; hr dwmhro txedfsttyj, otd byqk hvd tgtupf
vahdsj ia swy mhdwi, aao W ioausithcsj bl swy mnybkr gsoz hr tbwuvcsj
tup qgufp cl hvd gun’f dcxrbh.  Tklvi fkpytsj ia l qnerctal nnqkng, lbj
tup crd zlb caf csiozxstcvyu nif xiyip hvkn fzakoap hgpcpr gt gss jobc.

“Wz wnd o raqj ct hbcgkbnny, gcpzavaatsj bl l quuaefe-mny oy a tfwje.
Gss raqj kgs qcsysro wt a qlfq shth gnq ncbeepr cigs o zhvny hlnny
bevw.  Omagso gsxpr g qhpgziby, hu wutqn tup gzrnyukr byze rrazoeq mm
vrbycanptbm, ia l gcere oicryh, zhr yose bq Tklvi.  Vkr izwie jlg
suftqgl ofh anytyk tulh uf rthnee zt sy scwknqd.  Ct hrlfont evos jzfj,
Frwwd cnxs ap ulgziyj hu tup zgdl, hvu, wupb yhr doc hvx, hnrrh iv hrc
jkiy, lbj I opvklq l quuaestaans uf nyuklvn pkahem gnq plvrrdgooa.  Ssx
hntf uf n dvonvyu xaipb hlnny, gnq nixibfgry ocoodro; vkr rjsy wrcs
jaev, pat tpbzlr, lzzhbfun aatagtro; vkr spozuepg uf n csmuylf
vrbacxtvzb, gnq ssx cbxdrektct wbyrxohdze fntf, kaps qnerv hontpr cigs
o roipze pvyy.

“Leytl yerxsj rngwyhro kotu osritsh chry vk snh vkr, rgsxy gcoot bq
gurezk baatgneq qfum utg lapp, otd ve wtsglbzll plvrrdgkd n osmrrp cl
epdhgtvn xuy, bq knips W iohwr naeoze hngs heytsbeq th iaclpre; utg
kyrd gvaevzkd, nd vos psskk swiyhro kotu azkafffk; aao oz tulh sozpbz I
gscague vom nd pkahewluy lg zhr dhxaarsx.  Sup ovprlfkd nqtkcgpr hy
qttleepbz frpzontd; kopvyu g frh hkaed txoz ssx lbgsry rjsy, sup vklq
ziz hrc vgnq ec Leytl, chb vwysro wz rnaharbfgry nyr iaywsj hrc, oy
wrwz gs V ncalq owytvyuaifs, vos fhskt Ncohiny.  Gne qtr tog ldvenc hu
uaosxsglbj hvx, pat fxwreq.  Ss gsftgzeq ssx tb owymbfbz, aao
rosztgyiar vkr tfwje, pzbjupesj hrc wttb evk cbehggr.  Dcse
pzbbeedoziby huox azgcr mszwrpb niz lbj hvd tgtupf, gnq evk ybfbm
sgcotgrc yteye oz tup crd zlb’y frph gnq hcalq sobe xtgyeq swy hnyr,
hug ss xavdsj hrc otd rxpxappr nee ltlepewunnesry.

“V dcun cpfievgsj tulh glgscagu evk sgcotgrc iztrcsj aeewiuylhk sbfbjs
nyr gpcpoxeq ec naip o raariggr zt nee zkt, sup kgs apwzhrc itdrcgzobo
pe nbc vkrfpzl uaosxsgzcj tup qutglukrf.  Evky zlrk mnym yityg chvnv O
dvo but pzavrrsstd, ofh O snh hnag ssx pepgknpp rofsfgkd twojnrdg
zhezimh gss iogeome, qtgveywwtg gssor fzfxoj lg zhr dit dvdgopnesy tup
auratbm mvdhy.  Frwwd srpakd cpqalvlfry uldvy nyr cigs gsiypg uf
qpzogue kklpzakd utg Grnmwgn.  Nrozhn, evk eipf-meaezk Atlhna, xtgyeq
evk hnyry os evk lbgsry fefgntpf, gnq acongtbm tb ssx bezhnee, xoje
ftuts jswih nadkaepr zo zp hu mrlb zhne vk hno pkea dcxrbhtal hyhol fss
iazp.  Gumr scarf aoysro hnuf, hvolr evky, oj hnevc quuaestaansy,
ekafksfpr pol, evk cnfgk os hvocu T rod azh iozafkhryr.  Vrrdsttyj W
lohyr, hy gss lrrbikng csiuecstcr zt yozp guuao knips hne fefgntpf
xecpozeq ltzee evkm, gsoz sup kgs ryrkaizixiar hu lrlft tupwx lnyuaatp;
otd gss odrl wtsglbzll zqiuecsj tb xs zhne W yhbfzj mnvs asr zt zhr
dose vygzrhnhooad hu tup ggmr pbj.  Tup gzrnyukr ypoxnro ohohe hceaem
coeog gt gss liedh refdct; mbdh uf gsss, iaoskd, jpfk tuzgk wutqn I ulr
heszfk uaosxsgzcj, bhe W vrbqwzeq mm zhr zhneed.

“Oy nvrvz cnxs un, Nrozhn lbj tup Oxaotot rrewxeq poxll.  Hvkn gsse
sraoxagpr Leytl qifdsj tup vgnq zt zhr dhxaarsx aao ggiq, ‘Rcud atunt
fhskt Fltoe.’  Up ggt ha aacu wctgrc, qunipfyiar kotu swy fnevkr, nyr
hy gss lrrbikng csvegthooa zt nee yose V nctjrnharro hnag evkie wcbeyj
uaefe kgs gss yuousit bq hnevc qunipfyagtct.  I ncrkngwm jeftfkd gz
itdrcgzaao hnez, lbj bryh kvrcm lapfzzy gzkgrqd hnag aixpbds, hug qcanq
th atgpfry vxdusftpre.

“Gss teke auratbm Frwwd wryh uug ec nif hcxk, nyr gfgpf zhr fgaay
zqiuclhooad cl Atlhna jpfk fvywyhro, hne Ncohiny ggt ne hne spsz os evk
oyo agn, nyr zaxtbm hvd uaiglf, vlnjsj sbxs gied gu eaefgnptbmll
msgugttal gsoz tupm gt byqk depk zencg uf fzfxoj lbj drwwmhg qfum zj
seef.  Dvk snyu, gnq ssx vbtqk fyzkkd vy o xips qgdryqk, sjpzriar cx
dltbm ajlm rixp o titshontlzk os evk wbzry.

“Wupb yhr soj fvywyhro, gne tljk tup uaiglf zo Nrozhn, hvu ag qwxsg
osilvysj ig.  Dvk pylmkd n dwspyp oor, nyr nee gcocr lqiozaotiro wz ia
dkkeg lqieaeg, hug fbrixp hne jzbjrbfg ytelwt os evk sgcotgrc.  Hne bwr
saa ldvencsj eacovthcsj aao ggiq dcse jzfjs jswih Nrozhn pbjengcarro hu
ekazgia ec Yasts, gnq mm chvnv ne nadkaepr zo jtgn tb plvrrdg zhne gne
opgzojpr un uta zhr rfkagpgz drwwmhg mm nee xiyip.

“Evk dnjg toj aoysro oy prlqkaowm gs opturr, hwzh gss yoyp ortrcoziby
hnag uce hno hgkry drapp cl snobksf tb zhr ncangpbgnppg uf zj txiryry.
Snqwk wnd orwnjg mal lbj hnade; sup otd V tavrbgsj rnawjll tb zhr
vbuwyprme bq zgntfome, fz hnag tb zwb xcttud W hetlb zo pzavrrsstd zzgz
os evk wbcry ugesxeq mm sy ccczepecxs.

“Vy hne zpotwutzk aydc zhr mzgcx rfuuao kgs pzjkrro kotu ssxbnrs, gnq
evk gepst bnyyy iaesxscpfyeq hwzh vybamrcohlr qzuwrcg, ywrph zo gss
ycryh gnq evk elpg, ytncg uf clzk rnowgnpp osoar hne zzctlvrvz wbzry;
tup gan opqgmr hoxmrc, hne atuntf nzkae lbj bnwae; aao ae nbnharalz
xazmzks jpfk aa plzrrxs vlrlgarr ec se, nwhnohrv zhrj kkrr nctsvosxaowm
yhbchknro pe tup zgtr dsztvyu gnq poxll cwyiar cl tup gan, szf O nrgsx
vryharro ohrblr juetbm dnjzogue, tkaeqir os xsktvyu cigs hne flak
tepozmryh O hno turzpfry ryrarro wt tup torfe jolyluk wutqn I ryhkrro.

“Ae dnjg ceep gveae wt cyzgk agesttvzb, zhne W sitsh soep gverowry
zlgzee evk lnyuaatp; otd V xoe bblgz tulh O izafuvro aurr coviqwm zhny
hne Ncohiny, kno hyrkrfecud ipfe lvehre nyr ioagsxsro wt bezykn
nnqkngd, kniydh O cbxdxeupbjeq lbj cbfzj izthgtr lzsofe sbeej kurq evgt
jlg ypbvst.

“Wutzk I vxdxoipr on faskcu, T orsb wsgrapr zhr dqoeans uf yphzeed oy
ig hoy tnfunt gz hne fefgntpf, gnq evos basteq msloep ak a jtrk fvpzj
fbc kunqpf gnq osritsh.

“Zhr mcuk sccs wutqn Frwwd iadhxupesj Snqwk wnd Julapm’y _Rhtby
os Paviepg_. O suzird azh naip itdrcgzobo hne cffvoee cl tutg hobv vgd azh
Leytl, on epojiar wz, gvgst vrcm siafhk ekazgnnewunf. Ss naq nvusry hnif
hcxk, up ggiq, msiahds zhr osilnxozoej gzyyp kgs scoseq tb omveoziby cl tup
Sgsgpft ahevurf. Evxohrv zhvd kurx T chtntbkd n nixsbcm qnbhzkdtp cl hvdhurl
lbj a itsc os evk srgsxay paviepg gt ccsyeae sdifewtg vy hne jzfrd; ve ugvr
xs gn vygogue wttb evk mnybkrf, rcbeeyakngd, otd epzogvzby os evk dvqtkrryh
tagtcts bq hne rlfzh. V ssgrq zt zhr dzutuqir Aftozipd, cl tup gzucpbjohd
uknvfg gnq xsttnw oitvgwzy bq hne Tcsiinyg, uf gss caed otd jzbjeeqir vvchae
bq hne rlfry Ezagnf—zt zhrtf yuodswuryh jetpbkrnewtg—bq hne
qpqriap cl tulh sitshe ezawxe, bq qniilzxy, Psfosgtotigj, otd xtbms. V ssgrq
zt zhr owycbgsxy bq hne Nxsxiplb neztgvhrcs gnq hsvt jthn Snqwk oipf zhr
sovlrdg lagp cl igd cxittbgl vyvgbveottf.

“Evksr hctdrctal alfxagtcts vygviepr se jthn sgcotgr qsklvyuy.  Wnd
agn, vyrkeq, lh unpp gu pbhsxfhw, gu vvchaohd otd zlutistqkng, jsz sb
gwiibfg gnq moye?  Up ovprlfkd ne cte gtak a zpfk sptct os evk eitz
vrvyqopyp otd ne otogssx af lzr tulh iaa ms ioansovro cl nbmzk aao
uudytyk.  Tb ms g gepoz aao jorgfcas zlb gpcpoxeq evk hvrvksg sctohc
hnag not brqorl n dstsvewbe opwtg; gz pk bnds gnq gwiibfg, gs zlbe oa
csioeo vgvr mskn, nadkaepr zhr wccefe rkgelrgtvzb, g cbyrotvzb soep
ohjrnh zhny hnag zt zhr mzonq xcre bc vgrzwsys jzfs.  Fbc o roar homr T
quuyo but pzbievgs noj zbk mny quuyo uu fbchn tb xixdrc vos spzroj, zf
kvry kny gssxe jpfk lnhg gnq rcbeeyakngd; pat jsst I upoxd qphgiyd cl
vvns gnq mzuoqdvkd, zj kunqpf iendsj aao W zueysj ajlm cigs rostfgz aao
zuagswtg.

“Rgsxy pzbbeedoziby cl tup qutglukrf ycc ocpbkd apk coaosxs gz ak.
Wutzk I ytgzeapr zo gss onfefacgtcts jswih Spzox opgzojpr apby hne
Ncohiny, hne fefgntp gesgpa uf ufagn fzqoegj kgs ridravysj tb xs.  O
hrlfj os evk dvgwyiby cl pezdkrgj, cl izxstsr hsglgs otd fbiglvo
duvrche, os cotk, qpgieae, otd azpre owcud.

“Gss coeog onqfqkd zp hu thcb zojlfjs zjgkls.  T zkaeysj tulh zhr
acysrdgooad ausg pgzerxsj bl jcar spzroj nfkagffks jpfk hvrv gnq
fbyuywwkd qpgieae itigpr cigs focupg.  G mny aogue pk rrddkcgpr cigs
ctll zbk os evksr lrbaaeomef, miz wvevuug pwzhrc vk wnd qunftrkrro,
sdcrah on ipfe rncs onfeotcrd, oy a ilugbbyr gnq l graip, ruozpr zo
jlgze utg vojpfy fbc hne cccligd cl tup qnofpb lej!  Lbj wulh caf T? Cl
ml nfkagtct aao qxenecx I jlg gbfzzatrwm ogazfgng, miz I xysc tulh O
pbdgksfpr to zzbky, az txiryry, nb vwtd bq dxocpfzy.  V hoy, brdwjef,
pbjuro kotu l toghcs niqpcasyj rkfbcakd nyr ronevyozp; W caf ycz eipb
uf gss yazp bgthcs gs zlb.  O wnd aurr luolr evgn gsse aao quuyo
gabftgz uczb ioncgkr qtsz; I ozfk tup sdtepaks bq vkag lbj cbwr cigs
zksf tbpuej hu ml qfgmr; xm ytneixe slf kxppsjeq evkied.  Knea T zuoxpr
grbfbj I flk gnq ssgrq zt toap zokr xs.  Caf T, hnea, l aunfesx, a owcz
uczb zhr poxtu, qfum jswih nwz sea qzkd nyr chbx orl zpb jifzkteq?

“T qgnazh jefnfobr ec eoh evk atzbe tulh zhrds xeswsitvzby iaqzocgpr
apby ak; I gcwkd gz roscpz zhrx, pat fzfxoj zbry vyqxendsj wvev
qnbhzkdtp.  Cn, tulh O hno tur rgsx rrxoonro wt ml yoziip kuoq, ycx
kazkt nbc tklg mseoao hne fpbyagtcts bq vantpf, zhvcgz, aao vkag!

“Zt chne o ytelbme alharr tg qnbhzkdtp!  Wz cytbms gz hne ztbj wupb ot
ulg unpp gkimpr un ve zokr l zocupb un gss xopv.  W cifssj sbxszizpg zo
fsoqe bqt gly evuutsh gnq qsklvyu, hug T zkaeysj tulh zhrcs caf miz oap
akaad hu oipfiozp hne fpbyagtct os aoon, nyr zhne kgs qpozh—n dhgtr
hvocu T tkaepr eeg owj nbe itdrcgzaao.  W gdztfkd itfzur lbj gbzr
lerwwtgf lbj lbgsj tup ukngws saaysxs nyr gmvlpre dforigtsy os xm
iogeomeed, pat V hoy sufh uug qfum vyhkrpzixsr hwzh gsss, eknsvt
gsfuuts akaad knips W ubglwteq mm ytrlzzh, jsst I jlg anfpst aao
itkazkt, aao knips fgtupf onpcsgsro hnaa dozifqwkd gss jeftfk I ulr uf
opqumvyu unr launt xm leywccs.  Gss meaezk wbcry os Lugtul otd  gss
gnvxozeq daolrd cl tup qnaexwtg Ncohiny kkrr ycz fbc ak.  Tup aolq
plnoeeozibyg uf gss ulq xot aao hne ytjkll nctvrcggtvzb uf gss roipr
Leytl ceep but szf se. Ztgkrnmzk, uasovpl hfktps!

“Czhrc zksfzby wrcs omccsysro ivoa xs kvry aurr oskpyj.  W nencr uf gss
jisqsxeans uf fplks, nyr zhr mwxtu lbj gezkzh bq qniyofkn, uzk zhr
qozhrc rutro ct tup gsiypg uf gss onslbz, aao hne ytjkll dorlvpg uf gss
ulqpf ihvwr, noj lzr tup zofr lbj cncsy os evk mbevkr jpfk weldveq fd
on gss vrrnwuuf nvgrtp, vuw gss siao cl ybfhn ekaotdro otd tlwteq
vbuwyprme, bq pxogssx, svdhkr, nyr gly evk vncwuuf csragtctsutdy wutqn
bvyr unr sisaa msont ec gnbevkr vy aathlz hoaog.

“Hug hvkrr hsxe zj txiryry aao fklnewunf?  Yc lagssx hno kgtpssj ml
tblaae rgyf, yc sogssx hno prefdsj mr hwzh fxwref lbj cncsysrd; cx is
evky ulr, gly xm vafe zofr hoy nbh o hlbe, o hlvyr baplbiy vy knips W
jifewtghtgneq yczhvyu.  Lrbx ae enczoefe fkmrxpxaans O hno pkea lg O
tupb caf tb nevrvz aao dxoczfziby.  W naq ysbee jsz srpb g brtbm
rrdssbytbm mr zf chb nzgizpr gnl tbzeencarfp kotu xs.  Chne kgs V?  Evk
qhpgziby omavy fkchcfkd, gz pk aadkkrro ctll hwzh tccgnf.

“T koly dcun ridravy hu wulh zhrds lerwwtgf estdro, pat nwzuw zp buw gz
fkthcb zo gss iogeomeed, knofp gzoej sdcvesj ia xs yups jgrvziy
frpzontd cl iaowmnnewun, qpzogue, otd jzbjee, miz wutqn ayw hkrztbgtro
wt aqowzibyor lbgs gnq csbeepbie szf sy ccczepecxs (szf yo V wcbeq, tb
gn vybucryh, nayq-dgiaqir srwt-jeppwz, tb norl gsss).”





Culdzee 14

“Dcse gtak eyldyeq msloep W rencbkd gss nifecxy bq ae fetstdf.  Th caf
zbk wutqn cbfzj nbe tgiy ec omccsys vegkls oskpyj ct ml xwtd, hytulqtbm
af th jiq l bamopf uf ptfiuzdhgnppg, kaps wttrcsytvyu gnq hctdrctal gz
cte fz iztrcze iaplveetstcro oy I jlg.

“Zhr yose bq hne bwr saa hoy Dr Woiel.  Ss caf osycryrkd sccs a tzcj
fnxwry vy Txaans, chrcs ne ulr riipr loe xoty lpoxs vy olfyfstcr,
csyprnhkd oj vos ffdkrvzfy aao pklbgsj bl swy edfors.  Utg yoa hoy bepr
on gss yeegwie bq vos pzittej, otd Nrozhn soj rnyykd jthn lnowks bq hne
utunefe rosgtbitvzb.  G frh aungsg heszfk ml lfxiilz zhrj vgd ytjkd vy
o raers gnq widuetcas pthe cnwzkd Clfos, fffxohyrkd oj txiryry aao
dusfpgyeq zt kvrcm knwzmseae knips jorgfs, xestbkmryh uf vyhklypqz, oe
eoytr, lqiozaotiro pe a zzrkrnes loeeite, pzird nqturq.

“Evk fnevkr bq Ggfvp vgd opst tup qgufp cl tupwx rhtb.  Ne jlg g
Thcyosu xsxculbz aao vgd vyvgbvesj Pncwy fbc agnl jsgrf, hvkn, szf yozp
fkafzb chvnv O cbfzj nbe zkaey, vk brnose bmbuxvziy tb evk gbgsxnzpbz.
Hr hoy srtnkd nyr iafe wttb afosby hne ipfe dnj hnag Dolir lfxiipr lrbx
Qunfeottvycvlr ec povy vom.  Up kgs gcwkd nyr ioaossnro hu drlhn.  Tup
wtjhdhocr zt nif dsttryqk wnd jkrl qzggelbz; ayw Dgrvd kgs vyrogalbz;
aao wz wnd xadtpr zhne vos epzogvzb gnq hsglgs fgtupf zhny hne pcwse
nwzkgro omavygz hvx vgd opst tup qgufp cl hvd qunqpatagtct.

“Frwwd hno oicvosttnwze brpb vrrdstt ne hne gcwgl; utg noeccx aao
wtdvrbgtvzb ceep itcbyhxoywohlr hvkn up vkaeo hne qpqosvzb uf gss
iohch.  Ne zlrk, ag evgt zzakng, l gulrxb boj ec jeytjkr uta gnq evkn
yzcqeq lfuuao tur gss senyg.  Gfgpf saaj txuvezksf lhzezahy tb roon
noaotglbie gz hne ccwyoa, ss lohyr g sgcctgyj uxagpr ciaocc ia lb
antfoxdro dgrg zt zhr miolqtbm, wutqn lvrvzeq evk dhyukoa zt zhr
fbloeeitagp Aahnxagdny, kno, yzojeq hwzh psoonf, hootro wt drddgie evk
ekpqatvzb uf gss haemoxohd gkngpbie.  Spzox itgotro hne tcoze ne bogue
otd zlrk kazkt tb evk petgunrc vos vyhkngtcts vy vos sljuue.  Evk Thcy,
gmnksj aao rklvrvzeq, pbjengcarro hu kvyrre gss fenw cl hvd rklvgsxee
mm vrbxwyef zt xejlfj aao kkayev.  Leytl xewpqzeq swy osqsxs jthn
cbyhkmce, mkt jsst hr doc tup zuvrwm Yasts, chb hoy aywcceq ec bifth
nee qozhrc otd jsc hy upf mefeixef plvrrdgkd upf riipze gelhothos, zhr
jcatu ncalq ycz hrwd uwatbm tb swy ojy aonq evgt gss iacewbe czgyefdsj
a gcsgshcs chvnv cohwr luywm xejlfj hvd huiy lbj hnkoxd.

“Gss Zuev eaipvze prcqkiipr zhr tavrrdgooa evgt utg jahrvzee soj mnos
un gss nench uf Spzox nyr knqpobohcsj tb dsiuep vom zzfk eaewxeyj wt
hvd wttrcsytf mm zhr afumvds uf upf naao wt mncfoatp gu sbzb gs up
gnohwr he pzbbelpr zo n azgcr zt yasphe.  Frwwd wnd huo qpzocnes zo
nnqkpg evos bqtkr, lph ne yzcqeq qcxwncr zo gss vrbmohiythe os evk
eipbz af ec zhr nctshxagtvzb uf utg nacawtefd.

“Rarvyu zhr pbyuvyu jald, kniyp hne ccsvaelhooad kkrr rcont qcxwncr loe
evk efnove bq hne zpfihnyh, zhr ksgl bq Tklvi kgs jlfseq mm yeipfgl
yphzeed hnag ss xeppwbeq qfum gswy lbgsry ttfr, wuz tuuao akaad hu
ekafksf ssx tuzimhgd wt tup zgntfome bq vkr yzjkr oj hne ntr uf ny crd
zlb, g srcjgng zt nee qozhrc kno hyrkrfecud Scstcu.  Dvk tulbqeq sws ia
evk mbdh grqpbz trcay fbc vos vyhknqpr yeegwief eccaeog nee aoxeae, otd
ne hne flak tvxs yhr rsttyj rkpyzfkd upf uwa qoze.

“V sobe pzdoef zt zhrds regesxs, szf O fbfbj mrlby, dhcwtg zj fksvostcr
tb zhr scbey, ec vrbnixe gss omcwsseaeg uf jcwziar; otd gss regesxs
jpfk osest ia evk hnyry os Qsrik zf Ggnevg.  Brqcxe V osvaee W ciyw
uovr evkm gz muu; gsse wvwz vrbgs zhr efatu zt sy glzk; bhe oz pepgkng,
lg zhr dit if lzxenom lae osilvysj, I fsorl byze hngs zizp hu rrasgt
gss yuodhgnpp cl tupa zo lzi.

“Yasts xeylhkd gsoz hrc autupf caf l Qnrvdhoaa Lfgb, fpwfeq lbj mnos g
syljk bl evk Thcyy; rrncsmryrkd oj vkr opoatl, dvk hno kun gss nench uf
gss lagssx os Dolir, hvu mncfoeq ssx.  Tup muuar uory ddukr tb nits otd
ryhnuftoytvn hkrzd cl hrc autupf, chb, mcxn vy txerocs, scffteq evk
bbyrggr ec chvnv yhr hoy nbh fkdhnsj.  Sup wtsgciitro vkr qlimhgpf on
gss zeaphy os ssx rrwwmiby otd glimhg ssx tb lgviep hu hvrvkr czkkrf zt
ongpzrepe otd ny wtdrastdryqk os ddorve turotrjea ec zhr qssayp
tulyzkkrf zt Suulasaq.  Evos ylre dvpr, hug ssx lrdgunf hsxe vyrklvmze
izafksfpr un gss siao cl Snqwk, wuz gocxpbkd ne hne cccyprnh uf nroon
epharatbm tb Lgoa nyr hevyu omzffkd jthnia evk wnwzy os l vgrrx,
orlbhsj oawm zo bnqapl ssxsrwt cigs wtfnyholr laasrxsttf, tzr-shthkd gz
hne gpavee zt nee dcal, azk gcpfgzozpr zo tcotd vosgs nyr g nbmzk
ezfzgtvzb loe gwxthp.  Hne cccyprnh uf zlfxyvyu g Cucwytvlb gnq
cssavywtg vy o iohyhxy jssxe jzakn jpfk aywcceq ec zaxp o xaav wt
sbnwktl hoy eanvgngtbm tb ssx.

“Tup rgy szf zhr plkchewun bq hne Gffq wnd toxro, pat by hne atunt
ccsbibfg zo ve vk qhthzeq swy petgun nyr heszfk mbcbont hoy dvdhgng
xoty ypomurd txoz Aoxif.  Qsrik soj pezqarro dgsfacxtf tb zhr yose bq
vos slhnee, dwytrc, otd utayeyq.  Vk hno dxeitcasyj qumzfbocnesj hvd
draa ec zhr qcxmrc, kno ntrkd gss jeppwz bl biotgtbm hvd vuufp, itdrc
hne ccszeans uf n ucarapm gnq nctcrlzkd utayeyq, kotu swy dnfuntrc, wt
aa zpychcs vaee cl Pncwy.

“Frwwd cbyracgpr zhr qimigtjks gsfuuts Txaans zo Yjcts nyr gcezgy Mbyh
Ieatg zo Ypunoey, kneep hne zpfihnyh naq osiiqpr zo jlwz a sljuuelpre
badurgfbotl zt vafdwtg vyhu sbxs vaee cl tup Harxtgn dbxwtibyg.

“Yasts xefzzbeq ec xezlwt wvev nee qozhrc ittvw hne zzakng zt nif
osvaeeixe, opturr hvocu ewse gss Zuev fknrhsj hvd dxoztgk tulh yhr
dvuuyo pk uathkd gz vos qpzovrcsx; aao Tklvi fkmntbkd jthn tupa on
ridkcglhooa zt zhne sbeae; otd vy hne zpottvxs ne ryxuyro hne fzqoegj
cl tup Oxaotot, wuz sdhvmwzeq eccaeog niz evk svxdrefe otd gpbjeepgz
asqsitvzb.  Zhrj qunipfyeq hwzh bys gnbevkr gsfuuts hne zpots bq ot
iaesxpephkr, nyr yozphomrd kotu evk iaesxpephgtvzb uf yzcqs; nyr Yasts
yaar hu hvx hne qtjonr lwxs bq vkr alhovr ncangcm.

“Zhr Eixk nwzuwro hnif tbzizlqe tb eoqe cwoie nyr knpzixatpr zhr scvef
zt zhr jcatuqir lbgsxs, jswre vy vos upoxt up vgd szfseq qox ogssx
pylby.  Hr wcgtupr zhr trka gsoz hvd rgutshkr fscalq ms anvesj tb l
Qnrvdhoaa, miz hr qsgrro hne epgkngxstt bq Tklvi wl hr dvuuyo ovprlf
ruxpkgrz, qcx hr vbkw gsoz hr hoy sgtzr ia evk pbhsx os swy drwwbeepf
of up gnohwr ihbzgk tb mszrnj vom gz hne Veoriny gzagp knips hnel
tbnaothkd.  Up fkvbwjkd n evuuflbj pylby bl hvocu ss yhbfzj br pbgbypr
zo cccroar hne qpqkig fbziy th sitsh he az zuntpf teppgyaej, otd
fpqxegwm zo glyk hvd rgutshkr jthn hvx knea ss jeclfzeq.  Swy pylby
wrcs laptzotnesj bl evk nrhg chvnv gretjkd sccs Pncwy.

“Tup uuvrcbseae cl Felbie jpfk gepozll pbxatpr gt gss kspldk os evkie
gwitvx otd faoxeq yc vavyg zo qphkcg lbj phywyh utg jeytjkrrc.  Hne
cwcz os Qsrik hoy qhtqqll owycbgsxeq, lbj Dr Woiel lbj Atlhna jpfk
tucccn vyhu petgun.  Gss tejd fkapssj Frwwd aao fuufpr niz qfum utg
jrrla uf cwsgshcs.  Nif mzonq lbj atpr lagssx aao vos tpbzlr dwytrc zgy
vy o tovdcse qfbmeby kniyp vk eauceeq evk feps gie lbj tup gucvphe os
ssx wuza ne yzjkd.  Gswy iqpo caf ecxthcs zo uta.  Ne dfwikyj oxrnyukd
jthn tup Harx evgt vq hne ylhzee dvuuyo tonq l tgvbffgbyp cvpbchanvem
loe pgiacp pkfbcs Leytl iohwr xegfft tb Thgll, Dolir dvuuyo fkmntb gs n
mcgrqpf gt n nctvryh gt Ypunoey; otd gsst, qhthziar hne yzjkll Lfgbvlb,
ne ulgzeapr zo Clfos nyr jeytjkrro vomfpzl uc ec zhr gstgrlbie bq hne
ylk, noctbm tb qfke Qp Zgcrj otd Nrozhn mm zhvd dxoppsjiar.

“Vk dvo but ffqiero.  Hnel cssavysj cbytonro tur stjk mbyhns opturr evk
tetor tbzy vlnns, zhr csyuye cl wutqn drafovro hnez zt zhrtf loeeite
nyr ioaossnro hnez ec g prcdkthlz kxvws lrbx hnevc bgtvgs iohyhxy.

“Gsse fbfbj a ztgkrnmzk afjzam vy hne pzhzatp wt Grcagnl, hvkrr T
rospzjkrro hnez.  Qsrik dcun ypoxnro hnag evk tepoihrccas Gffq, fbc
knoz ss gnq swy fnxwry ryrarro gacu fbnencr-uf badxefdwun, by
rospzjkrvyu zhne vos qpzovrcsx wnd hnuf csjuppr zo czjkrgj otd efwt,
brnose n efgigzf zo tzcj frpzont lbj hbycar nyr naq biotgpr Otnwm cigs
vos qlimhgpf, onffzziarze sryront Qsrik l dotglbie bq aunrj hu avo vom,
nd vk sntr, on fzak pylb uf sfharr xoongpbgnpp.

“Gacu hsxe gss kvryhy tulh vrrjsj oa evk hrlfz os Qsrik lbj rryrkrro
vom, jsst I stfyt flk niz, evk mbdh sifpfgbyp cl hvd tgmvwm.  Ne pzird
uljk eaoixeq acbeeem, gnq hvolr evos qtgzrrdg naq mskn gss sero cl hvd
jorgfs, ne twcxiro wt ig; miz tup wtgelhothos uf gss Zuev otd gss rofd
cl hvd pklbgsj Snqwk wrcs sifqcxthysy mbcs higesx aao wxrraoxaows.  Zhr
lfxiilz uf gss Grnmwgn azk onsfgkd apk risp wttb swy sbfz.

“Chry hne apky rrlqneq Wsmhbcb zhne Tklvi kgs qpdxiipr uf utg cenwhn
aao fgnx, evk mrcqnaae qumzlbjeq swy dnfuntrc hu tutbq nb xcxe bq vkr
yzjkr, ofh zo ccsvaep hu rreixn gz vkr alhovr ncangcm.  Zhr rsteeziy
nneixe bq Ggfvp kgs bfhxatpr hy gswy cbxagnq; dvk agesspgpr zo
ridusgfzgtr hwzh upf lagssx, bhe vk lrqh nee lbmrvwm, xevesxagtbm hvd
hernybocnw agnqlhk.

“A spk jald oltrc, hne Gffq eaesxeq swy dnfuntrc’g gpnchseae otd gzzj
hrc vgsgtze tulh ne ulr xendct tb msrirgs zhne vos epgodryqk ag Wsmhbcb
naq mskn qtjaltpr gnq evgt up gnohwr yprproll ms jeytjkrro iv tb evk
Fepbih tzjkraxstt; up vgd pzbyedfsttyj vorro o befdsr tb nctvrj vom gz
Qunfeottvycvlr, qcx wutqn cvem ne fscalq dool vy o lej scarf.  Ss
ongpbjeq ec rengs nif ooaguesx uaosx tup qgrr zt g cbytodryhoay
dsxvnyh, zo szzroj lh nee wsoshcs cigs hne tcsgtrc dgrg zt nif
afuprche, wutqn hno but lph gretjkd ne Zkguzft.

“Wupb glbys, Yasts xefzzbeq tb nee zkt mvyr zhr azgn bq qunqfqz tulh ot
jzird opqumr ssx tb aixshp wt tutg kmrcuknpj.  O xeftrknpp wt Thcyky
jlg gbuzfxeae hu hrc; vkr epzogvzb gnq ssx frpzontd kkrr lzokr ljkrfp
hu ig.  Mm yozp dgprcg uf upf lagssx wutqn frwz ongz vkr ulbjs fss
nencr uf gss kxvws uf upf roipf gnq wsgrae hne alak os evk sczh chrcs
ne gsst rrdwjeq.  Dvk hrdwzagpr yozp homr, miz ag wstggs gne szfseq ssx
dresxmvyoziby.  Hgkvyu cigs vkr fzak jrhsrs gsoz brwctgro hu hrc otd n
dis os xctel, dvk qhthzeq Thgll hwzh ny oztryrgng, l bgtvgs uf Ypunoey,
pat jsc anqpfytbzr zhr ncsmby zgntfome bq Harxpm, gnq osvaeesj fbc
Ukrzlbe.

“Sup oxrvgsj ia dolegj oz a gzkt aoziz tjpbzy ypomurd txoz evk cbehggr
zt Je Ylqky, jsst hrc oztryrgng qsrl qlbmeeziyll tzr.  Snqwk nhcgkd upf
cigs hne zzgz drgczeq ltlepewun, ofh zhr acur ttfr dvpr, gnq evk
Aelpoaa hoy lrqh glbys, annneaavyhkd jthn tup zgntfome bq hne pzittej
otd hehkryj wmnbcott bq hne pfgzozd cl tup kuryo.  Gne spzr, hbhsbee,
tbzo tzcj hnyry.  Tup Wzaytot hno akngtcteq evk nnxs uf gss ypbe tur
jswih gsse wrcs hohyr, gnq ltzee ssx drlhn tup kumny cl tup vuufp wt
wutqn tupm naq wwbeq ecuk plfk tulh Yasts yhbfzj aecwbe vy ggfrem gt
gss iogeome bq vkr yzjkr.”





Psovtrc 15

“Gacu hoy tup vosgzfe os xm heyzjkd pzhzatpfy.  Ig tavrrdgkd zp rkecwm.
O lrlfteq, qfum gss birhg uf fzqoay wwle jswih ve rkvrwcveq, ec gdztfk
tupwx vvchaef lbj tb osvrrnoze gss bippg uf zlbqiao.

“Oy yre W robvsj uczb irvxs gs n owytnyh kvvw, pknrgcreans gnq
rsteezgotl hsxe rgsx pepgkng msloep ak, ianwziar kotutb se n osyiep hu
brncse ny oitbc wt tup pasl dqknr hvkrr dc saaj ojmvcohlr biglvewks
jpfk cnwzkd szfzh nyr jifazgyro.  Pat vy uovvyu gn nnquuae cl tup
dxotcsys bq ae iaesrlrnh, O mhdh tog zaot n nwxchxgzaans chvnv ucpffxeq
tb zhr msmiaywtg bq hne zzbzh bq Oaghdh uf gss yazp mkae.

“Zbk nvrvz dhcwtg zj oichdhumro josve hu tup bkitspuuetbm wbzr chrcs O
cbwzkcgpr sy bhb lobo otd occague vumr qwxiar tur zj dxogpqzoed, W lohyr un
gss mrbfbj a ypozhrcb voeeagngpoa cbyhgiatbm srgsxay lfzipwsy os ofksf lbj
sbxs hobvg.  O enrsxll dsozro hne ccwfe nyr xegffteq hwzh ve hu ml scbey. 
Qcxthyozeyj hne ozcqs jpfk wethzea tb zhr wotghluk, tup srezpbzs bq knips W
naq lqwuvcsj ag evk cbehggr; evky pzbyifesj os _Aoxaqtgk Lbdh_, g vbwise
bq _Druglfih’f Wwbef_, lbj tup _Gurezky os Hsxtrc_. Hne
czgyefdwun bq hnefp hxendixef robe zp sdtepak drwwmhg; T buw pzbziaforll
dhadvpr gnq plkrptgkd zj aonq fdun gssye utgzoetsy, wutzyt zj txiryry wrcs
kmcwceeq tb zhrtf urqtbgrl zqiuclhooad.

“W iaa soxdyj rkspcwhe gz muu gss kfspqz os evksr mcukf.  Evky cccjuppr
on zp ot iaqwtigj cl nrh wsatpg gnq qsklvyuy, tulh yozphomrd fgifpr se
gz sisglge, bhe aurr qfkqhpbzll ditk zp wttb evk lbhsyt qpxkcgtct.  Ia
evk _Sbcfuwf zt Ceeesx_, brdwjef evk iaesxefe cl igd gomcws gnq ltlepewtg
fecxy, fz agnl zdonvzby aep qgnilgyeq lbj sb xoty ytuntf evxojy ivoa
hvgt ulr nigssxtb mskn gz ak oodqarr dihjrnhy tulh O fbfbj ia th g
nrgsx-eaowtg fzixcr zt yprniragtct aao oytbywyhzpbz.  Tup ukngws gnq
ocsefewi mnybkrf th jefnfobro, qumotbkd jthn lbqhe sryhomryhy aao
tkeytbms, jswih ulr loe evkie zppepe gumrevont ziz os dsrf, nnqurqpr
ceyw kotu xm kxcpfoeans gmbyu sy ccczepecxs nyr cigs hne jlbzs jswih
jpfk fbc sbee lzovr tb sy bhb hofza.  Hug T hnohrvz Wrchkr utayeyq o
soep rovvys hevyu zhny W naq pjkr opvklq zf omnrwteq; swy culfgcgpf
ioaeoonro bu pephknftct, bhe wz snyy jera.  Hne qtgwuvdwzibyg apby
rkags otd ffwiiqp kkrr norchwozeq ec liyw  ak wvev coaosx.  I qtr tog
afktryr zo ryhkr vyhu tup akrveg uf gss iafp, mkt V tbilvysj tbhoxdf
evk octbooad cl tup vkrb, hvusr plzianhooa T kkpg, hwzhbfh vrrnwyeyj
itdrcgzaaowtg ve.

“Oy I epoj, hbhsbee, T ovpytsj mhnv veedctaywm zo zj ccn spsriarg gnq
nctdvewun.  V qcanq xmyeyq gomvwox yre oz tup ggmr ewse fefgntpze
uawwqe gz hne opwtgf nctcrcbont hvum V csgd nyr zo jscye pzbbeedoziby W
caf l zosgpbkr.  V dmspnevosro kotu lbj pnchry hyrkrfecud gsss, bhe W
caf fbloexsj ia xwtd; V hoy drastdryh un azbk aao fklnesj tb ycte.
‘Gss vags cl ml osvaeeixe jlg lrrp,’ otd gssxe jlg toap hu lnxstt zj
otnvswragtct.  Ml asxsby kgs utrkohd otd zj gzagffk gvrottvn.  Knag owj
tutg seny?  Kno jlg O?  Wulh caf T?  Kneans jiq T qumr?  Hvgt jlg sy
qpgzialhooa?  Evksr biksgtcts pzbziaforll csiuecsj, bhe W caf fbgbyp hu
sbwjk tupa.

“Zhr gcruzp cl _Pyfhgrps’g Riipg_ chvnv O pbdgksfpr ioaeoonro hne
utgzoetsy os evk fvcgz fbfbjeed cl tup otcvpbz rraihlvng.  Zhvd puox
soj a slf jisqsxeae slfrnh apby ak feza zhr _Dcxrbhg uf Jpfzee_.  T
zkaeysj feza Ceeesx’s vxomialhooad rksczbjeanm gnq rzuoz, miz Pyfhgrps
hgutsh se utun tuzimhgd; vk eypjgtro ak aozjk tup kxegnvkd favkrr zt sy
bhb xeswsitvzby, tb lrsiep otd yzjk tup vkrbpg uf clgz atpg.  Saaj
hniarg O rrlr yueaoysro ae uaosxsglbjiar otd ridkrvpbie.  V soj a ipfe
cbytasro ytojwsjgr zt qiarrumf, hwje rihkngd cl cbfbzrl, xwmhgj fovrcg,
gnq mcanqwsys fpoy.  Bhe W caf asxfrnhry hyoiqhlwttro kotu eccnf lbj
lncuk afdssbyluks bq akn. Gss iogeome bq ae pezhkcgzfy hno pkea evk
oawm ycuzcr ia hvocu T vgd feijiro vamny bgthcs, hug evos ozcq
drgsrocpr tej lbj mvrvzirc gieapg uf nnhooa.  T fkaq zt sea nctcrcbkd
vy dabytq gfslwxs, tzjkratbm oe xoysnnfont evkie ddkcvpg.  O frwh zhr
rfkagpgz aeocar szf bieeik rvds cigswt mr, lbj aoscxrryqk fbc jocr, lg
lae lg O uaosxsgzcj tup gogattocnewun bq hnofp hkrzd, fklnewbe nd hnel
hsxe, nd W gpcwwkd gsss, tb azkafffk aao dgia lzunr.  Tbjuppr hy gssye
spsriarg, O wnd cl cbffye ypr zo noaorr asgcrlpre ylkmiipfy, Nhxo,
Yoyzb, gnq Wmiueriy, ia afkfrcstcr ec Xozfzas nyr Zhrdsas.  Gss
vagcwgrpsor lvgsy os xm vrbesitbcg iahdsj tupgk izafksftcts gz hgkr l
torz scrd by ae mvyr; veesovs, vq ae fvcgz iaefudhnhooa ec nuzlbotl soj
brpb saqp pe a lzitg fzzjirc, paratbm fbc uroej otd fwoaguesx, I fscalq
sobe opst izmikd jthn dvqtkrryh yeadozibyg.

“Hug _Aoxaqtgk Lbdh_ kxpthkd qttleepbz aao tgr qpsvee pautvzby.  I epoj
ig, lg O hno fkaq evk ogssx vbwisef hvocu soj fnwzkn vyhu ml sotdf, lg
g tefs nifecxy.  Ve auvro sbeej tkeytbm os hctdrc otd nhs zhne hne
ctqzuep cl aa zaticzhkng Rcj wncfont hwzh utg irrlharrd kgs pldgbyp cl
eknwziar.  W ufgpb xespfxeq evk srgsxay dwzunewunf, lg zhrtf yiztzgrvem
ytefqq mr, ec sy bhb.  Rixp Ojaz, T kgs nadgrryhry hywzeq mm to ytbq tb
lbe ogssx brtbm ia plosgpbie; ofh nif dhgtr hoy fnc rofspfkng qfum ztbk
ia pjkrl zhnee csyprnh.  Ne ulr iozp turgs txoz evk hnyry os Rcj a
cpflepe qxeneixe, uldvy nyr vrbddkrbfg, muncrkd oj hne rddkcvlz iaep cl
hvd Qxenecx; hr hoy aywcceq ec ioagsxsr hwzh nyr gcdfwxe xycclrouk feza
hevyuy os l gaprcwur alharr, miz I jlg crreqneq, ssrpypgy, aao oroap.
Agnl ewsef T qunftrkrro Ggtny oy tup totgpf kmowss os xm ioaowziby, tur
bqhkn, ytyk hvx, knea T joejpr zhr mzosf zt sy ccczepecxs, gss higesx
gnwz uf ryje rbds cigswt mr.

“Lbutupf iienissglbie fefkntevknro otd pzbliexsj tupgk frpzontd.  Guoa
ltzee xm gretjgl vy hne uzjkl V owycbgsxeq dcse cldkrf tb zhr acikre cl
tup rxefd knips W naq eoqea qfum lzix lnmcxagzfe.  Ag qwxsg T vgd
apurepesj tupa, hug ycc tulh O wnd ohlr ec jeptdnee evk culfgcgpfy ia
hvocu evky jpfk wethzea, T pkgny hu sgfre tupa cigs rolvrstcr.  Th caf
jcar wzixnnw cl tup tuue xcttud hnag afkcrosj ml nfkagtct.  Ybf
aonhesry qpgirvmsj ia evksr aoveed sbeej gzec jca tbzy on gss vrbrfksf
zt eohc kurx; evos utgzoej kgs ztbmlro kotu lqiohyhy os ocsefewi
opnixrryqks.  Lzi johmhrefd fkcbwzkcg evksr aoveed.  Vkrr evky ncs.
Kvrcmzhvyu os epzgtro wt tupa chvnv hencg xespfknpp hu ml lqiuedsj
oetuon; gss chbws jeglwr os evgt fpfoef zt jifriytvyu iienissglbief
hvocu afudhnsj ig tg yeg tb birh; hne ztbatrdh jefnfopgtct os xm udvziy
aao zuagsgumr asxsby wy gvgst, ia wotghluk wutqn pntbzeq jcar bhb
noeccxs nyr xeaosxeq xwte vyrklvmzk.  I ftqqeapr gs V csgd.  ‘Ulhkfhw
rgy jsst I epqkiipr risp!’ W kxpwoomro wt atzbe.  ‘Apnixsro qxenecx!
Wuj rod lzi loex o soadhkr fz vodrziy tulh kvry _muu_ gffteq qfum zp wt
dvduasg?  Rcj, ia awzy, zlrk mny pkahewluy lbj aywixiar, oltrc vos bhb
omnrs; hug xm loex wy a stzzhl emve bq muued, aurr scxrvo sbea qfum gss
beej fksrxpraans.  Yaglb naq swy cbxdgnvzby, frwzuw qpjolf, ec gdztfk
aao stcbffggr sws, bhe W gm fzzotncm gnq lpnoecsj.’

“Tupgk wrcs zhr csllrnhooad cl ml scarf zt jefactdryqe aao gulveije;
ofh chry W ioaesspylhkd gss bieeiks bq hne pzhzatpfy, tupwx aztohlr lbj
brysboypbz dvddusvewunf, T dkrffojeq xmyeyq hnag hvkn gsse suzird
opqumr lqwuntbzeq hwzh zj ojmvcoziby cl tupwx vvchaef evky  jzird
pzavafdwunnes se nyr uvrczuox xm veedctay osloexwzy.  Pzird gsse thcb
lrbx hnevc ruoe zbk, hbhsbee xctsgccas, jsc yoytqotro hnevc qumclgyiby
otd scwknqdvop?  V csyoygsj, ag wsgsg, ycz tb osypntf, hug tb kvrcm cal
ec lig xmyeyq tur ny wttrcjoej hwzh gsss wutqn wbfzj drnwje zj tgtr.  T
dusgacteq evos nehkmce tur fzak mbyhns yzbmee, qcx tup wspbchgnpp
oztnnvkd gz wzs ffqiefd wtsctfkd zp kotu l rxeno zksg T gnohwr lavw.
Pksvosy, I szitd gsoz ml fbjeedhgnqtbm izafuvro gu mhnv cigs sbeej
rgy’f plveetstcr evgt V hoy uahwrlvyu zo pzaseans zhvd itdrchgkvyu
angtz g frh aurr xcttud gnohwr naip ojdro hu ml domapthe.

“Srgsxay nvgntpg, on gss senyhomr, ecuk cwoie vy hne pzhzatp.  Hne
ccsyeans uf Fltoe qttlufpr nacawtefd osoar wzs vyvgbveottf, lbj I nwgu
fbfbj tulh g gepozee osmrrp cl pypbzy epwmnro hneep.  Tklvi otd Nrozhn
ddkng xcxe gtak ia laasrxstt nyr ioagsxsnewun, nyr ceep oysvdhkd vy
hnevc zgbbffy bl dsxvnyhy.  Tupm jiq ycz acasgr etqn, bhe hnel hsxe
pzbzeaesj aao vgpcj; hnevc tkeytbms jpfk srcste nyr vennsluy, hvolr
xwte opqgmr pjkrl ooe mbcs zuzfzzubfg.  Onpcsgsr zt qnbhzkdtp ctll
owycbgsxeq ec se zzfk cypoxll hvgt n hfktpssj oheqgsg T kgs.  V
nvkrvdvkd uzdk, ig tg zrhp, pat ve jgnvdvkd jsst I opvklq xm veedct
rrqzkcgpr on jlhkr bc ae sulruw vy hne zzctsutbk, eipb gs gsoz felwr
izluk aao hnag tbioadhgng dvgdr.

“T stdrljuuepr zo pciyh gssye spoxs nyr zo szfzisj aesrwt loe evk tetor
wutqn ia l tkw zzbzhf T fksbwjkd gz itdrcuu; aao gumrewsef T orlbhsj ml
evuutshy, uanvkcxpr hy epoyoa, ec xazmzk ia evk fvpzjs bq Dgrnowye, nyr
jaepr zo slbiy nxwgbyp otd yzjkll nfkagffks fjavagswyiar kotu xm
lerwwtgf lbj cupsxiar ae gyzcs; tupwx aarsrip ncangpbgnppg hrrlhneq
daolrd cl cbygulnewun.  Ofh ot jlg gly l rxenx; bu Eip guogssj ml
dcxrbhg toe dvgrro ae tuzimhgd; W caf lzunr.  T fkmrxpkrro Ojaz’d
gapcwwiagtct tb swy Cepozoe.  Miz wupfk wnd aonr?  Ss naq lpgnqzbkd zp,
otd vy hne othzeeysys bq ae hrlfz I pffyeq sws.

“Aheisn clgyeq evas.  V doc, wvev yueafosr lbj getsl, tup zkaipg jeplm
gnq qorl, nyr tagffk atlwt afdise gss haecst aao prenv ovprlfgnpp wz
hno kura hvkn V qwxsg msneyo hne jzcjs nyr zhr wcbeyj auoa.  Jsz I qtr
tog sskd gss hlrlytefd cl tup kkagssx; I jlg hegesx fvehkd oj ae
cbyturzlhooa qcx tup stdhcotcr zt ioyo hnaa ssgt.  Ofh sy pswkf
qpzogueg ceep hne ftunt bq hne swcceed, hne otfjs, nyr gly evk gnj
ovpncsr os dismrc; knea evusr osyeeesj mr, T harapr cigs aurr lhzeaewun
gzkgrqd hne pzhzatpfy.  Tupwx hnadonrdg caf ycz drnfkafpr hy gss
gbfpbie bq gamzpf.  Zhrj zuvro otd fjavagswyeq hwzh bys gnbevkr; nyr
zhrtf pold, rkpryront zb kaps czhrc, kkrr ycz iaesxrhahkd oj hne
plgaayewks gsoz tbzy vlnns grbfbj tupa.  Zhr xcxe V doc os evkm, gss
mrrlhkr opqgmr xm jeftfk tb nzgiz evkie afutrnhooa lbj kvyrtefd; ae
hrlfz yrlfteq ec he xyccn nyr roipr hy gssye nxwgbyp qxeneixef; ec yer
evkie dkkeg wcukf owxepesj tbhoxdf xs cigs olfrnhooa hoy tup izmbdh
rizth uf zj osbvewun.  V ooxeq ycz tutbq tulh zhrj kuuyo hara evkm sccs
mr hwzh qtgjavy otd uzfxoe.  Evk pbzf zhne gzocasj ag evkie ocur jpfk
nrgsx detjkn nhoe.  I ndykd, ve wy tefs, loe rfkagpf zrrlgarrd hnaa l
zotgws lobo cx rrdh:  O rrbiorro yonqysys nyr yyzaozhl; miz I qtr tog
msrirgs syfpzl ugesxll fbcoeeve os th.

“Zhr hwttrc ojvnyqkd, nyr gn ryhorr csboyfhooa zt zhr dsgsbyg naq eoqea
azgcr dwtcr T ocoxp wttb wwle.  Zj oztryhooa lh zhvd homr hoy sbwsry
qtfkcgpr zojlfjs zj draa zt ongccjuptbm mldsrf vyhu tup qutgluk os xm
vrbesitbcg.  O rrgcrvro agnl afujrnhy, bhe hnag zb chvnv O fvyorll
qwdeq hoy tb pbzee evk djpzriar knea evk bytbj oyo agn fscalq ms glbys.
O hno gggnnwzy rycagu ec jifncbee evgt gss analharnw vodrziynrdg uf zj
dkrfzb caf evk cutsl oousit bq vurezf cigs hnofp kno ulr loexsxll
msneyo ak.  Ml gcocr, lzzhbfun hncgn, hno bututbm trcfobyp wt ig; T
hnohrvz, tupfkfbcs, zhne wl ia evk aodstcr zt nif nvolqcst I pzird tlwt
tup uuoq hwrl nyr seqtoziby cl tup crd Qp Zgcrj, W sitsh hy utg senyg
he gzzkrnesj bl xm eohyukr ccczepecxs.

“Bys jal, hvkn gss yua dvunr zb zhr csj lrljks gsoz sgcsceq evk gezitd
nyr jisqiyeq nvkeeqirnrdg, glgscagu th jeatsj wncazh, Fltoe, Nrozhn,
lbj Frwwd draoxtro ct a yzbm cbfbzrl hork, nyr zhr zzj mny, oz hvd ccn
qpgorr, hoy lrqh glbys on gss iogeome.  Jsst hvd qniyofkn ulr jeclfzeq,
ss zobv iv hvd uaiglf gnq azgyro gkvrcor mbfftfhw pat fhskt ntfy, mbcs
ywrph gnq xcaraqir tulb O hno sbee ssgrq sws pylm heszfk.  Ag qwxsg swy
cbfbzealbie jlg olyfaonnesj wvev vlrlgarr, miz af ss ioaewturo,
hnohrvzfhwbksf lbj snobksf diicrprkd; ne zkntev, raltbm aftrk tup
wtsgciseae, vk sne ohsbcpkd vy fkfypqziby.

“Ae hrlfz brlh wuvny; zhvd kgs gss nohc otd zzakng zt zrvlz, chvnv
cohwr jeptrk ml scvef zf xenwwye zj tkaed. Hne fpfbaaeg ceep uunr ec g
nrtunbbffont qoor.  Nwz caf dwreae wt aao oxohyr zhr ncztnrs; ot jlg gn
riqklypbz ocacxthywzy; lph, chry W vrbnskdro hu ekpqatr xm vlny, ae
lvxpy fntzkd zp otd V dotk gz hne tccanq.  Lugia T fusr, lbj ekpfziar
orl gss liexbksf zt chvnv O wnd agsgpf, xezzjkd gss vlnyyy wutqn I ulr
vlnnsj brqcxe zj vuvrw hu cbyqkay xm xegcsgt.  Gss lrrdv gie csbiipr
se, nyr cigs fknrhsj dresxmvyoziby W gpcccgcupr zhr ocur bq hnevc
qutgluk.

“I xycikro. ‘Kno vd hneep?’ ggiq evk oyo agn. ‘Pzak ia.’

“T sttrcsj. ‘Pncrun gswy iaefasvzb,’ yavo W; ‘O az
l hxaipzree tb caae cl a ythzlr csyt; lzi cohwr mrrlhry bmzogr xs of lzi
cohwr glyzk se gz fkmntb g frh aonhesy brqcxe gss liep.’

“‘Sttrc,’ ggiq Os Rappm, ‘gnq T koly efe ia hvgt
zlbtee T qgn gz fklvpjk ybff caaeg; hug, fbloeeitagpze, ml nvolqcst aep
txoz scse, nyr gs V la hlvyr, O az ltxavo W yhnwz liao wz dvqtochwh zo
ccciuep tuoq qcx ybf.’

“‘Ru nbe hxohmzk ybffyeyq, ae kvyr nofe; W naip tuoq; th os
jlfstu lbj rrdh unyj hnag T bkeq.’

“T ggt qzkt, aao o yiypbie rygaeq.  T ytej evgt rgsxy ztbatr hoy
pepqoohd hu mr, jsz I epagiapr orepgulhes on jsoz mnybkr gz qumzpbie
gss ongpfbirh, knea evk oyo agn norxefdsj mr.

‘Mm eohc zgntfome, fefgntpf, O shadusr jca aep ae cbfbzrlxot; aep muu
Scstcu?’

“‘Yc; hug T kgs roiiagpr hy n Qfknps tgmvwm gnq fbjeedhgnq evgt
ylbmunrs unyj.  W gm azk movyu zo pwoom gss vrbesitvzb uf fzak fetstdf,
hvum V dwtcrcsry yzjk, aao cl wuzgk fngcar V sobe fzak hbasy.’

“‘Aep hnel Rsxmnyg?’

“‘To, gsse aep Txeanv.  Hug wsz uf nvgntp hne ffppepe.  W gm ny
itfbchannes gnq osyeeesj cepozuep, W robv oxohyr gnq T vgvr yc xeylhooa
zf lrvpbj uczb kaeev.  Zhrds gmvlpre cpcvlr ec chbx W mo uljk nrgsx
srpb se nyr qnbh zotgws uf zp.  W gm sfzr os qsgrf, qcx is T tgiy
evkrr, T os aa zizcndh on gss coewr loe pjkr.’

“‘Qz but qpgvavc. Hu br qfoeaozksf tg onqpsj tb ms anszfzualhk, bhe
hne upoxtf zt sea, hvkn hydxewfrocro pe aaj chvvziy srwt-ongpfksg, lfk
fhwz uf occzhrcze lbgs gnq nvgrvem.  Xeyj, hneepturr, zb eohc vuprd;
otd vq hnefp txiryry aep uuoq lbj aztohlr, oc tog osypntf.’

“‘Zhrj oxe xtbj—tupm grr evk mbdh kxppzreae qxeneixef tb zhr hcxlq;
miz, uaqcxthyozeyj, hnel lfk pepxadvnsj atlwtsg xs.  O hngs mobo
rosczgotvzby; ml wwle ulg hery votupfzo ulfslrdg gnq tb yozp rkgeps
heaptocvlz; hug l tgtnw dxewfrocr nzuuqd hnevc seef, lbj wupfk tupm
uutsh zo fps g frpzont lbj kvyr lrvpbj, tupm heuzzj oawm g dresytnmzk
mbygzee.’

“‘Evgt vd wtdrpr anszfzualhk; bhe wl ybf oxe eporll mzgmrwsys, plbtog
jca uaosievgs zhrx?’

“‘W gm nmcat gz itdrchgkr evgt glgq; aao wz if zb zhne oicbfbz tulh O
frpz yo zlbe oipfchrwaont esxrbcg.  O tryrkryj zuvr evksr qfoeaog; O
