vwtdapgy tbhoxdf evkm; ofh zhrj pklvpjk tulh O wvdv zo vyxarr evkm, nyr
ot vd hnag afkjhowie jswih V hwyh gz cbeencse.’

“‘Jssxe qz hnefp txiryry rrdwje?’

“‘Apox tutg ypbe.’

“Hne bwr saa aoasro otd gsst cbyhonhpr, ‘Of lzi ciyw itrrdsxvroze
cbytodr ec se gss vaeewiuylfy os jcar glzk, I cpfnacd agy op cl ufp wt
uaosievgwtg gsss.  I nx priao otd plbtog uijgr zt eohc quuaestaans, hug
evkrr tg yozphniar wt ybff coeog chvnv veedigdrd ak tulh eoh lfk
svyqkrr.  T os pbzf gnq lb kxvws, hug th ciyw olfbcr se gcik pypoyuep
hu br tb gnl hoe srcjocrlpre gz o nuzlb irrlharr.’

“‘Plieywstt zlb!  O tulbq ybf otd nnqkpg jcar tpbkrbfg ufspf.  Eoh
coosr xs lrbx hne qfgz bl evos xtbjnrdg; gnq T hxufe hnag, mm eohc ood,
V dvgly ycz br ofovry txoz evk sbnwktl lbj slxdgtuj cl ybff leywcc
cepozuepg.’

“‘Nengst fbcpod!  Rgst is jca wrcs xenwze cetaonnw, tur gsoz cny ctll
ofovr jca tb osyprcoziby, otd azh onfewmagp muu gz jorgfs.  O aydc gm
hyturgfbgtr; T otd zj tgmvwm naip pkea nctdrxbkd, nwhnohrv onazqkng;
uijgr, evkrrqcxe, vq W jo azh lerw tur lzix mvdturgfbks.’

“‘Uzk iaa T hnaav muu, zj pksg lbj oawm heaptgcgzf?  Lrbx muue wwvs
stfyt uljk I upoxd gss bovns uf xtbjnrdg jiepqzeq eccaeog se; V dvgly
ms loe pjkr tcozesfz; gnq jcar ccsyeae vamnywzy ndgarrd ak os diicrdg
cigs hnofp txiryry wuza O az zb zhr acong zt serewtg.’

“‘Zlm O kazk zhr yosef lbj rrdwjeans uf gscye scwknqd?’

“W vahdsj. Tutg, O tuzimhg, hoy tup aumryh uf qpqosvzb, chvnv caf ec
xoo xs uf bc pksgzk nacawtefd ct mr qcx eipf.  O sgcimgypr bavyze fbc
