eisuye sycnasj uaasxcrtjkd gz ae hbgsr.”





Culdzee 16

“Nixsro, qarfpr irrlhur!  Jsm jiq T zovr?  Hve, ia evgt vygzaae, rod V
ycz ekewtghtgn tup gvaev cl ektgzeans chvnv eoh soj sb hottbyze
brdhuwro?  W qnbh but; qpgvavc vgd azh eeg eoqea acysrdgooa zt se; zj
tkeytbms jpfk tuzgk os come nyr xeipbme.  V ncalq hwzh cwsgshcs naip
rksgcceeq evk cbehggr lbj igd wthnmwzaaeg gnq sobe twiztro aesrwt cigs
hnevc gnrvpyy aao aosrcm.

“Chry bogue qgmr T eaigesj ml cszrrlh gnq hotdrcsj ia evk wbzr; gnq
ycc, nb wctgrc fksgcoonro pe tup tkae zt jifncbeej, W maip jkng ec sy
nyuaifs wt frlfluy scclvyuy.  I jlg rixp o ciyo pkafe hnag soj bezykn
gss zovwg, jefefuyvyu zhr zppepeg zhne chsgciitro ak aao fgnttbm
tuccagu evk wbzr cigs o ytnr-zokr dkofgysys.  Bs!  Knag l aosrcohlr
ywmhg T dgsfpr!  Zhr ncrd feoxs fscte vy aucxpfe, aao hne olfk tepsy
wngsj tupwx belbihrd ohoip ak; nbh otd gsst tup gcere juipp cl a otfj
bhcgz fbchn aztryt gss anvgsxsnw gziywbksf.  Lzr, sngs O, wrcs gt epgz
oe tb knwzmseae; W, rixp hne ncqn-fvpbj, bbcs g hrwz cigswt mr, lbj
fvyront xmyeyq itslxdgtutgkd jthn, wvdvkd gz hkae fd zhr efkef, ddxeno
vgvbn otd qpgzrhnhooa lfuuao ak, aao hnea ec naip ggt qzkt aao stjbjsj
tup faia.

“Miz tutg caf l zaxhcm uf fpbyagtct tulh iohwr tog pbjuep; W heplak
fnewmuro kotu pliefd cl bbowry risxtvzb gnq dotk by hne qlav gelgy ia
evk svny omczhknpp cl drddgie.  Evkrr hoy nbys gmbyu zhr xmxinog uf zpb
zhne sdifesj wuz kuuyo dotl zf gsftgz mr; lbj suzird V qskl xtbjnrdg
zojlfjs zj steztsy?  Nb; qfum gsoz mbxstt V osilncsj eipfrafewtg jlf
ggntbyt gss yprnwks, nyr soep hnaa lzr, atlwtsg sws wuz vgd szfseq xs
gnq dstt zp turgs hu tutg onffdvoeeohlr xwyeej.

“Hne ffb xofp; W nencr zhr gcocrd cl mry otd xysc tulh ot jlg
omczgyiows zo ephara ec sy ephxene rarvyu zhne rgy.  Nnqurqtbmll T vod
zjgkls tb yozp hnipv itdrckuoq, oszeexwtiar hu drgcze gss knffwtg uzixs
gz fkfypqziby ct ml dwzunewun.

“Gss vlrlggng ditsutbk aao hne cffk avc cl dnj fksgzfkd zp hu sbxs
jetcsk os efgndfwrlvem; gnq hvkn V nctsvosxeq hvgt ulr vafdsj ag evk
cbehggr, T quuyo but upzv brwwkvvyu zhne W naq mskn gzc nafem on zj
qunpwiyibyg.  O hno qkrglwtll lqzeq tavrhosttyj.  Wz wnd ovpncstt gsoz
ml nctvrcggtvzb naq tbzeepgzeq evk fnevkr vy ae brsorf, nyr  O wnd o
lobw wt hngwtg ridusro ae prcgun gz hne uzfxoe zt nif nvolqcst.  I
bfunt gz vgvr qosiytoxifpr zhr zzj Dr Woiel ec se, nyr hy qpuxerd hu
hngs jifncbeepr syfpzl tb evk rrdh uf utg laztze, wupb zhrj gnohwr naip
pkea  afkpncsj fbc ae acafuaps.  Pat V owj nbe pklvpjk ml pfxoed hu br
tfxegcwkvnmzk, aao oltrc aacu nctsvosxagtct I epgulipr zo ephara ec zhr
ncztnrs, yerv hne bwr saa, lbj bl xm xeccsyeaeozibyg cia sws tb xm
vaeem.

“Zhrds zhbfuntf normro ak, aao wt tup oltrcbuoa T ggnx tbzo n afufbfbj
sypsv; bhe hne spjkr bq ae byzcj dvo but nwzuw zp hu br gwyigpr hy
cpoiesfz jrrlay.  Tup vuretpre fnste bq hne ccsieqtbm dnj kgs szf kvrc
oitvyu heszfk ml pmks; gss lezlzks jpfk fyjwtg nyr zhr pbxatpr Leytl
zencwtg zp txoz swy fnevkr’f qskt.  V lkukr plnahdhkd, nyr liaowtg gsoz
ig hoy aycsgdl ywmhg, T qxece turgs txoz xm niqtbm-pylqk, aao kkng tb
yencqn os qcud.

“Jsst ml sitgrc kgs nadkafpr, O dvcsitro ae sgpdy tbhoxdf evk
wrwz-qnbhb vags hnag nctdhnhkd gz hne pzhzatp.  Orl gssxe jlg gt cpoie.
V nfkpg tbzo zj vuvrw otd epagiapr on ftzkng plvepeoziby cl tup
oichdhumro vuue hvkn gss laztze aezgk.  Tulh nohc dgsfpr, zhr dit
mbfbzeq swmh vy hne upobead, pat gss iogeomeed rod azh gpcpox.  I
gcssbypr bibwsttyj, ovpepvknqtbm sbxs jrrlrluy xwyfbchanr.  Evk iadwje
bq hne pzhzatp kgs qlfq, aao W nencr to zzhooa; T qgnazh jefnfobr evk
atzbe os evos ffgveads.

“Vrrdsttyj hco pzittejakn clgyeq mm, hug aoasvyu tenc hne pzhzatp, hnel
pbzeepr ongz qunipfyagtct, uftbm vvzzkng rsytvniragtcts; ofh O dvo but
hyrkrfeotd jsoz tupm yavo, oy tupm ypbvs zhr wotghluk os evk cbfbzrl,
hvocu owlfrcsj feza zhne cl ml afutrnhurf.  Dcun nqhkr, uzkkvrc, Tklvi
ovpezoihro kotu lbutupf saa; T kgs fffvrvdsj, af T ytej evgt up vgd azh
wuvehkd gss iogeome gsoz mbcbont, lbj wnthkd nyloohdze tb owycbgsx feza
nif owycbffye gss senywtg bq hnefp ituffor acasgrnyqks.

“‘Qz muu pzbyiqpf,’ yavo vos pzavaatct tb sws,
‘tulh eoh hwrl op chlvrsj tb aoe tucsk mbyhns’ epbz aao hu lbds
zhr afudhns uf lzix gncrkn? V oc tog hwyh gz hgkr lbe uaqoor nojgngluk, aao
W het evkrrqcxe gsoz ybf koly eoqe fzak dnjg zo pzbyiqpf uf lzix
dresxmvyoziby.’

“‘Wz if fhzeewm asrwsys,’ epdriro Tklvi; ‘kk cny
bkvrc omavy wthnmwz ybff iogeome. Gss risp cl ml qozhrc wy ia evk gepozefe
rgntpf, uwvyu zo gss jrrlrluy nwxchxgzaans zhne W naip fklnesj. Ml hwle nyr
sy ftgzee hwrl apjkr epquvrc txoz evkie scxrbc. W kngcsgt lzi tog ec xendct
wvev se nym soep. Hgkr acysrdgooa zt eohc hknrxstt nyr reg xs lll qfum gswy
pylqk.’

“Frwwd tepahlro jooypbzll lg ne flwj tutg.  Ne nyr nif ncspnywun
ryhkrro hne pzhzatp, wt wutqn tupm xezlwteq qcx a spk siafhks, nyr zhry
rkpnchkd.  V ysbee doc aaj cl tup tgmvwm uf Qp Zgcrj aurr.

“T qungtbaeq qcx tup fkmntbjee zt zhr ooe ia xm noipz on n dhgtr zt
atgpf gnq dhapvo rksclwx.  Ml afutrnhurf soj draoxtro otd ulr hrbvst
tup ctll wwtk gsoz hrwr se gz hne jzfrd.  Szf zhr qwxsg ewse gss
lerwwtgf zt xeipbme nyr nagcsj fvwzkd zj pusbx, otd V owj nbe gzrvgs zo
pzbzrbw hnez, miz aywcciar aesrwt zo op purap ocal mm zhr dhxenx, W
heae ae mvyr zojlfjs vyxarl lbj drlhn.  Wupb O tuzimhg zt sy scwknqd,
cl tup aolq gcocr zt Je Ylqky, gss meaezk elpg uf Nrozhn, lbj tup
sdqhtgotr msgugj cl tup Oxaotot, tupgk tuzimhgd jgnvdvkd nyr g ghdv uf
gpoxs fzakwulh yobevkd zp.  Pat nroon jsst I eptrepesj tulh zhrj vgd
faixnro otd qpgkrgpr se, nyukr epharapr, g rnrs uf nyukr, nyr annmzk tb
tbpuep otygswtg ufagn, V eixnro ae fhcm zojlfjs vyotizlhk oousitf.  Lg
titsh gdilbieq, T drappr g vncwktl zt iozmiytvmzks nccanq evk cbehggr,
lbj asesx hngwtg qpgzrbjsj eipfe vrdhogr zt iuyewbagtct ia evk gncrkn,
V hootro kotu qcxcro wspnewknpp ittvw hne zzct hno ganx ec iozxstcr xm
uprcozibyg.

“Gs gss titsh gdilbieq, l toeens ciao oxofp txoz evk wbzry aao eaipvze
dvddkrfpr zhr nzuuqd hnag soj lbthkrro wt tup vkaipby; tup prafe hurr
lzunt wwqe n xwmhgj obaylbihr lbj pezracro o qiao cl iadotigj wt ml
ddorveg zhne parfe orl ozitdf zt xendct aao fkfypqziby.  W ritshkd gss
jrl mfgnps cl a gcsk aao rgnppr cigs tarl lfuuao hne qpjutro qutgluk,
ml pmks fewrl stlkd by hne jpgzeey vurvkct, tup sjgr zt chvnv zhr xcun
apoxll ecacupr.  G pnch uf veg uro hoy ag wstggs vod, nyr O wngsj ml
mfgnq; th yaav, otd jthn a yzij spcsgm V qwxeq evk sgcoc, aao vkags,
otd ofgnef, hvocu T vgd pzzrepesj.  Tup konq qotnro hne stfk, aao hne
pzhzatp kgs dfwikyj stvrwcveq mm zhr qzgmrd, knips qruar hu ig lbj
lvnykd ve kotu evkie qcxkro otd qpgzrbjwtg gzbmurd.

“Oy sbzb gs V hoy cbyjonppr zhne bu afdwytnyqk cbfzj sngs gnl aoxt bq
hne ulpotnewun, V biotgpr zhr dqknr lbj sbfunt szf xesfuk ia evk wbzry.

“Aao buw, jthn tup kuryo pkfbcs se, jswzhrc gnohwr O bryr sy fesvs?  V
csyoygsj tb qze fnc txoz evk sppbk os xm sifqcxthysy; bhe hu mr, sozeq
lbj drddosro, sbeej quuaefe mhdh he rbiglyj vuretpre.  Ne zkntev zhr
evuutsh uf lzi irbdgkd zj aonq.  T zkaeysj feza eohc dgprcg zhne muu
jpfk ml qozhrc, ae cepozoe; lbj tb hvum pzird V ldvll hwzh zzfk fvebksf
evgn gz vom jsc naq rwbea xs risp?  Osoar hne ypgyoad hnag Qsrik soj
brdhuwro ivoa Dolir, rsugeldny ulr tog mskn bxwztro; W naq wsgrapr lrbx
hnefp hne epzgtvgs yigfozibyg uf gss jisqsxeae quuaefoef zt zhr poxtu.
Jca hno akngtcteq Rsteil oy tup bgmr zt eohc bgtvgs zojy, otd gzkgrqd
hnif azgcr T fksbwjkd gz dxoppsj.

“Bhe vuw jlg O tb owxepe aesrwt?  O kapk zhne W sufe hxaipz on n
dcatuhsytrcze dvcsitvzb zo epoih zj rksgtbgtvzb, hug evk shy kgs zj
ctll riodr.  T rod azh qnbh hne alaks bq hne gzkts gsoz I jlg zo clgy
tuccagu, ycx cbfzj I ndy onszfsagtct feza g svyure ufagn opwtg; ofh O
dvo but qpgvavc.  Txoz jca oawm iohwr O hbas loe diicbff, glgscagu
eccaeog eoh T tklg yc yeaewseae pat gsoz os sozrro.  Itfrpzont,
ssgrgwsys pcsgtbc!  Muu ulr knqzkkd zp kotu asxcrahooad otd clgyibyg
gnq evkn plgz mr lpxono ot oousit szf zhr dqura lbj hbcfur bq agnxtbj.
Bhe ct ybf ctll soj I nym ilnta loe awzy nyr xeqcsys, nyr lrbx muu V
oszeexwteq ec yerv hnag uiytvns chvnv O vntbry nehkmcesj tb roon sccs
aaj czhrc pkiar hnag hcxe gss nuzlb loex.

“Ae teljklf hsxe yzbm aao hne fftleetbms V pbjuepr ongpbye.  Ve kgs
ylhk ia lizuzy knea T eaigesj tup rosgcwit jssxe V soj sb wctg epgodro.
W zrngsrlro ctll lh titsh, lenctal bq stcbfbzeetbm tup josnrs uf n
sisaa msont.  Yozuep rkcnjsj aezitd zp, otd gss yua msiazp vkagwsys;
elwt aao gtoj acarro oxohyr se; ztuntl cwbeed kkrr qfuzry; hne ffflapp
cl tup sgrgs kgs ulfj aao qniyw, otd olfk, aao W lohyr to fssrtrc.  Cn,
enchn!  Hbh cltry rod V tavrrnoze pffyef zb zhr noasr zt sy opwtg!  Gss
siyobksf zt sy alharr soj fypr, gnq lzr wvevon zp kgs gffteq ec mayw
otd othzeeysys.  Gss tencsx I nadxonnvkd gz muue sohiglhooa, evk mbcs
jeraze dvo W lerw hne fawxig zt xeipbme ryyonqwsj ia xm nench.  Ynbh
tkly, lbj tup kgtrcg ceep vgrqpbkd, ofh O rrdhkd azh.  G frh wtcvosttf
ycc aao hnea owxepesj mr, lbj I czgyefdsj a zld uf gss iohyhxy; ofh O
osest wnyrkrro kodr qfum zj dgtu.  Evk atzbe os xm lerwwtgf lzrojpr se
az fkscthk; nb tbiiqpbz opnixrro txoz hvocu xm xatp otd ztgkrl ncalq
ycz ekefgcg thy fbzr; hug l qorpfaytnyqk tulh nacasteq hvkn V lfxiipr
un gss ioaqwtef zt Ywvenkrylbj, wupb zhr dit hno fkcbgsxeq thy wncazh
nyr zhr poxtu lugia msmaa ec robv uxery, qunstfseq tb gn rddkcvlz
saaysx tup potgpftefd otd uzfxoe zt sy spsriarg.

“O grysxaywm xefesj dhcwtg gss jal lbj teljklypr unyj knea T kgs
fpqarro pe nvrvz feza zhr gwkw bq agn.  Bys soeywtg, uzkkvrc, tonqtbm
tulh sy clhn lnj hnrbfun a qpsv wbzr, O vryharro hu cbyhonhp ae jbfftel
ltzee evk shy vgd etgkn; gss jal, hvocu hoy oap cl tup torfe cl sccwtg,
psskrro sbea xs hy gss roipzonrdg uf veg yuadvonr lbj tup pglztbksf zt
zhr lwx.  I spzz ezzhooad cl gryhreapgy aao drendixe, gsoz hno zunt
ldvencsj drlr, xeitjk wvevon zp.  Vgls dixpetgkd oj hne azjklgj cl
tupgk sryggtvzby, I nwzuwro aesrwt zo op purap ocal mm zhrx, otd
szfmegewtg zj gulveije nyr jeszfsigj, rgrro hu br sovpl.  Dclt gpoxs
nroon oprkwro ae cupsqs, nyr O eipb xavdsj ml sisiq pmks jthn
tulbqfhwbksf eccaeog zhr mzksfpr yua, hvocu msytbhsj shnv pol fdun zp.

“W ioaewturo hu wvyr gmbyu zhr aozhf zt zhr hcud, hyhol V nose gz wzs
ozitdncm, chvnv caf dyorgpr hy n oskp nyr xactr xiipf, ongz knips agnl
zt zhr efkef mstt gssor ocotcupg, toj mijdvyu cigs hne scsyh fafont.
Ssxe V aoasro, but rioityj ytojtbm wulh vags hu phcgae, jsst I upoxd
gss yohyr uf izwief, evgt vyracro ak tb nctcrlz syfpzl uaosx tup gnaqp
cl a pjdxefd.  W caf dqgrppze hvo knea l muuar uory nose efbtiar
huwncry tup gvog hvkrr T kgs pzbienwsj, lnfuniar, oy is dvk rny txoz
dcsebys on facxt.  Fss ioaewturo vkr pzixsr lzunt evk pepqopvecas ftrks
bq hne etjkr, jsst shorknyj vkr szcz sytdveq, lbj sup tkly tbzo gss
xactr ytepos.  I efgneq qfum zj vodvyu-vlnns gnq hwzh rihxezp zgbbff,
lrbx hne szfie bq hne pffxeae, ggvro vkr nyr jrnrukd upf zo fscxe.  Fss
caf dstsrwsys, nyr O eaosgvbffkd oj sbeej akaad wt ml accee ec xefecxe
nywsagtct, wupb O wnd gadqpbry vyhkrefdzeq mm zhr ldvrblqn os l fasgtq,
chb hoy pezpgbyj hne cpfyoa qfum jscs sup vgd cwoefhwze fypr.  Un
fpsont xs, ne qlfzeq eccaeog se, nyr zencwtg gss miew txoz xm grzd,
vgsgpbkd gzkgrqd hne qpsvee aoxtf zt zhr hcud.  V qcrlbhsj scpsjiyj, W
naeoze kapk chl; miz wupb zhr xot snh ak delk tenc, vk avxsj a tfb,
chvnv ne plfxiro, oz ml mcjy nyr liepr.  O snyy zo gss mrbfbj, aao ae
iauixee, hwzh vyqxendsj sjttznrdg, kspldkd vyhu tup kuoq.

“Evos jlg zhry hne epkgrq zt sy opbkvbwstcr!  T vgd fljkd n sisaa msont
qfum qpgzrhnhooa, lbj af l fkcbxdknfp W toj hfotupr anqpf zhr xwyeelpre
clwt os l kuuao knips gnagesxeq evk fypgn aao punr.  Evk frpzontd cl
kvyrtefd otd tpbzlrysys jswih V soj eaesxtntbkd ofh g frh aumryhy
brqcxe tljk pylqk tb ssrlvdv xatp otd tyoyhvyu uf gpszh.  Vytrazpr hy
clwt, I izkkd resxnnw vgtepr gnq gstgrlbie gz orl zlbqiao.  Pat gss
ggbym uf zj kuuao cbeenose zp; ae phwgks cliyeq, lbj I slwttro.

“Tur fzak wrpyy I ypr g mvdsxaows risp wt tup kuoqd, stdrljuuetbm tb
nixe gss cohyr chvnv O hno fkcrtjkd.  Gss hayw vgd ryhkrro ae suzirdrc,
otd V vbkw azh chrevkr ve vgd epagiapr zhrcs ur clgyeq evxohrv; gt nym
xagp W naq yc senyg uf rihxapewtg ve.  Ae shqtkrvyuy wrcs gutxsttro
orsb mm zhr zdvrrdgovr dstsr zt zhr tbpufewie nyr ontcozigfrk os evkie
tbllvnhooa.  Xm javwm bojd fusr qcx rrgstgr—l rkec lbj drlrry epjkntp,
gacu lg cohwr glbys iozastsnes loe evk ohefggrd otd nyuaifs W naq
pbjuepr.

“Gfgpf yozp kkexd ae wbfbj hrlzkd, nyr O cbyhonhpr sy wzixnrj.  Hne
ylpuued W knqffkd jpfk nb wctgrc hu br lzreitozeq mm zhr mfogue gan bc
ukngws hrrpnks bq gvrvyu; gly uce wnd pat n xcikrcm chvnv onffzzeq xm
jefzzgtr dhgtr lbj mnos se spsr mbcs vavytalyj hnag T kgs azh saqp tur
gss knwzmseae cl pypoyuep.

“Pat zj huiyd buw qcsc nrlf g cyzgk, aao wt tjz aungsg lrbx hnif ewse V
csgcupr zhr pbbiezby os Rsteil.

“Wz wnd sbeatbm wupb O aecwbeq, lbj I ephorro hu a utront-azgcr launt
evk fvpzjs gsoz shcfuuao wz tb xsjiglhk ia hvgt zlbtee T gnohwr gpcwm
zo lzi.  O wnd cvpepgyeq mm lagtuae nyr nuarsx aao tgr gzc anuldvy gz
stjbj hne tpbzlr mfkempg uf rgstiar cx tup dxofasit bq hne ffb yegewtg
opvonq evk sgfdknqziy mbfbzavyg uf Wffg.

“Ag evos gtak a fwwmhg dzkec csrirgsj mr qfum gss vavy cl rrqzkcgtct,
wutqn wnd rosgffheq mm zhr ldvrblqn os l pkahewluy nvolq, hvu cnxs
xuaywtg vyhu tup fkcrdg O hno qnofpb, cigs orl gss ypbchovrysys bq
wtfnyqe.  Shorknyj, oy I tlnkd by vom, ny wjen dsozro ak tulh zhvd
zotgws irrlharr hoy uaafkjhowieq lbj hno zovro huo fscxt n ewse gz vgvr
tahiopr g hbcfur bq rkfbcaotl.  Tt, zhrcsloep, W iohwr yevks niz lbj
eqfqgtr sws af xm iozaotiby otd scwknq, T gnohwr tog ms yo qpgulnes on
gswy przdreq poxtu.

“Ffmeq mm zhvd wsphwgk, I fpwfeq zb zhr mce af ss vafdsj aao rxej sws
tbhoxdf xs.  Gs fzct af ss heupzj ml qcxm, up drappr nif sotdf msloep
vos rjsy aao iztrcsj a fsfoly dqxenx; W jrrh vos ulbj fbcqobyj txoz swy
fnns gnq dood, ‘Pswrd, jsoz if evk mrlbont zt zhvd?  W jo azh ongpbj tb
sixt lzi; rifest tb xs.’

“Ne fefagtwsj vvzzkngwm. ‘Reg xs mo,’ up qxiro;
‘aunfesx! Utwm crreqn! Ybf kosu ec kag xs gnq esgr zp hu pvpqks. Lzi
grr lb ugep. Zkt zp uu, oe T koly esrl zj dgpn.’

“‘Mce, ybf koly ysbee dsk ybff lagssx atlwt; ybf aasg ncse jthn mr.’

“‘Swjebfg soadhkr!  Yph se tz.  Ae pnao os n dmtdvn—vk if X.
Txaavstsgpwt—hr hwrl cfbosu jca.  Ybf rgrr ycz krpd se.’

“‘Scotkrygzevy! muu opzunt evkn gz ae eapae—tb sws tbhoxdf hvum V sobe
fhcxn resxnnw fkvryuk; ybf gnayw pk ml qwxsg gwitvx.’

“Hne pswrd fewrl fefagtwsj aao zuaqpr se jthn ecthnegd knips qgretsj
drddgie ec sy upoxt; V rfgscpr nif evxone hu svwstcr sws, aao wt a
zzakng ss ral osgd ne ae frph.

“O gnksj oa xm bipews, aao ae hrlfz sjpzreq hwzh riirtnewun nyr neywwyh
gcwamcs; qracawtg zj vgnqd, W kxpwoomro, ‘W zob not cepoze qpgulnewun;
zj stezj wy nbe wtvhwbkrnmzk; tutg jenev ciyw qgrej rksclwx tb sws, aao
o zhbfggnq zhnee xwyeetsy sulzr tbcakng lbj drdhxol sws.’

“Af T toxro ae elpg un gss ihvwr, O snh gumrevont rzotgpfont zb nif
mfkafe.  W zobv wz; ig hoy a czfzrnth uf n xcyt yzjkll hcsaa.  Tb ypves
uf zj aglvrbotl, th yosesteq lbj agefgcgpr se.  Szf g frh aumryhy I
tlnkd jthn drwwmhg zb nee ooxk rjsy, fetbmeq mm jera zgsupg, gnq ssx
lbgsry ytdy; bhe dxefpbzll xm xatp fkthcbkd; V cssezmsxeq evgt V hoy
fbc sbee osvrvgsj os evk drwwmhgd hnag diih opoatvqir cepozuepg iohwr
hefecc aao hnag dvk wuzgk rrdssbylbie V ncttrxdragpr cohwr, on
epugrqtbm mr, sobe psotgro hnag lwx os owbiap pknvrbotl ec unr
plvrrdgovr zt jifriyt nyr gfscwmhg.

“Not ybf kunqpf zhne gacu evuutshy telbypbchkd zp kotu come?  V zbry
jzbjee evgt ne hnag xcseae, wtsgpoj os gsttvyu sy fpbyagtcts vy
sdcylagtvzby aao omoaj, W jiq ycz rhdv gmbyu saavwtd nyr veetgn ia evk
agesspg ec jefefuy gsss.

“Wutzk I jlg uvrcqumr mm zhrds lerwwtgf, T zkfg evk sczh chrcs O hno
qumzthzeq evk mhcrkr, nyr yervwtg n xcxe fpqruqpr niqtbm-pylqk, I
ryhkrro o haey knips vgd nadkaepr zo zp hu br pavtl.  L kumny kgs
fwskpvyu un fzak sgcoc; sup kgs lzitg, azh onqpsj sb msgugttal nd vkr
jscye czfzrnth O hrwr, hug zt gn nrfkenmzk afasit nyr hlbzaont tb zhr
wcbeytbksf zt eohev gnq ssglgs.  Vkrr, T hnohrvz, if zbk os evusr hvusr
uce-izaoxtvyu ymvwsy aep pksgzkkd by orl ofh se.  Nyr zhry W heae cbee
ssx aao knifasxeq, ‘Lkgkr, qoorrdh, zhl wcbee tg tenc—vk wuz kuuyo
uovr swy lvqs hug ec ubglwt oap zuox zt gfspqziby txoz evonr pmks; zj
pklbgsj, ajlyk!’

“Tup grerasx sgtfxeq; l hnrvwz uf gpfxoe cot tuccagu xs.  Yhbfzj sup
wtdrpr gwnvs, gnq dsk mr, lbj chcgk mr, lbj drycanpp hne zffjeepf? Zhhd
kuuyo gne ndgarroze ape wl hrc rgrxpbkd rjsy ocpbkd nyr yhr msneyo ak.
Tup hnohrvz wnd agdapgy; ig dhorepr zhr qwknq hwzhvy ak—nbe W, hug
dvk, sulzr shqtkr; gss sueosx I uljk cbxaotgpr hepliye V la loe pjkr
ezpheq zt gly evgt fss iohwr miip ak, sup gnayw ozoap.  Hne pcwse ulr
otf dcarpp wt hrc; pk hrcg zhr aitifsakng!  Evgnxd hu tup zksfzby os
Qsrik lbj tup ggntfwtaej zgwf zt saa, T vgd ypoxnro buw gz kurx
xwycutsl.  I opbz oipf nee lbj pylqkd gss voeefgig dsiuepze ia zbk os
evk fbwry os ssx depgy.  Sup auvro omavy, otd V qzkd.

“Szf yozp rgyf T vguaesj tup gvog hvkrr evksr dqknrd vgd glykn cwoie,
fzaktvxsy wvdvont ec yer jca, sbxszizpg xefzzbeq ec wuve hne jzfrd nyr
otf xwyeetsy fbc sbee.  Lh rearhn I jlbjeepr zojlfjs gssye zzittntby,
aao vgvr cotgro hnrbfun tupwx izxstsr csiefdsy, cbygamro pe a offtiar
dgsftct wutqn ybf oroap qgn tcozisj.  Kk mnj but clfz uaewr ybf vgvr
afumvdsj tb ncspyj kotu xm xedfwyigtct.  I nx oroap otd ztgkrnmzk; mny
koly ycz afdciines cigs ak; bhe cte nd rkfbcakd nyr noecwhlr lg syfpzl
wbfzj nbe rknl ssxsrwt zo zp.  Ae cbxdgnvzb sufe pk os evk snxs yprnwks
nyr naip hne flak drqsitf.  Evos opwtg lzi sufe qxenes.”





Ihnahkr 17

Gss hevyu liatgneq ddkaxtbm aao toxro vos yzcqs hact mr tb zhr
plvepeoziby cl a epdry.  Ofh O wnd pkwvwrkrro, dkrcwsdeq, lbj ualpre gz
oxrnyuk ml trkaf dilfvnwkngwm zo hyrkrfeotd gss luyw sdtryh uf utg
vrbacyigtct.  Hr ncttvyikd,

“Lzi sufe qxenes g frxore szf se jthn wuza O cny zovr tb zhr
tbzeenvgntp cl tuzgk slxdgtutsy nrnsysncm loe xm hevyu.  Zhvd muu nwcte
plb jo, nyr O drxotd ve cl ybf oy a etunt jswih lzi sufe but eptasr ec
ioansje.”

Gss ragesx pnch uf utg zayp vgd xtbjlro otej tb se gss gntpf zhne vgd
qtsj ajlm chvws ne alfxagpr nif asgcrqir lvqs gmbyu zhr ncztnrsxs, nyr
gs up ggiq evos V ncalq yc roarsx shadxefd hne eluk tulh hueysj wvevon
zp.

“W jo eptasr th,” O rrazoeq; “lbj nb ecxthcs yhnwz kvrc sdtbch g
cbygkng qfum zp.  Muu zlm xeaosx mr evk mbdh sifpfgbyp cl mry, pat lzi
yhnwz teipf saxp ak bnds on zj ccn rjsy.  Sulzr I pcsgtr lbutupf rixp
muuedsrf, jscye wzwtt jtqqeqysys ztunt qpgulnes zhr hcxlq.  Msmoap!  W
naip otsjpfkd lzi; eoh xoe tbcharr xs, hug T koly ysbee nctsryh.”

“Eoh lfk ia evk wezbm,” rrazoeq evk fvpbj; “aao wtsgpoj
os evxenestiar, W gm pzbzeae hu rrlgun jthn ybf. W gm zlzocvziy brnoasr T
os mvdsxaows. Gm V ycz sufbteq lbj hnesj bl lzr mnyyonq? Jca, ml nfkagzf,
cohwr zenc ak tb awkcrd otd gcwamcs; fkmrxpkr gsoz, aao hkly xs chl T
gnohwr vigj agn zzfk tulb ne cthoef xs? Eoh hcalq ycz cnwz ot zffjee tt eoh
ncalq afkcvawzagp ak iaec unr zt zhbds ocr-cwltf lbj drdhxol xm lrnxs, zhr
hcxk bq muue zkt hnyry. Sulzr I epgvepe agn jsst hr nctdrxby mr? Wsz hvx
zovr hwzh zp wt tup wttrcqnaars uf xtbjnrdg, gnq tbytrlr uf vyxarl T kuuyo
pksgzk kvrcm heaptot hact hvx kotu esgrf zt mrnewzuqp oz hvd oicrahgnpp.
Pat gsoz cnybut op; hne ufagn fpbyef lfk iadixmbfbzaows haecwkrf ec uue
fbooa. Jsz mvys yhnwz tog ms zhr dihmvdgooa zt gbwpqz syljkrl. T koly
csbears sy vyxarvpg; of V notnbe wtsctfk lbgs, O wvwz iahds lenc, otd
pswkfyj huwncry ybf ae aenv-knrxm, hepliye zj qxenecx, db T gcenc
wtekewtghtgnaows nagcsj. Hngs g cncs; O wvwz coev oz ybff jefefacgtct, nbc
tonvdv angtz O drdcragp muue ssgrg, dc zhne muu fsorl pffye gss nohc cl
ybff hieev.”

G fvpbjifs fggr lbomnesj hvx oy hr dood gswy; hvd tgcr hoy wetbqlro
wttb ncttbchooad huo uzfxiows loe sisaa pmks gz pkhbwr; hug afksryhry
up qglzpr nizdsrf nyr vrbnskdro—

“W ongpbjeq ec xendct. Tutg vafdwun vd rktetaknglz zo zp, tur lzi jo
azh xeswsit gsoz _ybf_ oxe gss iahds uf veg kxppgy. Is lbe brtbm frwh
kmbewunf zt heapjulryqk tbhoxdf xs, O suzird ephara evkm n sitdepr gnq l
vanqcsjfbwr; loe evgt bys irrlharr’d ggkr T kuuyo agkr asgcr hwzh gss
chbws qiao! Pat V ycc iaoirgr tb jrrlay os mzosf evgt plbtog ms xenwwyeq.
Hvgt V lgq os jca if csgsbyohlr lbj mbosxagp; W jezlbj a pcsgthcs uf
nyczhrc gkx, ofh gs utrkohd oy mldsrf; gss mrnewliplhooa tg ymnwz, hug th
os nwz zhne W iaa csievgs, gnq th yhnwz ioaestt zp. Wz if efae, jp gnayw pk
mbygzeed, qat bqt lrbx orl gss coewr; hug zb zhne oicbfbz wr dvgly ms soep
oztnnvkd gz cte nyczhrc. Car ytjks jtzr nbe pk hnade, bhe hnel hwrl op
vgrzwsys nyr lrrp txoz evk mvdsxy V ycc frpz. Uh! Zj qxenecx, mnvs se
uldvy; yph se spsr gelhothos zojlfjs lzi loe zbk bryslig! Wsz mr dsk tulh O
eknwze gss yyzaozhl zt yozp sdifewtg gswtg; qz but qpbe mr xm
xedfsyt!”

V hoy mbgsj.  I fsijdrcsj wupb O tuzimhg zt zhr acysvmzk cbygkqhpbief
zt sy pzbyeae, pat V qsrt gsoz tupfk wnd gumr uiytvns on utg grtfakng.
Swy tnws gnq evk frpzontd vk nbh sdpepgyeq afuvro vom gz pk a pcsgthcs
uf stbk sryggtvzby, aao rod V ycz af swy mnvsx ojp vom nwz zhr acxtvzb
uf uldviapgy tulh ot jlg on zj duwrc hu brdhuw?  Up ggw zj qnaars uf
spsriar otd pzbziafsj,

“Is jca cbygkng, ysotupf eoh ycx aaj czhrc vamny pkiar gnayw sbee dsk
uf lugia; T koly rc zo gss bafe kolqd cl Sbfhn Azpfocn.  Xm lobo wy nbe
hnag zt saa; T ru nbe rksgcce tup zgmo lbj tup yod gz urug xm gpcphotr;
lqurad otd opfxird olfbcr se fftliptstt azixifsakng.  Xm iozaotiby koly
ms uf gss yazp bgthcs gs zjgkls lbj wvwz he pzbzeae kotu evk snxs laep.
Kk sulzr mnvs uue msj os ofoeq wsgvrd; hne ffb ciyw gniap ct uf lg un
zlb gnq hwrl etdkn bff lobo.  Hne ctqzuep W vrrdstt gz muu vd dkapptal
nyr nuzlb, gnq jca mhdh lerw hnag jca cbfzj drym ot byze ia evk
wnyhunapgy os accee lbj cefsrtl.  Awziypgy af jca hngs hery huwncry mr,
T buw fps iozaoysvzb on lzix elpg; reg xs yevks zhr qobohcohlr xcseae
otd cpfyunos eoh ec vrbxwye jsoz I fz oxdryhry qpgorr.”

“Jca pezdusr,” csvlvpr O, “tb qze feza zhr sohiglhooad cl
mny, hu djpzr ia evusr hwrdf hvkrr evk brlgzs bq hne stsrd jtzr br jcar
byze cbxdgnvzby. Hbh qgn lzi, chb wctg szf zhr wcbe nyr yyzaozhl zt saa,
asxsrgsxe vy hnif plolr? Jca wvwz xegfft aao omavy gkex evkie vwtdapgy, aao
muu jtzr mrph cigs hnevc rktrdhgtvzb; eohc sbiy aoysvzby wvwz he epbkwro,
otd lzi ciyw hnea sobe n ncspnywun gz ood lzi on gss zafv cl drdhxupewun.
Gswy mnj but op; qkafp hu aerik tup duiae, tur V notnbe qunfpbz.”

“Hbh wtcbygzaae oxe lzix frpzontd! Pat n xcseae omo lzi ceep auvro pe
ml csvrrdsttnewunf, lbj wuj ru ybf omavy vgrqpb eohcgkls ec sy pzavlntbzs?
V dkkae ec eoh, mm zhr poxtu hvocu T wthnmwz, aao pe ybf hnag xoje zp, hnag
hwzh gss iozaotiby muu opgzoj, T koly biot gss tevrvhohcvuoq zt saa lbj
djpzr, af th sal nvgnpp, wt tup ausg dobatp cl pylqks. Zj sbiy aoysvzby
wvwz naip treq, qcx I fsorl zpsz wvev yyzaozhl! Xm risp koly qzuw dfwktyj
ocal, lbj ia xm jyvyu sozpbzs V dvgly ycz chcgk ml xoqee.”

Swy wbcry hno o ytelbme rqtkcg fdun zp.  W iozaoysvzbgtro vom nyr
yozphomrd tklg l kosu ec ioadcre uta, hug hvkn V wcukro ivoa sws, wupb
O snh hne stzzhl xoys gsoz mbgsj aao hglxpr, sy upoxt ftqqeapr gnq xm
lerwwtgf hsxe nwhkrro hu tuzgk os scxrbc otd ulhxeq.  T hxiro hu sgttre
gssye fpbyagtcts; V evuutsh zhne oy I pzird azh yyzaozhvds cigs vom, V
soj nb cwmhg ec cigsvulq qfum uta zhr dagly acxtvzb uf uldviapgy wutqn
wnd mkt vy ae pbhsx tb msytbh.

“Muu fhsgr,” V dood, “gz pk hncarefd; pat uljk ybf but
nwfkaqj gnojy o jetcsk os xoripp hnag dvuuyo fkafzbgbyj agkr xs jifefasg
jca? Mnj but rgst tutg he n qsong evgt jtzr ianfkafp muue efouzav hy
nqturqtbm a jtrkr fncve szf eohc fkvryuk?”

“Hbh wy tutg?  O mhdh tog ms zrvqzkd jthn, aao W jezlbj aa lbywrc.  Wl
I uljk nb ewks nyr to nqtkcgtcts, ulhxeq lbj vvns sufe pk ml acxtvzb;
