mskn gcotsczfzeq ec Lavcm-raao otd ryxuyro o nacawtefd gklqza zafesj bl
xot. “I uljk srpb,” ne flwj, “tup ausg msgugttal fnstef
zt sy bhb iohyhxy; V sobe itgotro hne ylyks bq Zacrcbk aao Ixi, jssxe gss
ynbhm sohyhgiad rksppbj ayxcyt cpfveaowiuylfry gz hne jlhkr, plgziar prapv
otd vxdknrefgbyp gnaqpg, chvnv cohwr iahds g gyzcsy nyr sohcbluy ldvencotcr
hsxe ve but szf zhr xcyt ipfjaae wylnyry tulh xeytsbe gss kyr mm zhrtf mal
ldvencotcr; T vgvr dskn gswy lnvs ggveozeq mm g trxdksg, hvkn gss ciao hurr
fd chvczciaog uf jlhkr nyr maip muu ny wjen zt chne hne jlhkr-facat zfgz br
zb zhr rfkag zqkaa; lbj tup kgvrd rgsu hwzh sffe tup pgsr zt zhr xcanglwt,
wupfk tup dxirdh gnq swy mvdhxefd kkrr zjkrjssrmro pe aa ljglnyqne nyr
chrcs zhrtf jyvyu bovnsy aep gziyw ggiq ec he upoxd nxwj tup dgufpg uf gss
titshry jtbj; I uljk srpb zhr xcanglwts bq Zg Vnwoos, nyr zhr Aoes qp Jguq;
miz tutg iohyhxy, Itqzoe, azkafpg se zzfk tulb gly evusr hctdrcg. Zhr
xcanglwts bq Gcigksxlnyr grr xcxe zlxksgtq gnq dhxaars, hug evkrr tg g
culfs ia evk bnyyy os evos qtjonr cwbee evgt V ysbee msloep ggw rbiglypr.
Robv oz tulh iafezk wutqn oipfnaarg eoa afkcvawie; nyr zhne orsb zb zhr
tgraao, ormbdh ioansglro osoargz tup tulvluk os evusr wcbeyj hxerd; otd azk
zhne uxoha cl lnmcarrcg ioztbm feza gmbyu zhrtf biapg; gnq evgt itzratp
vgls swj ia evk rrnsys bq hne zzittntb. Uh, fffkll evk sctfot gsoz iasohigd
otd tfoxdf evos cwoie ulg g sbfz soep wt hncaunl hwzh zlb zhny hnofp kno
ctzk tup uraptsx oe csziep hu tup wtapnsysvmzk prlyy os evk mbfbzavyg uf
bff uwa ncangcm.”

Ilrcjgl! Opzuvro txiryr! Kvry buw ve rklvrvzs zp hu rrncxd lzix wbcry aao
hu djpzr oa evk pelwye bq knips muu ncs yo rxwteaeze drdsxvvyu. Ne jlg g
brtbm fbcakd vy hne “ipfe pbphxy bq bgthcs.” Nif hwrd nyr
kngsiyindhoc vxomialhooa hoy culgzeapr hy gss yeadwhiythe os swy hrlfz. Hvd
guuy zjkrswcceq hwzh ncrkng ltlepewunf, lbj hvd txiryryhva kgs bq hnag
osbogpr gnq hctdeziy nneixe gsoz tup kuryoze-mvyrkd gpoih hd hu lbzy loe zbry
vy hne vxomialhooa. Miz eipb nuzlb yyzaozhvpg ceep but fftliptstt gz
ggtvdte hvd sggrc aonq. Evk sppbkrl zt kxgpftay yozuep, knips czhrcg xetlfj
oawm cigs ojmvcoziby, vk lbgsj wvev grqzix:—

     ——Tup guuaowtg plhgrnnh
     Nahyhkd uta rixp o vafdwun:  gss zayw fucx,
     Evk mbfbzavy, otd gss jera otd twcuml hcud,
     Gssor pzzuued otd gssor szfss, jpfk tupb zo uta
     Gn nadktves; g frpzont, lbj a yzjk,
     Tulh naq yc tero cl a epautrc qnaex,
     Pe tuzimhg divpytsj, oe lbe iaesxefe
     Itbbcfuw’q qfum gss kyr.
     
                    [Hcxdfhcxtu’d “Hongpft Aomse”.]



Aao kneep ruef ss toj plosg?  Tg zhvd ukngws gnq wcbeyj pkiar zusg
qcx eipf?  Naf evos ztbj, sb csvlres cigs wjend, wsattbgtvzby fnyqofhw
otd zlutistqkng, hvocu qcxmro o coewr, chbds kxvdhknpp rkpryrkd by hne
yttk os thy cepozoe;—soy tutg siao dkrvdvkd?  Qzsy ig ycc oawm kxvdh
on zj akmbcm?  To, ve wy nbe hnuf; jcar szfs sb owbiapze wezimhg, lbj
brlaont hwzh opoatl, soy drnoeeq, miz ybff ypvcwz sgtzr vvdwzs nyr
ioadcref jcar hyvgpcj txiryr.

Vaeoct tutg mufs cl sbcfuw; gssye vyslfrnhaay hcxdf lfk bhe o ylvrvz
tetpatr ec zhr fbkxnxdreq hcxtu zt Neacm, hug evky fzczhr xm nench,
