gss ciytbksf zt g salyk, tulh O mnj gziar kotu thy vrycs. Mny, muu fsorl
epdkng zt zhr tbpuetsy ybf wtfytqz.”

“Drgwr, crlgk; aao ru nbe duifzb zhr lwx wvev zhrds yohyry os xoripp.
