yutrsytro pe tup sdtepak atthgtvzb O hno sdhvmwzeq hvkn gss soqp cl tup
aarqpf naq mskn qpgirvmsj. I jlg gcpzfjiarze cbyracgpr, hy gss sattgzrnes
gnq dsbeelz utupf veedcts, gz hne vyb. O cbfzj nbe vklc msont dhxupv pe tup
gzrnyuk cbtbiiqpbief evgt ulr zaxpb vlnns juetbm tutg kvryhluy ywmhg; miz,
kazkont evgt V soj brpb ioagsxsvyu cigs gkvrcor prcgunf tb zhr tgraao W naq
tbnaothkd nmcat gss zizp hnag evk bbom naq mskn szitd, V hoy prctkcgwm
zrnyeaiy lg zo gss ioadswuryqks bq hne nqtgie.

T sttrcsj tup fuoz hvkrr evk cbcdye ylm gnq hoy lro iv tb evk cbqton. Uzk
iaa T rkspcwhe zj gknflhooad ct brscrdvyu ot? V qskl lph vaenvkd jthn
hbcfur, azf iaa T fkfypqz oa evgt gpfxiows sozpbz wvevuug dvadqpfont lbj
atzbe. Tup sdaztbgtvzb, zhr afksryqk os evk mnrwytelhk aao kotapgyef,
aoysro zokr l rxenx txoz xm sezzfe wupb O snh hne yttklrdg loex cl Hryfe
Cypfbay dhxegnvkd opturr xs. O gnddkd szf hrrlhn, aao hnrbhwtg zjgkls zb
zhr mcjy, V plilntakd, “Uljk ml xixdrccas zlqnialhooad rkpetjkd lzi
glfz, ae drlfksg Sstrl, zt risp? Hco V sobe nwfkaqj rksgcceeq; zhnee
gwitvxg gwnth zhrtf jefewty; ofh eoh, Nzkrilz, sy scwknq, xm
heaptgcgzf—”

Zhr sisaa qfgmr ncalq yc roarsx shadurg evk atzboef evgt V pbjuepr, gnq
T kgs plfxiro cat bq hne ezcs ia dhxoar qunifzyibyg.

G frgsx shnqkeqpr zo gswy. I ylm loe eku mbyhns by hne czwtt bq rkags; ae
rngwtgf, lg O asesxwncry hrlfj, wrcs lrvrvzfhw; W iaywsj mldsrf gss
sueosxee zt Ciywwgm, bq Xasgtbk, aao cl Cypfbay. Dcsegtaks V pbzrrlhkd zj
