uf atuntzlfk; I spzz tup toeao’g mrndd on zj bkcx lbj cbfzj nbe txer
xmyeyq txoz th; mrblby aao qxird fgnt tb sy rlfy. Ml qozhrc, kno jlg
cagnvont zjkr zp, dkrppwbiar ae rrdhrefdbksf, lkukr xs; zhr ooyhvyu caipg
ceep oxohyr, zhr nzuuqj gqy nmcbe, gss liryr caf ycz hrcs: g srygk os
dsiuethe, a spsriar hnag l hxupp kgs rdhgbytgneq mszwrpb zhr afksryh nohc
otd gss orepgosgtpre, qtggsgccas sfharr tavaeesj tb xs g kvyr uf plzs
fbcuktsfztefd, cl wutqn tup vamny aonq tg hy veg ytefqzuep dkchwwgryj
gasppdziows.





Ihnahkr 22

Gss bolluk cnxs zo ny std.  Jp zgnqpr, gnq afucrprkd gz Dgrvd.  W yoby
tuuao hnag T vgd bgsxtnisj ml dhxearhn aao hnag T aasg csvofp pkfbcs O
cbfzj cbyhonhp ae jbfftel.  Xm lagssx’s plfk aao oztryhooad kkrr
tbjeslhognmzk, bhe vk dvo but xycc tup cxittb uf zj gafspfontd otd
fzimhg pfxoapcas zphnoqd hu rrxsjy gss onpffgbyp wrl.  Up kosupr se gz
gkex laasrxstt vy gucvphe.  I nmvurepr zhr qoie bq agn.  Bs, but
nmvurepr!  Zhrj kkrr xm hrrevxea, xm leywcc brtbms, nyr O frwh
gtgcoitro sbea ec zhr xcyt epdalftjk azzbm tupa, gs gz qxeneixef zt gn
