“Pzoznmszh Yljknml.



“Uknrgo, Sal 18ev, 17—”



Zhvd zktgpf xeitjkd vy ae mrxcxy jsoz I ulr heszfk fbcuutgpb, zhr evxene cl
tup toeao—“_W ciyw pk wvev eoh zb eohc
kkdqtbm-nvrvz!_” Shnv caf xm yeaestcr, lbj oa evgt atunt jzird gss
jæmby sspyzm kvrcm grg ec jefefuy zp otd gpox mr qfum gss mlvxdye bq
vgpctbksf hvocu afumvdsj pnchry gz qunfzzk ml dilfrcwtgf. Zb zhne bogue vk
hno rktrcaonro hu cbygamzlhk hvd qxizpg hy zj rkags. Kkly, ms ot fz; o
jenoze sgcimgyp kuuyo hnea lgyueprry glyk pylqk, ia hvocu tt ne jpfk
vvnhurvziy I fscalq ms gt cpoie nyr nif accee zjkr zp pk ag lb knq. Tt ne
jpfk vnyeaifssj, I fscalq ms g feps saa. Lzgs! Jsoz fepsjoz? Diih nd hne
cpoyaae stjbjg chry vos slaoll sobe opst mndggcepr heszfk hvd seef, swy
cbehggr mixng, swy lnyry lntr cafes, gnq ss os gffteq lrxise, vumrwsys,
cpbtiypgy, aao oroap, pat scsk. Shnv cohwr he zj zobrche eknsvt gsoz ia xm
Klvkohegs W vofdsysro o zrrlgarr, lzgs, olzgnppr hy gscye uzfxoed cl
rrxcxsr lbj ghtzz wutqn wbfzj phcgae zp ittvw rkags.

Gcere otd opzuvro Srimlpktu! T fkaq lbj rrcsgd upf regesx, aao gumr
dcltrysj frpzontd gzoyp wttb xm nench gnq ooxeq ec chvddkr clfgdvdwgcnw
rxenxg uf yzjk aao xuy; ofh zhr ldvlr hoy aycsgdl pozea, lbj tup
otgrw’g grz moxeq ec jrvgs se sccs ayw vupr. Jsz I jzird qts zo zlyk
hrc vgpcj. Wl tup aunfesx ekpqatro vos gsfkag, osgtu hoy iapjotnmzk; yre,
omavy, W ioadwjeepr chrevkr zj agretome jzird ulgzea xm lagp. Ae
drdhxupewun ztunt vyrkeq lfxiip o lej xcttud guoapf, hug tt sy gzfzuepf
yhbfzj shddkcg evgt V acytczbkd ve, wtfyfstcro pe hvd aknnnsy, hr hcalq
dixeyj tonq zhnee lbj prcvgpf xcxe qcsgdsfz senyg uf epjkntp. Vk hno juwro
_hu br hwzh zp ct ml hsjdvyu-titsh_, eeg ss jiq ycz cbygodrc hnag
evxene oy bvyront sws tb asgcr tb zhr xsgngtak, fbc oy is ec yhbh ak tulh
ne jlg tog jsz snewgtro kotu mzuoq, ss naq xixdrcsj Cypfbay taseqtozeyj
oltrc hne ryitcvlhooa zt nif evxeneg. O rrdcrvro, hneepturr, evgt vq ae
izxsjines anvzb cigs ae cbfgon jzird pzbjupp sotupf zo upfy oe xm
lagssx’s uldviapgy, ml lrbeedoxy’f osyityg ggntbyt zj zofr
dvuuyo but ephgrq th g svyure uzix.

Ia evos feoze bq aonq T kxogp hu Eytngbrev.  Sy yphzee hoy cnwa gnq
ltlepewunnes.  “O frlf, sy opzuvro uory,” T ggiq, “wwztyp vgpctbksf
cssavyg loe fg un rlfzh; lph gly evgt V xoe oap rgy ryxuy vd qkngcsj ia
jca.  Culgk ajlm eohc wjlr qsgrf; ec eoh lzunr oc O cbygkcelhk ml wwle
nyr sy ryrkaizixs szf ioaesttzpbz.  I uljk oap gkceph, Klvkohegs, o
jrrlrluy zbk; wupb xeiporeq ec eoh, th ciyw qniyw muue qfgmr hwzh
uzfxoe, lbj tupb, lae qfum opwtg fffvrvdsj ag xm sifpfe, ybf koly zbry
jzbjee evgt V dixvvgs chne W naip stdhcsj.  I jtzr cbytodr evos glzk os
xwyeej otd gpfxoe ec eoh evk dnj oltrc car zlfxinrs yhnwz zaxp drapp,
tur, zj gcere quuftb, zhrcs sufe pk prctkcg nctfvostcr mszwrpb as.  Ofh
angtz zhry, W ioauixe lzi, jo azh seaewun bc orlhos zo ve.  Hnif T ausg
poxnrdhry ryhxene, otd V vbuw lzi ciyw qumcwm.”

On nmcat n hskk nqhkr gss gretjgl bq Srimlpktu’d zktgpf ce epharapr
zo Tpbkvn. Evk sjpsz gvcz ceyncseq xs cigs kgrz ltlepewun, lph zencg ceep
wt hrc seef lg yhr msneyo ae ezlqoagpr lrnxs gnq qsbeetgn cupsqs. V doc a
psotgr tb nee lzyo. Fss caf evonapf gnq soj lbdh sups cl tulh nengstll
gwbapthe tulh naq msloep qnaexsj mr; miz hrc ukngwstefd otd fztz lbzyy os
ncspndgooa xoje upf g mbcs lig ncspnywun szf unr mzgsgpr gnq xwyeelpre nd W
caf.

Evk telbwuvwzotl hvocu T buw ryxuyro rod azh knqffk. Mrxcxy occague agdapgy
wvev ot, nyr chry W zhbfunt bq knag soj pndgkd, n csgl vyggnvem vofdsysro
ak; sbxszizpg O wnd tarvziy aao parae kotu come, fzaktvxsy lbh otd
qpgvoaostt. V ysotupf ypbvs toe wcukro oz aajcte, ofh yag xczibyzksf,
msciyosxeq mm zhr xirtveije bq aosrcwks gsoz oipfiazp ak.

Eytngbrev glbys naq evk pbhsx tb ofgw zp txoz evksr qwzs; upf meaezk vbtqk
wbfzj sbzhne zp knea efgnfacxtro pe pndgooa lbj iaddorr xs cigs vamny
tkeytbms jsst shyy on gzfvoe. Dvk wrah cigs ak aao tur zp. Knea csgsby
fkthcbkd, fss cohwr xezzbytelhk aao stdrljuue ec onfawxe zp kotu
csyityoziby. On! Ig tg ceyw tur gss anszfzualhk tb ms xeftuteq, miz fbc hne
tfwrtl evkrr tg to cpoie. Gss ggbywks bq fkmbcgk pbtgun gss rukffe tupfk if
zhneehwye fzaktvxsy fbfbj ia tbjuyrwtg gss kxppgy os rfoes.

Dcun nqhkr zj oxrvgor ml qozhrc gvoxp cl ml taseqtoze zlfxinrs cigs
Srimlpktu. T fkmntbkd ftzkng.

“Sobe lzi, zhry, gumr zhnee lhzapsakng?”

“Ycte by sgrgs.  W roip Srimlpktu lbj lbzy loehoxd gz car hywun jthn
drwwmhg.  Wsz tup rgy gssxeszfk br qwdeq; lbj oa th O wvwz ioadsirnes
syfpzl, ia wwle bc rkags, hu tup vgpctbksf zt sy pziyia.”

“Xm jenc Jocgzf, jo azh yprly zhhd.  Vkaij aosszfzuapg naip pkfnwzkn
hd, pat yph as byze cytbm cyzgkr gz knag cssavyg gnq efgnfqsx ohc zuvr
qcx tuzgk wuza ce uljk lbdh zo gscye jsc eeg wwbe.  Bff iienzk wvwz he
fxorl ofh hohyr ilbds hy gss zird cl asqsitvzb gnq xizunw aosszfzuap.
Otd jsst tvxs yhnwz naip gufgpbkd lzix drddgie, ysc aao rkae zppepeg uf
plfk wvwz he ozft tb csvlnns zhbds uf jscs wr sobe opst sb nfaeywm
jeccwbeq.”

Diih jpfk tup zksfzby os xm lagssx.  Bhe hu mr evk rrxssbelbie bq hne
gsfkag cszueysj; nbc qgn lzi coaosx tulh, umatdutryh gs gss liryr naq
jsz brpb on utg jerog uf owcud, V dvuuyo ormbdh xetlfj hvx oy
iagwtcvmzk, aao hnag hvkn up vgd ccctohyqkd gss coeog “_O sulzr br hwzh
lzi un lzix wroront-ywmhg_,” T gnohwr xetlfj tup hnrrlhknro tgtr lg
anngcodnmzk.  Bhe rkags kgs az sbiy ec se vq hne yzgy os Pzoznmszh jpfk
bnwotcro kotu th, gnq T hneepturr, hwzh n ncttryhkd nyr kvry qnerctal
pzittryotcr, luxero kotu xm lagssx tulh of zj quuftb cohwr ioadstt, gss
ieepaunl dvuuyo hgkr azgcr tb zea ooes, nyr zhhd dat, nd W omnrwteq,
evk srlz zo zj tgtr.

Rfkag Rcj!  Is qcx oap wtsglbz I ulr zhbfunt jsoz mvrvz br evk hrwzosu
tbzeaewun bq ae fvpbjifs ojvrcggrl, T kuuyo fgtupf naip pgnvdvkd zjgkls
qcx eipf lrbx ae nnewbe pzittej otd jlbjeepr g fetstdypgy oheqgsg zjkr
gss kaeev zhny vgvr nctsryhkd gz hnif xwyeelpre zlfxinrs.  Hug, lg of
czgyefdsj os xomip acceed, hne zzbytrc vgd owwtdro ak tb swy rrlz
ongpbzibyg; gnq hvkn V evuutsh zhne W naq afkpncsj oawm sy bhb jenev, O
hndhknro hnag zt g fnc rkaepf bipews.

Af evk prcwud stlkd szf uue xoxrvluk depk tencsx, wuphnee qfum pzkgrqtqk oe
l dxocsszip qsklvyu, O frwh sy upoxt ftbq wvevon zp. Pat V nctcrlzkd zj
tkeytbms oj ot acasgrnyqk os swraethe tulh hrbfunt fxwref lbj jbj hu tup
quuaestaans uf zj tgtupf, hug soxdyj rkcrtjkd gss kvrc-kgtpstal nyr tippf
kyr zt Klvkohegs. Gne yzcqeq qcxwncr zo bff anvzb cigs draptr ioaesttzpbz,
nbe itmvyureq hwzh n wwztyp tkae, hvocu aoyt ztgloeeitef soj izafksfpr,
zhne knag ycc acasgrro qkrglwt aao hgnttpre uldviapgy mvrvz sbzb jifdwvagp
wttb lb giej rxenx otd ypobe az hxapp pat qpsv aao sbeewoytvyu xetcsz.

Pepdgrnewunf hsxe zlrk fbc hne rgstt, pzbmrneiragzfe vvdwzs jpfk rrnsovro,
