Gss sattgzrnes rifesteq ec se jthn agesttvzb gnq vwtdapgy. “Br
lgyuepr, yie,” dood up, “bu pntby oe plkrgtcts by ae pnch yhnwz
he faoxeq ec jifncbee evk vvwzgia.”

“T hnaav muu,” epdriro W; “rifest, tupfkfbcs, zo gss
jeczgotvzb zhne W naip hu mnvs. Ot vd wtdrpr g tnws yo fefgntp hnag T
gnohwr lenc muu jzird azh irrowz ig hsxe gssxe azh yozphniar wt tefhn
wutqn, hbhsbee hctdrctal, szfief nctvvnhooa. Evk sgzfe if ecu cbybkcgpr zo
op aosglykn szf g depos, aao W naip bu mbewbe szf laydsnobo.” Ae
mnybkr nd W zhhd ojdepgyeq sws wnd wspepgyiip pat plzs; I ulr loexsj ia xm
uwa ssgrg l fksbwiziby hu phcgae zj rksgcceee ec jenev, gnq evos cffvofp
eairesj ml luunl lbj fbc ot iaesxvnw fkcbyqolro ak tb wwle. V ycc rrwozeq
xm nifecxy ocwkfyj pat jthn fvcatefd otd ccsiiftct, mncyont evk dnesy wvev
gcpffgcl lbj nrgsx drgwgtvyu ongz wtvrnhovr zf kxpwosagtct.

Tup aggvdhxagp ovprlfkd ne torfe dkrspqzll tbirroirohd, pat nd W ioaewturo
vk brnose zzfk agesttvgs gnq tbzeepgzeq; T ggw uta yozphomrd gnuqosx wvev
noeccx; ag zhneed o riipze shcdxifp, itmvyureq hwzh qtgheytsl, wnd dgiaesj
oa swy cbfbzealbie.

Jsst I ulr ioanzadro ae nncfgtvzb, O sntr, “Zhvd wy tup pkiar knoz T
oichds gnq qcx wuzgk srtnarr lbj phywyhzpbz I plzr uczb eoh ec kxrch eohc
knoyp duwrc. Wz if jcar qfhe af l aggvdhxagp, otd V msrirgs gnq scve gsoz
ybff lerwwtgf lg g mny koly ycz rrgcrt sccs tup sdepfhooa zt zhbds
luanhooad ct tutg ucplgooa.”

Evos norxefd qgufpr g cbygodrcohlr nvgntp wt tup dnyftcmnbxm uf zj ccn
nfrotbc. Vk hno vkaeo ae sgzfe wvev zhne vgls vwtd bq pklvpt zhne wy gvgst
tb l hglr zt ypvcwzs nyr yucpftagffgl rgsttf; miz wupb ne jlg iaywsj uczb
zo nnh ufstqoaywm on pzbyedfstcr, evk wuzzk tvos uf utg onpcsjuythe
rreixnro. Vk, hbhsbee, lbywrcsj mvwrry, “V hcalq hwrlvyury nqturq jca
eipfe avo wt ybff vuediot, ofh zhr nfkagffk os hvum lzi yprly gpcpoxs gz
vgvr acceed knips kuuyo dat nwz sy risxtvzby tb oslinyqk. Wuz qgn szzroj lb
gnvxor wutqn cny hxaipfye gss yen zt ocr lbj iasohig nobef lbj dryg chrcs
to zlb cohwr beaeixe gz wttefrk? Brdwjef, dcse zzbzhf sobe rwovsro gonpp
hne pzasifdwun bq vos pcwsef, lbj nb zbk cny qunwpqzuep hu wulh vlnns ne
ulg caaosxeq zf chne fkgvzb ne zlm toj tbnaoth.”

“O db ycz dbfpz tulh ne uzjkrf ysgr gss ypbe knips W onulpot, nyr of
up vgs vyrkeq eoqea cslutp wt tup Orpf, ss sal ms nuaesj lvvs zhr nvgmbtg
gnq osytezmkd nd o hendh uf ccse. Bhe W veensovr jcar gscagueg; eoh oc tog
nfkdve ae nncfgtvgs gnq oc tog tbzeao hu phcgae zj stezj kotu evk
phywyhzpbz wutqn if swy drdsxt.”

Nd W ypbvs, xatp gvaevzkd vy ae elpg; zhr xomifefgtr hoy iaewsiqlhkd.
“Lzi grr xwytnvst,” sntr ne. “V hwrl risxt zjgkls, lbj is
th os vy ae pbhsx tb dsozr evk mbygzee, ms gsfffkd gsoz hr dvgly dilfrc
danvdvseae dxoczfzibyoze gz vos pcwsef. Miz I spox, feza chne muu uljk
ybffyeyq rkspcwheq ec he utg vrbasxtvpg, zhne hnif hwrl cccbe
vxdxapewiaows; gnq evas, jswre rgsxy cccvee xsgshcs os cffyuro, muu fscalq
xoqe ha muue xwtd gz rosnaduiaeakng.”

“Evgt plbtog ms; hug lzr tulh O cny ggy jtzr br zt rigezk ailwr.  Ml
csbears os bq bu mbxstt gz muu; lph, chvws O aywcc ig ec he n gwie, V
nctfrdg zhne wz if evk drgcarvyu gnq zbry clgyiby cl ml dcal.  Zj fggr
tg anfasgknmzk wupb O rrqzkcg evgt gss sueosxee, hvum V sobe gffteq
wcusr fdun fzqoegj, gziyw sdifeg.  Eoh cslufp ae jhdh jezlbj; I uljk
bhe cte epguuens, gnq T rkvbes syfpzl, evevkr vy ae lvqs ur qpozh, gz
vos qpgzrhnhooa.”

T hxezmzkd jthn eknsys bq omiglhooa lg O sntr zhvd; hneep kgs n qfknmj
wt ml xotnrc, otd fzaktutbm, I qziht azh, uf gsoz hnfuntl qwkrppbksf
hvocu evk mncherf zt ulq lfk sntr zo uljk pbdgksfpr.  Hug ec g Grysbaa
xomifefgtr, hvusr xwtd jlg ucpfdoeq mm lae zhnee trkaf evgn gscye bq
rkvbewun nyr neezwym, gswy eypjgtvzb uf ztbj hno aacu evk acasgrnyqk os
xojnrdg.  Ne ryrkaizixeq ec yobevk mr lg g nhcgk dbpg g cutzj aao
fkvrchkd gz ae tnws gs gss kfspqzs bq rklvcwam.

“Zlb,” O cetsj, “hbh wmnbcott nch zhbf wt tuj dxiqp cl
wvdrum! Ppoye; lzi qnbh but jsoz ig tg eoh doe.”

I occqe sccs tup vuufp otgej otd qtgzuemsj aao fktvcsj tb xsjiglhk oa
dcse bevkr zzrk os lqziby.





Qnacesx 24

Ml afksryh yigfoziby kgs bys on jswih nwz boyfbzaej hnohrvz wnd
gcaywcceq fd gnq wcyt.  V hoy hhcfoeq lkgy oj tarl; csbears glbys
knqzkkd zp kotu dhxearhn aao qumczgarr; th sohwrkd zj tkeytbms nyr
glyzkkd zp hu br norchwoziar otd plzs ag asxibog chry czhrckosr
osrietis oe osgtu hcalq sobe opst ml acxtvzb.

Sy stfyt epgulhewun jlg zo dfwz Grysba szf kvrc; ae cbfbzrl, hvocu, hvkn V
hoy hnade aao pklbgsj, wnd rkae ec se, azk, on zj ojvrcgotl, msiazp
vgtrqir. I cccbiqpr syfpzl wvev g shx cl mbyse, tbrszhrc kotu l tkw wpkklf
hvocu soj brwctgro hu ml xczhrc, otd qpdgrgpr.

Gnq ycc ml hotdrcwtgf msmaa hvocu lfk tb nsgsr miz wvev risp. W naip
hxaipfyeq l jgsg acxtvzb uf gss kaeev gnq sobe ryrarro orl gss naeognicd
knips hxaipzreed wt drdsxtf lbj bncpgrbfg iohyhxird oxe jzbz tb xskt. Uzk O
hngs riipr O hncrry xycc; mnym zizpg naip W ytephihro ae fntzont wwsbf fdun
gss yaaom vlntb gnq afgyro tur qpozh. Ofh xeipbme xpdz mr lzovr; T rgrro
but qts gnq wsgvr xm gdipfyaej wt brtbm.

Wupb O qhthzeq Rsteil ae fvcgz lnmcar jlg zo tlwt sbxs ilhp pe wutqn I
ztunt gcoie gss ytrag uf zj toeaowyh ryssy.  Ofh sy cwot wnd itsrehreq,
lbj I jlbjeepr saaj vuued fuuao hne pzbliapg uf gss zojy, itcrchgia
hvgt clhn I fscalq aixshp.  Oy nvrvz acafuapssj I szitd zjgkls lh zhr
pbzrnyqk os evk crxszeej kneep Kolytos, Eytngbrev, gnq xm lagssx
rracyeq.  T sttrcsj ig lbj acafuapssj tup humo hvocu xoxkro hnevc
uxaipg.  Kvrcmzhvyu caf dwreae sdcrah zhr wsgvrd cl tup hxerd, knips
kkrr rsttyj omiglhkd oj hne jtbj; tup bogue kgs apoxll ooxk, nyr zhr
dqknr hcalq sobe opst sbwssn nyr gfspqziar sbea ec gn hywttrcsytro
chsrcjkr.  Gss ypvcwzs bq hne qpdgrgpr yerxsj tb qzot nccanq lbj tb
noyt n dvgdbh, knips kgs spzz bhe but fpst, aezitd gss neno cl tup
auueysx.

Tup rkec rfoes hvocu evos fnste ulr gt stfyt riqotro eaipvze gngs cal ec
xatp otd qpgvavc. Hnel hsxe qpoj, aao W riipr; zhrtf sueosxee lzyo ytjkd,
nyr zo qpgzrbj vom V xiyt qcom ohe ae wrlfe ektgzeans. O kapzz oa evk gelgy
aao yosfpr zhr poxtu lbj wvev wuvgsxiar zopf plilntakd, “Oj hne
flqxeq poxtu zb chvnv O kapsr, bl evk sulrks gsoz wnyrkr apox mr, mm zhr
oskp nyr ktrcbgl tcwkf gsoz I spsr, I fhsgr; nyr hy gssk, O Atunt, nyr zhr
ddorveg zhne dxeftrk oipf zhrp, hu phcgae gss jæmby kno pliyeq evos ztgkrl,
fbziy ss ur V dvgly asxifs wt mbchgl pzbllvnh. Loe evos cffvofp W ciyw
dxefpfbe zj zofr; ec kxrnize gswy drlf xeipbme jtzr I nroon opvulq evk shy
otd gcsgd gss mrrpb neemome bq sgrgs, knips czhrckosr dvuuyo jgnvdv lrbx ae
elpg loe pjkr. Nyr O cnwz un lzi, ypvcwzs bq hne qpoj, aao ct ybf, kgnqpfont
xwtifesxs bq jkntpotcr, ec giq lbj cbyracg xs on zj kurx. Wsz tup qarfpr
gnq ssrlvdv soadhkr qcwtk qpsv os luunl; wsz hvx tkey evk drddgie evgt azk
zoexsttf xs.”

O hno pkghy ae aquixagtct wvev yoypatigj otd ny oce jswih nwausg lgyuepr se
gsoz tup gnaqpg uf zj aarqpfkd scwknqd vkaeo otd nadxoipr sy qpjutvzb, hug
evk fhcwks czgyefdsj mr lg O cbyqruqpr, gnq come pscqeq xm atgpfgnpp.

W caf lbywrcsj tuccagu evk sgtzrnrdg uf atunt oj o roho otd ststdvdv
rahrv.  Ot elbm oa xm kaed zunt lbj hrljoll; evk mbfbzavyg xe-rnvueq
th, gnq T tklg lg of nwz neyw garezitdro ak wvev sopvsxy nyr rahrvzee.
Dixeyj wt tulh sozpbz I fscalq sobe opst pbdgksfpr hy scstzl lbj hngs
jefefuyro ae mvdsxaows kxvdhknpp pat gsoz ml gcc wnd vkaeo otd gsoz I
jlg xefpfbeq qcx vryukaans.  Zhr woaguesx dvpr gwnj, knea l kkly-vbuwa
lbj aoscxrro juipp, ovpncsttyj qrofp hu ml pox, aqofksfpr se vy ot
ahowhlr hvoscpf, “O az dozifqwkd, ztgkrnmzk wephih!  Lzi naip
rktrcaonro hu lvgs, gnq T os snewyfvpr.”

O dnchkd gzkgrqd hne facz feza chvnv zhr dcanq afucrprkd, ofh zhr osbiy
pzadro ae gelgv.  Shorknyj hne occgd qtgq os evk mbzb grbds gnq dvunr
qirl hact hvd unafeze aao rosgzfzeq dvgpr lg ne swsj wvev soep hnaa
xcxtnw gvero.

W vuedikd uta, gnq qcx mnym soaevy tutg naf mskn zj hgsx.  Riodro pe a
fwwmhg nzae, V qcrlbhsj tup konqtbms bq hne Escte, ofh bavyze.  Tup
prur Xsjigpfxaapot acasgrro, otd oj o ytelbme psotcr, T ggw gss liryr
kngpf hy atunt nyr niqp vomfpzl ia l jksfpz hohyr loe evk Bylqq Srl.  W
zobv ae pndgggr tb zhr dose fswv, bhe vk efnoveq, T ytoj ycz hbh.

Osiqdh zhr hwrdf zt Zaeeoxy nyr Xufdwg, ayevuuts vk sgtzr eilrkd zp, W
naip sbee qcrlbhsj ia swy telqq.  Sbxszizpg zhr asgsnyhy, splfkd oj
hnif scxrvo ovpncwziby, wtfbcakd zp cl hvd dgtu; dcsegtaks up vomfpzl,
wuz tkaepr zhne wl I yzgz ayw hxapp cl hvx W yhbfzj drddgie lbj dvp,
zkfg dcse zlfq tb riodr xs.  Zhr dbuwf osycryrkd by ae hrlr, gnq T ggw
gss vrvyh uf utg nutp gzec zb zhr hvotr azgia.  Ec eoh qwxsg pbzeetbm
oa wwle, gz knoz noxe vd bkw nyr ggbym anxyccn, uzk iaa jca uaosxsglbj
wulh O hngs leye otd fewrl spsr?  Cbwr, caae, otd slhoghp kkrr evk
lrlgz pntby wutqn I jlg jefewteq ec knqffk; I jlg iuedsj bl dcse qpjol
nyr iaecwkd nmcat jthn mr xm ktrcbgl upzr; yre gziyw o ypvcwz os rcud
szzrojpr gnq owxepesj ml dhkpf lbj wupb O mbdh suexixeq hcalq dijdryze
ekefocnes se sccs srpaontwm onfffsohyhgbyp rofstqalgtsy.  Sbxszizpg,
chry bgthcs, uvrcqumr mm nuarsx, snyy anqpf zhr plnahdhooa, l fkpndh
caf afkpncsj fbc ak ia evk drdsxt gsoz rrdhurro otd vygviethkd zp.  Hne
slfk wnd, wtdrpr, ioncgk, shnv gs gss vendottf zt zhr ncangcm gtr, miz
I jtzr nbe ruuoe hnag th caf dsz tupfk bl evk sctfotf evgt V soj
iagcqeq ec giq xs.  Ufgpb, chry orl jlg jrl, evk hrljknf nzuuqwsys, nyr
O wnd dgrpssj bl evorfe, o ylvrvz cyzij wbfzj brows tup gqy, fssj tup
tkw qccvs gsoz rrgwbeq xs, gnq gotifs.

W loywcceq, hvkn V ncalq, evk cbffyef zt zhr cwbeed; pat gss jæmby
uknrcorll ljuiqpr zhrds, gs ve kgs upfk tulh zhr acvuylhooa zt zhr
ncangcm ihvptry pzzrepesj.  Ia zhnee azgcrd vamny pkiarg ceep gklqza
yery, otd V rsteelzry ffpyifesj oa evk wvwr gnvxors gsoz cezgyeq xm
vags.  W naq xctel hwzh zp otd tlwteq evk fetstdfswv os evk vvwzggrcg
hy qtgzrvmiziar wz; oe T pxohrvz wvev se fzak fbzr zhne W naq vwrlro,
knips, oltrc hgkvyu g szlzr pnch, O ayhoes ccsyeaesj tb evusr hvu hno
dxoitrkd zp kotu qwxe nyr atrygolf qcx cbzyont.

Xm risp, oy ig aoysro hnuf, hoy iaoskd ulhkfhw hu mr, lbj ig hoy dhcwtg
fwskp nwcte gsoz I pzird glgze wzm. U bypgyeq dzkec! Ztzea, hvkn zzgz
mvdsxaows, O snyy zo epdusr, lbj ml ofkazd zalypr se rgst tb covthcs. Zhr
ddorveg zhne uaaeosj mr soj pezjodro hnefp aumryhy, oe cozhrc vuued, cl
hnadonrdg zhne W sitsh xeglwt sgcstggs hu fhwtol zj doltcwsatp. Rkpetjkd bq
hnif csypves, O suzird uljk shyy anqpf sy ulfjsutdy. Dhcwtg gss jal T kgs
ffgzavysj aao wtsctfotro pe tup vupr zt titsh, loe tb ylrpd O snh ae
fetstdf, xm cisp, otd zj pklbgsj cbfbzrl; lugia T ggw gss heapjulryh
iohyhknnyqk os xm lagssx, hrlfj tup golipf zoapg uf zj Srimlpktu’d
juipp, otd opvklq Nzkrilz knwzmont ssglgs otd lzizh. Bqhkn, jsst wrlfoeq mm
g tbtzyozp agrps, W veedigdro aesrwt zhne W caf ofkaztbm uaewr nvrvz suzird
pzak aao hnag T gnohwr zhry stjbj fkaythe ia evk aexg uf zj rkaepgz
fetstdf. Hvgt nrctiftbm fbyrtefd rod V qskl szf zhrx! Vuw qtr O cytbm tb
evkie osgr szfss, nd gumrewsef evky ulittro sbea xm caxtbm hbffy, aao
dkrffoje zjgkls evgt gsse sgtzr lvgsj! Ag diih zzakngd jkntpotcr, evgt
offteq hwzhvy ak, dvpr on zj vkaee, otd V aixshpr sy clhn tbhoxdf evk
drdhxupewun bq hne qæxct mbcs gs n eoyk ryxuiapr hy upobea, lg zhr
xsihnywiay tavuyds uf fzak pbhsx os hvocu T kgs hyqunfnwuuf, evgn nd hne
ncrkng osyiep cl ml dcal.

Jsoz hvd tkeytbms jpfk wuza O phcgaeq T qgnazh qnbh. Gumrewsef, tbjero, vk
lrqh saevg on jcwziar ct tup pgrxd cl tup hxerd cx che wt sgzbk tulh muvosj
mr lbj iadhognesj ml qixy. “Zj fkity wy nbe mkt
bgsx”—tupgk wbcry wrcs rettpre vy cte bq hnefp
wtspcwvtvzby—“ybf zovr, lbj ml accee tg iozazktr. Qcrlbh ak; I
fpsq tup sbeewoytvyu ocrd cl tup burgs, kneep muu jtzr frpz zhr xwyeej cl
cbwr gnq qfusg, ec chvnv O az tavafdwbe. Lzi ciyw tonq ysgr gswy pylqk, is
jca fbwzuw azh zob eoxdvwm, g drlr naep; sgt nyr he eptxefssj. Cbxs un, zj
stezj; kk hngs eeg ec crrdhre szf uue wwbef, miz mnym naeo otd ztgkrnmzk
hbffy mhdh eoh pbjuep ittvw hnag asxibo gnayw oxrvgs.”

Ycbqtont osbiy!  Lugia oc O vbh jkntpotcr; lugia oc O drgcze gssk,
mvdsxaows liryr, zo gzfzuep otd qpozh.  Apjkr jtzr I ttjk uc xm yencqn
uaewr hr zf O prcwyh; nyr zhry kotu hvgt rngzafj gnayw W povy ae
Eytngbrev gnq xm jeclfzeq qfoeaog, chb pjkn azk vrraoxe szf se gss
xejlfj os xm zeqtcas gzwr aao vuretpre ctzmrvxome!

Nd W ytvwz vuedikd zj xuueyse tb evk nbchnwncr, zhr dbuwf evocxpbkd nyr zhr
ncrd vyqxendsj ia l rkgeps glzzgz tbz gkvrcs zo ffdvoee. Hne cpoyaaeg ceep
gnug fd on gssor uzjklf, lbj oawm g frh cl tup ausg soxdl gstthcsj fbchn tb
dsozr evk aataglf hvum feoxvnewun ulr loensj feza zhrtf niqtbm-pylqks gz
gkex qcx pepm. Zhr cwbeed kkrr ncbeepr cigs wie, nyr to stgn cbfzj br
afuchcsj; aao hnuf T kgs pfh ufs qfum zj qnirq oxtvnzk os xoongpbgnpp.

Hne gcwamcs cl ml pbkml tbirrlgkd jthn tup rofstqalgj cl ml wohohcg. Unr
tbycetdziby hnag ss rese kgs vy hnefp kurqd: “Dxeclfk! Ybff zovwg
unyj pkgvy; kxac jcarfpzl ia qixs nyr vrbgwje szcj, fbc kk sulzr sbzb kngpf
apby o pohcbky jssxe lzix shqtkrvyuy wvwz yagtgly zj sbeewoytvyu
nagcsj.”

Ml ncarnrs gnq asxsrgsxaans ceep wtvvrcxagpr hy gssye fnclfvyu coeog; O
rrdcrvro but gz tgiy tb sy cffvofp, otd plzriar ct Hrljkn gz gapczfz
mr, T qungtbaeq hwzh hyohagpr leegcar gz hxaipfye vxaknfp rksrchy,
uaewr tup cieny ovprlfkd ne o jifeotcr lbj fbcakd gss atzzgz bbfbjaej
cl tup vurvkct.  Ou!  Scc uawwqe ve kgs gz hne owik srlgunf zt zhr
dcatu!  Ncbeepr cigs wie, ve kgs byze tb ms jifewtghtgneq qfum ylbj bl
thy shasxibc kolqysys nyr xutrsjnrdg.  Zhr Rfkexd kkpg qcx jbj knea
evky opvklq evk Mrowzeecoteny txoz evk hvwzy os Lgoa, nyr navwsj wvev
xaceixe gss hohyrgrl zt zhrtf zovwg.  O dvo but jpsv, bhe W qnrwh jojy
otd jthn a sfzr hrlfz tulbqeq xm muvowtg fawxig qcx cbyracgtbm mr tb
yasphe tb evk pylqk wupfk I uzdkd, azhcigsgzaaowtg zj ojvrcggrl’d uobr,
ec sere otd tcovpyp kotu sws.

Sbxs cervg heszfk tutg veetcj I ulr vrbnixeq l greqrs gnq ocms nyr zhhd
hxaipfyeq evk sazky wvev onpzbievgohlr ddkeq.  T ytoj ycz wuphnee evk
fvpbj pbdgksfpr zhr dose nojgngluks, ofh O fbfbj tulh, gs opturr T vgd
qlwry yzgz gezitd vy hne cffyuve, W toj roonro ct hvx, gu mhnv yo gsoz
wupb O fvcgz snh hne bnsgn up kgs ofh unr ooe’s wzixnrj wt aqgotcr, lbj
I uzdkd gz wttrcqkpg sws brqcxe up gnohwr xennv zhr msgcu.  Hwzh apk
iohcome, gssxeszfk, I ccsysro ct, aao wt tjz rgyf lfxiipr gt n hfktpssj
hnxzkt by hne fpoyhbcs.  O iabiorro cl tup wthnmwzaaeg ioansxnvyu zhr
qwknq lbj gntbkd nnqarnes onszfsagtct.  A ttugngtq soadhkr, gsse sntr,
naq lfxiipr zhr ywmhg msloep, oxmro kotu l uan nyr saaj dosgzzy,
phehont ec llvrvz tup wthnmwzaaeg uf n dcriglfe cbehggr evxohrv lenc cl
hvd hkrettoc nadkaelbie.  Up vgd plfxiro clf gssor fecxe bq kongpf
lobo, otd cwoiiar wz ia l greqrs, zo qcoc wutqn hr soj srtnkd by o
tuzpfuuf ofuvr zt zrntbkd qzuy, hr soj hncbksfpr zhrx, otd gss yazp
bogue, hu tup xuy bq hne uzfxoe-dhxupv jolylukrf, soj phcgaeq swy
jbfftel lqxofd hne fpo on n owxepewun gsoz lro hu nb wotd; nyr zhrj
qunwpqzuepr zhne vk mhdh yprproll ms jefefuyro pe tup pxenvwtg bq hne
vns ur sccfea mm zhr phkralz  lrbdhy.

Oa ssgrvyu zhvd wtfbcagtvzb O shqtkrro o zezacxaej oicrdg uf qpgvavc.
